(2, 505, 'Shamila JIwa', 'shamila@shamila.com', 'http://www.shamila.com', '78.251.157.246', '2009-07-27 00:32:32', '2009-07-26 22:32:32', 'Hi!\n\nI happened upon your blog and I am so happy to be able to make this connection! I am a jewelry designer based out of the US and in Paris this week (till thursday). I wanted to make some boutique/gallery/museum contacts and was wondering if you could help. I have emailed and visited some boutiques in Le Marais. My work is featured in some luxurious boutiques in Seattle, Manhattan and Toronto as well as museum shops. I am enroute to Turkey where I am going to be doing some work with a goldsmith prior to my Fashion Week debut show in September in NYC. I look forward to hearing from you and see if you can impart some information about connecting with the European market.\n\nWarmly,\nShamila', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
