(253, 1733, 'Lisa Levine jewelry', 'Lisa Levine is a Brooklyn based jewelry designer who learned her skills through her travels around the world and while living and studying in Mexico. Lisa Levine''s designs are made from silver, 18k gold, copper and leather. The designer has a technique of wrapping chains and mixing metal colors making each piece uniquely eye-catching.'),
