(255, 1733, 'ebb.and.pflow Designer jewelry', 'A collaborative design team living between Paris and Bangkok, these two young women have made two-toned designs irresistible. Mixing silver, yellow and rose gold in almost all the designs. Handcrafted, handmade, hand drawn designer jewelry. If you are looking for unique, affordable and one of a kind, these designs are a perfect match.'),
(256, 1733, 'Anna Beck Designs, Anna Beck Jewelry', 'Anna Beck lives and creates her jewelry in Bali. Her jewelry is designed using traditional Balinese jewelry-making techniques. Solid silver bangles, stunning cocktail rings and easily transitional day to night designs. Anna Beck.'),
(257, 1764, '_edit_last', '4'),
(258, 1764, 'W Magazine photo shoot', 'W Magazine December issue 2009. Stated as a magazine about photography. I have always loved W Magazine for that reason and this month especially.  The December issue focuses on the unison of artists from all different sectors; dancers, actors, models, theatre, singers & songwriters.\nInspirational and groundbreaking was the ultimate goal for the United Artists photo shoot. Photographers Ines Van Lamsweerde & Vinoodh Matadin captured each individual in an element all their own.\nFashion Director Alex White styled each artist in the three different Armani collections; Armani Priv, Emporio Armani and Armani Collection. Dennis Freedman W Magazine Creative Director & Alex White Fashion Director styled and directed the shoot.\nExclusive video from the Inez van Lamsweerde & Vinoodh Matadin portfolio starring Hugh Dancy, Peter Sarsgaard, Meredith Monk.'),
