(505, 4, '2009-07-25 13:23:53', '2009-07-25 11:23:53', 'This is where we tell you all about us.\n\nIn a sentence, we are an online jewelry store specializing in the retail and promotion of independent designers. We sell and promote designers and Fair Trade jewelry &amp; accessories that range in pricing from $10 to $1200.\n\nWe don''t think beauty and originality only come with expensive prices. It doesn''t have to be that way.\n\nThe goal of the store is to bring well-deserved light onto the unique accessories world.\n\nEvery month we feature a new designer and offer you the chance to win a design or participate in a promotion (check out our current feature <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/home" target="_blank">HERE</a>).\n\nWe are based out of Paris, originally from Boston. Our goal is to create an international liaison for independent designer jewelry &amp; accessories.\n\nSo, if you are a designer, or you know of a fantastic one, tell us. This is what we are here for.\n\nStimulus, new art, out of the box thinking and design.\n\nThis is<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">IC U</a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-566  aligncenter" title="Zhen-U.N. Full Bloom Earrings" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/MG_9896.jpg" alt="Zhen-U.N. Full Bloom Earrings, $1050" width="480" height="480" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-571  aligncenter" title="David Tishbi Rainbow Moonstone Ring" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/MG_9429.jpg" alt="Dabid Tishbi Moonstone Ring $225" width="480" height="480" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-567  aligncenter" title="Fair Trade Beaded Bangles" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/MG_9389.jpg" alt="Fair Trade Zenzulu Bangles, $15" width="420" height="420" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-572  aligncenter" title="Fair Trade 100% Pashmina Scarf" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/MG_9962-Edit-2.jpg" alt="Fair Trade 100% Pashmina Scarf $65" width="512" height="512" /></a></p>', 'One of those &#039;about us&#039;', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'one-of-those-about-us', '', '', '2009-07-25 13:23:53', '2009-07-25 11:23:53', '', 0, 'https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?p=505', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(689, 4, '2009-09-11 02:43:02', '2009-09-11 00:43:02', '<div style="text-align: center;">\n<div>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">This is real life. We like to show and bring light to what people are actually wearing. And more importantly, what creative souls are out there, roaming the streets inspiring us to do what we do.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Since the headquarters for <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">IC U - In Paris</a> is now in actually in Paris, but originally from Boston, we want to bring to you street style from two sides of the ocean. So, from Boston to Paris street style, with some relevant and matchmaking designs to boot!</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>9.11.09</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em><strong>Paris, Street Style</strong></em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Below: Debra</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Photographer:<a href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a>.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Seen on Boulevard Haussmann. The whole outfit is self-designed. </em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="480" caption="Street style in Paris"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-675" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/street-style/the-hat-paris/"><img style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Paris Street Style" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/The-hat-PARIS.jpg" alt="This hat is too good. " width="480" height="720" /></a>[/caption]\n\nHat''s off (no pun intended ;) to the creative Debra for this fantastic and self-designed ensemble.\n\nNow, matchmaker time.\n\nBelow, some of the pieces Debra chose from the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">boutique</a>:\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-702" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/09/11/paris-street-style/choices-for-debra-blog-2/"><img class="size-full wp-image-702 aligncenter" title="giles and brother bangle, leigh and luca scarf, ebb.and.pflow necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/choices-for-debra-blog1.jpg" alt="choices-for-debra--blog" width="864" height="288" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n\n<div class="mceTemp" style="text-align: center;"><span style="line-height: 17px;"> </span></div>', 'Paris Street Style. Hats off. ', 'CinSummer.com an online jewelry boutique promoting and merchandising independent designers. Based in Paris, we like to celebrate our absolute love for real fashion and real women (and men). Those who push the creative buttons and inspire us for it. Every week, street style from Paris and Boston (our first marching ground). Matched with relevant designs from our exceptional independent designers. Paris street style, independent & unique designer jewelry, affordable jewelry and accessories, the kind you won''t see everyone else wearing. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-street-style', '', '', '2009-09-11 02:43:02', '2009-09-11 00:43:02', '', 0, 'https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?p=689', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(878, 4, '2009-09-14 21:01:57', '2009-09-14 19:01:57', '<em>9.14.09</em>\n\n<strong><em>Paris, Street Style</em></strong>\n<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Below: Lisa</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Photographer:<a style="color: #333333; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com/" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a>.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Seen on Rue De Rivoli.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Vintage Hat. Self-designed jewelry.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_879" align="aligncenter" width="486" caption="Paris Street Style. I love this."]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/red-lips-PARIS.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-879  " title="Street Style, Paris" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/red-lips-PARIS.jpg" alt="Paris Street Style. Just fantastic style." width="486" height="729" /></a>[/caption]\n\nWe love her. Really. This hat, the stand-out jewelry, the nails, the red lips.\n\nIts all just a great, great ensemble.\n\nWhich design would you say would be Lisa''s first choice from the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">boutique</a>?\n\n[caption id="attachment_880" align="aligncenter" width="420" caption="Vintage Pearl Necklace. Double Strand. Wear long or double."]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-880 " title="Vintage Pearl Necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/CinSummer48.jpg" alt="Vintage Pearl Necklace. Double Strand. Wear long or double." width="420" height="420" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_881" align="aligncenter" width="360" caption="David Tishbi designer ring, shines a magnificent blue"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-881 " title="David Tishbi  silver and gold moonstone Ring" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/MG_9429.jpg" alt="David Tishbi designer ring, shines a magnificent blue" width="360" height="360" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_882" align="aligncenter" width="360" caption="Linda Levinson Snake Necklace. "]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-882 " title="Linda Levinson Snake Necklace, gold and turquoise snake necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/MG_9755.jpg" alt="Linda Levinson Snake Necklace. Superb." width="360" height="360" /></a>[/caption]', 'Paris Street Style. Can&#039;t top this. ', 'Paris. Paris Street style. We love this city and all of its creative glory. Our Parisian street stylista of the day, Lisa. We chose three designer jewels from our CinSummer.com inventory...which do you think matches Lisa the most? David Tishbi ring? Linda Levinson Snake necklace? or our Vintage pearl necklace? We love independent design here, this is our way to celebrate affordable, one of a kind jewelry. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '878', '', '', '2009-09-14 21:01:57', '2009-09-14 19:01:57', '', 0, 'https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?p=878', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(906, 4, '2009-09-22 15:19:23', '2009-09-22 13:19:23', '<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>9.22.09</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="color: #000000;">So, as weather starts to cool down here, and the rounds of fashion week continue in full swing, the style is of course following. And one thing that I just simply love in this city is the way women gracefully, stylishly and ever so easily ride around on bikes without breaking a sweat or ruining an outfit. </span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="color: #000000;">And one perfect example is our street style of the day, Debra. Gorgeous smile, beautiful shoes, fantastic shades and a bike. Not your average accessory, but one we can commend.</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><em>________</em></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Below: Debra</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><em>Photographer:<a href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a>.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-style: italic;">Seen on Boulevard Haussmann</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">The whole outfit is an ensemble of vintage finds and small boutique rendez-vous.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Red pumps, red shades and a bike to match. Could you be anymore fantastic?</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">What<a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/" target="_blank">CinSummer.com</a> product would you say fits her best?</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_949" align="aligncenter" width="432" caption="Paris Street Style"]<a class="Paris Street Style" title="Paris Street Style" rel="attachment wp-att-949" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/09/22/906/red-shades-paris-2/"><img class="size-full wp-image-949  " title="Paris Street Style" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/red-shades-PARI