(999, 4, '2009-09-24 16:31:55', '2009-09-24 14:31:55', '<em>9.24.09</em>\n\n<strong><em>Paris, Street Style: Week #2</em></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">Here we go...post numero dos for the week. Paris Street Style. Loving it. Are you? Loving it? Since this is a new feature, we hope you are enjoying the posts as much as we enjoy scouring the streets for style.</span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">And as you may know, this is where we choose to pay homage to the men &amp; women who choose to express them self through style.Expression, being our definition of ''style'', or style being our definition of ''expression''.And self expression being one of those things we often forget we have &amp; if fortunate, are able to control.</span>\n\nOur homage for Thursday goes to the lovely,Karin. Styled in simple lines and an elegant black &amp; white palette, it was a pleasure choosing designs we believe Karin would adore.\n\nFrom the <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/home" target="_blank">CinSummer.com</a> boutique the <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/SR005" target="_blank">Sonya Renee moonstone necklace</a>, <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/DT006" target="_blank">David Tishbi Stackable Black &amp; White Pearl Rings</a>, and <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/LNY001" target="_blank">Lucid NY, Tiny Circle Necklace</a>. Which design would you choose for Karin?\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><em>_____________</em></strong></p>\n<em>Seen on: Rue Charras</em>\n\n<em>Photographer: <a href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a></em>\n\n<em>Jewelry from an independent boutique in the suburbs of Paris.</em>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1000" align="aligncenter" width="420" caption="Street Style, Paris."]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1000" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/09/24/999/paris-street-style-2/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1000 " title="paris-street-style" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/paris-street-style.jpg" alt="Street Style, Paris" width="420" height="630" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1009" align="aligncenter" width="270" caption="Sonya Renee Moonstone Necklace"]<a class="Sonya Renee Necklace" title="Sonya Renee Moonstone Necklace" rel="www.cinsummer.com/blog" href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1009 " title="Sonya renee moonstone necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/Sonya-renee-moonstone-necklace1-300x300.jpg" alt="Sonya Renee Moonstone Necklace" width="270" height="270" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1012" align="aligncenter" width="270" caption="David Tishbi Stackable B&amp;W Pearl Rings"]<a class="David Tishbi handcrafted ring" title="David Tishbi Ring" rel="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/set/2/38" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1012 " title="David Tishbi Stackable Black &amp;amp; White Pearl Rings" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/MG_9443-300x300.jpg" alt="David Tishbi Stackable Black &amp; White Pearl Rings" width="270" height="270" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1013" align="aligncenter" width="270" caption="Lucid NY Circles Necklace"]<a class="Lucid NY necklace" title="Lucid NY two-toned circle necklace" rel="www.cinsummer.com/blog" href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1013 " title="Lucid NY silver &amp; gold Tiny Circles necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/MG_97791-300x300.jpg" alt="Lucid NY Circles Necklace" width="270" height="270" /></a>[/caption]', 'Paris Street Style. The Classic b&amp;w.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '999', 