(1083, 4, '2009-09-28 11:18:25', '2009-09-28 09:18:25', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>9.28.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><strong><em>Paris. Street Style. Week #3. Post 1</em></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">A girlfriend of mine told me yesterday she never shops alone. She said she never knows what works best on her, therefore wants the opinion of someone else. I told her of course she knew, she just wasn''t listening to herself. You know what works because you know what your comfortable in &amp; what you are uncomfortable in. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Don''t wear clothes &amp; accessories just because the magazine tells you this is the ''thing to have''. Forget all that. Know yourself, know what you feel the most sexy &amp; beautiful in and go for it.Why buy something if you are not sure you will absolutely treasure and shine when you wear it? No point.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Trust your gut, sometimes its all you got. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em>Excuse the morning fashion sermon. <span style="color: #000000;">Onto Paris Street Style. </span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-style: normal;">And this morning we have something a little different for you. Mr. Loic Melane. A man who knows his style &amp; wears it quite well. From the two-tone laced sneakers, to the layering of a superb suit jacket, track suit jacket &amp; skater tee...al</span><span style="font-style: normal;">l the way up to the flat-rimmed plaid cap &amp; stylized eyebrow shave. Yes, it is there. </span></span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;">______________________</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">An ensemble of many styles all into one expression. </span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Seen on: <a href="http://thesartorialist.blogspot.com/2009/03/on-streetrue-de-rivoli-paris.html" target="_blank">Rue De Rivoli</a></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Photographer:<a style="color: #333333; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com/" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Clothing and accessories bought at random instances from small boutiques around Paris &amp; Berlin. </em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>It was a nice change choosing men''s jewelry from the <a href="http://www.cinsummer.com" target="_blank">boutique</a> this morning. Between the <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/GBM004" target="_blank">Giles &amp; Brother Brass Cufflinks</a>, the <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/GBM006" target="_blank">Giles &amp; Brother Brass RR Pick ring and/or Bracelet</a>, or the <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/GBM012" target="_blank">Giles &amp; Brother Brass RR pick Necklace</a>...which one do you think suits Mr. Melane best?</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span></p>\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1084" align="aligncenter" width="420" caption="Paris. Street Style. "]<a class="Paris Street Style" title="Paris Street Style, Men''s style, Men''s fashion" rel="https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?attachment_id=1084" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-1084 " title="Paris street style, men''s fashion" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/street-style-Paris-man.jpg" alt="Paris. Street Style. " width="420" height="630" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1087" align="aligncenter" width="240" caption="Giles &amp; Brother Brass Cuff Links"]<a class="Giles and brother brass cufflinks" title="Giles &amp; Brother Brass cufflinks" rel="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/GBM004" href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1087 " title="Giles &amp; Brother Men''s Brass Cuff Links" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/PCG-CUFFs-one-last-CU-nut-and-bolt-links-300x300.jpg" alt="Giles &amp; Brother Brass Cuff Links" width="240" height="240" /></a>[/caption]\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="c