(1107, 4, '2009-09-30 12:11:26', '2009-09-30 10:11:26', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>9.30.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><strong><em>Paris. Street Style. Week #3. Post 2</em></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">Post numero dos. Semaine trois. </span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">Paris. Street Style. Fashion Week is just about to begin. ouh. la. la. We''re looking forward to it, but merely for the slew of style that will be roaming the streets of Paris.</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">The idea for the boutique has always been to bring ladies &amp; gentlemen curated, unique and original designs from independent artists. Love the name brands, but the idea for this boutique is to celebrate the un-branded. The rising and up and coming. </span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">So, fashion week be as it may...we will scour for the original, the unique and the designers who are to make an impact on the independent world.</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">And onto our sought-after fashionista for the day.</span></span>