(1179, 4, '2009-10-05 16:51:02', '2009-10-05 14:51:02', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>10.05.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em> </em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><strong><span style="color: #888888;">Special Edition. Paris Fashion Week.</span> Street Style. Week #4. Post 1</strong></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">We said we would try, and we accomplished. This week we have a special edition for the street style and will be posting shots from Fashion Week here in Paris. Honestly, the difference from this week and our normal finds are not too large. This week is just a bit more extreme. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">And I think our post for the day describes for you what we mean by extreme. Not bad, just noticeable.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-style: normal;"><span style="color: #000000;">Happy Monday. </span></span></span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;">_________________</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;">Below: Brad</span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0p