(1258, 4, '2009-10-08 14:43:33', '2009-10-08 12:43:33', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>10.8.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;">Special Edition. Paris Fashion Week.</span> <strong>Street Style. Week #4. Post 4.</strong></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">Apparently, today is the official last day of Fashion Week 2009 in Paris. But of course that means nothing to our street style posting...it will just be less after this week. Back to trois fois par semaine.</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">It seemed to be a good week. I know the state of the economy plays a role in the mind of many people, but it seemed as though it did not so much affect the display of fashion. Living here, I am often perplexed by the cry of what the French call ''la crise'' a.k.a. ''the crisis''. And my confusion stems from the slew of shopping bags I see on a daily basis, the full cafs (with espressos priced at 2.50!), the visitors for fashion week, etc., etc. </span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">So, confusion expressed. I could go on. Lets just say, everyone has a different view and different situation on the economy, especially when living in different countries.</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em>____________</em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;">Below: XIAU CHEN</span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;">Seen at: Outsidethe<a href="http://www.jeanpaulgaultier.com/" target="_blank">Jean Paul Gaultier</a> show</span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;">Photographer:<a href="http://www.valentinafrugiuele.com/" target="_blank">Valentina Frugiuele</a></span></em></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Wearing: Vintage t-shirt and grey cummberbund (love this!) from a boutique in Japan, <a href="http://www.zara.com/" target="_blank">Zara </a>Jacket, <a href="http://www.leecooper.com/" target="_blank">Lee Cooper</a> pants, <a href="http://www.french-jewellery.fr/epages/62035491.sf/fr_FR/?ObjectPath=/Shops/62035491/Categories" target="_blank">Mi Amor Sic Amor</a> broach &amp; a vintage ring, shoes <a href="http://www.marcjacobs.com/" target="_blank">Marc by Marc Jacob</a>, the bag is <a href="http://www.robertocavalli.com/welcome.do" target="_blank">Just Cavalli</a> by Robert Cavalli.\n</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Choices from our Boutique: <a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/aa-kinal-madonna-earrings.html" target="_blank">AA Kinal Madonna Earrings</a>, <a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/lisa-levine-rose-gold-and-stone-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine rose gold and semi-precious stone necklace</a> &amp;<a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/brown-bolero.html" target="_blank"> Zhen U.N.''s brown leather bolero bag</a>. </em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_1263" align="aligncenter" width="384" caption="XIAU CHEN. Paris Fashion Week 2009. Jean Gaultier Show."]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1263" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/10/08/paris-fashion-week-2009-street-style-2/xhen-paris-fahsion-week-2009/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1263  " title="XIAU CHEN-paris-fahsion-week-2009" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/xhen-paris-fahsion-week-2009.jpg" alt="XIAU CHEN. Paris Fashion Week 2009. Jean Gaultier Show." width="384" height="818" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1268" align="aligncenter" width="262" caption="AA Kinal Madonna Earrings"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1268" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/10/08/paris-fashion-week-2009-street-style-2/aa-kinal-for-paris-fashion-week-madonna-earrings/" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1268 " title="aa-kinal-for-paris-fashion-week-madonna-earrings" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/aa-kinal-for-paris-fashion-week-madonna-earrings-262x299.jpg" alt="AA Kinal Madonna Earrings" width="262" height="299" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1270" align="aligncenter" width="270" caption="Lisa Levine Rose Gold and Stone Nkl"]<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1270   " title="lisa-levine-necklace-for-fashion-week-2009" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/lisa-levine-necklace-for-fashion-week-2009-300x300.jpg" alt="Lisa Levine Rose Gold and Stone Necklace" width="270" height="270" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1269" align="aligncenter" width="270" caption="Zhen U.N. Brown Leather Bolero Bag"]<a href="http://www.ic