(1286, 4, '2009-10-09 16:39:39', '2009-10-09 14:39:39', '<em>10.09.09</em>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em>Special Edition. Paris Fashion Week.</em></span><em> </em><strong><em>Street Style. Week #4. Post 5.</em></strong>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">There is not much to say about these two. Just a perfect pair to end the week. </span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">This is why I love fashion. To each his/her own. </span>\n\n____________\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below:</span> Anonymous.</span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #999999;">Seen: <span style="color: #000000;">Outside the <a href="http://www.jeanpaulgaultier.com/" target="_blank">Jean Paul Gaultier</a> show.</span></span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Photographer:</span> </span><a href="http://www.valentinafrugiuele.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Valentina Frugiuele</span></a></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">She''s Wearing:</span> </span><a href="http://www.mulberry.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Mulberry</span></a><span style="color: #000000;"> jacket and bag, </span><a href="http://www.topshop.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/TopCategoriesDisplay?storeId=12556&amp;catalogId=19551" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Top Shop</span></a><span style="color: #000000;"> shirt,pants and belt</span><a href="http://www.arrogantcat.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;"> Arrogant Cut</span></a><span style="color: #000000;">, </span><a href="http://www.miumiu.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Miu Miu</span></a><span style="color: #000000;"> black patent leather boots</span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><s