ris fashion week 2009. Style seen outside the Jean Paul Gaultier Show. Street style. creative style. fashion week images. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-fashion-week-2009-2', '', '', '2009-10-09 16:39:39', '2009-10-09 14:39:39', '', 0, 'https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?p=1286', 0, 'post', '', 0);
