(1337, 4, '2009-10-12 15:04:18', '2009-10-12 13:04:18', '<em>10.12.09</em>\n\n<em>Paris. Street Style. </em><em><span style="color: #888888;">Week #5. Post 1.</span></em>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">Even though Fashion Week is over here in Paris, we had some residual photos, and we couldn''t let them go to waste...</span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">But something I forgot to mention last week!</span></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><a href="http://www.notjustalabel.com/hosts/diane_pernet" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Diane Pernet</span></a><span style="color: #000000;">, clothing designer, co-editor in Chief of </span><span style="color: #808080;"><a href="http://www.zoomagazine.de/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">ZOO Magazine</span></a></span><span style="color: #000000;">, &amp; co-founder to the ever-stimulating </span><span style="color: #808080;"><a href="http://www.ashadedviewonfashion.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">A Shaded View on Fashion</span></a></span><span style="color: #000000;"> blog, held her 2nd annual </span><a href="http://www.ashadedviewonfashionfilm.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Fashion Film Festival </span></a><span style="color: #000000;">. The festival was held in Paris, and for three days 100''s of independent films were shown and rated. We were able to check out a day of the films, amazing. The winner was chosen at the </span><a href="http://www.centrepompidou.fr/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Centre Pompidou</span></a><span style="color: #000000;"> and announced by</span><a href="http://www.rickowens.eu/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;"> Rick Owens</span></a><span style="color: #000000;">. </span></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">We didn''t make it to the awards ceremony, but we posted on the </span><a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?page_id=1319" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">''artistic stuffing''</span></a><span style="color: #000000;"> page a small video clip of snippets from the winners of each category. Its something worth checking out if independent fashion, design, and voices are something you like. </span></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">So, happy Monday, and happy long weekend to the Etats-unis.</span></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;">Onto Street Style. </span></em></span>\n\n____________\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below: <span style="color: #000000;">AURELIE</span></span><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #999999;">Seen:<span style="color: #000000;">Outside the<a href="http://www.jeanpaulgaultier.com/" target="_blank">Jean Paul Gaultier</a> show.</span></span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Photographer:</span> </span><span style="color: #000000;">Valentina Frugiuele</span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Wearing:</span> A mix of vintage clothes, scarf &amp; bag,<a href="http://www.zara.com/" target="_blank">Zara Jacket</a>, <a href="http://www.leecooper.com/" target="_blank">Lee Cooper pants</a>, a truly original cigarette-butt pin <a href="http://www.french-jewellery.fr/epages/62035491.sf" target="_blank">Mi Amor Sic Amor</a>, andthe ring is also vintage.</span></em></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Choices From the Boutique: <a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/aa-kinal-charly-bracelet.html" target="_blank">AA Kinal Charly Bracelet</a><span style="color: #000000;">, </span><span style="color: #00