(1414, 4, '2009-10-19 15:28:48', '2009-10-19 13:28:48', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>10.19.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Paris. Street Style. </em><em><span style="color: #888888;">Week #6. Post 1.</span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Monday....Yeah. It''s Monday. Its cold here, not sure how it is where you are but we are wondering what happened to the fall? Gone too fast and no foliage to make it pretty. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">In either case, today''s street style is neither fall, nor winter and especially not summer. Its just Tara. And we like her because she is an ''out of the box'' kind of stylish gal. And from Finland at that. I would have never guessed that. Not your average ''street style'' and definitely not the average that we find in Paris. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;">____________</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below:<span style="color: #000000;">TARA</span></span><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #999999;">Seen: </span><span style="color: #999999;"><span style="color: #000000;">Jardin Tuileres</span></span></em></span></em></p