(1527, 4, '2009-11-02 14:21:14', '2009-11-02 13:21:14', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>11.02.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Paris.<span style="color: #ff0000;"> Halloween </span>Street Style. </em><em><span style="color: #888888;">Week #8. Post 1. </span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Halloween in Paris. I didn''t expect much. Parisians do not normally celebrate for Halloween. Of course , that being the case I was hit with a major surprise. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">The surprise? A parade full of zombies. And I''m not talking cute costumes and people laughing...I''m talking full on frightening costumes, dripping blood, groaning, growling, dying, &amp; hungry Parisian zombies. They went all out, hundreds of the them. There was even a zombie band. Quite good actually. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Can you imagine? No? Okay. Pictures please. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Paris. Street style &amp; the zombies. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Next time, I won''t assume they don''t celebrate. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;">____________</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below: <span style="color: #000000;">Lots of zombies</span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #999999;">Seen:<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://www.parismarais.com/" target="_blank">Le Marais</a></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Photographer:</span> Christan Summers</span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Wearing: </span><span style="color: #999999;"><span style="color: #000000;">V</span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #000000;">e</span>ry real, very frightening zombie costumes. </span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"> </span></em></p>\n<em> </em>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n<em> </em>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em> </em></p>\n<em>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1531" align="aligncenter" width="420" caption="The Zombie Parade."]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1531" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/11/02/paris-street-style-the-zombie-parade/zombie-parade-paris-street-style-2009/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1531  " title="Zombie-parade-paris-street-style-2009" src="https://www.icui