ouple with a chic, simple yet sexy style. This is Paris after all. Choices from the boutique include Giles and Brother silver cuff links, Lisa Levine falling rain earrings and Lisa levine silver and leather headband. We are here to support independent and unique fashion and designers. This is why we love street style and this is why we roam the streets looking for people who represent and wear all that is creative and unique. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-street-style-the-man-his-shoes', '', '', '2009-11-04 18:30:59', '2009-11-04 17:30:59', '', 0, 'https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?p=1550', 0, 'post', '', 0);
