(1586, 4, '2009-11-06 17:42:49', '2009-11-06 16:42:49', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>11.06.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Paris.<span style="color: #ff0000;"> </span>Street Style. </em><em><span style="color: #888888;">Week #8. Post 3.</span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Today I wanted to do something different. So far I have posted ''street style'' as people. Fashion. Accessories. Yes, of course this what ''street style'' has been defined as, however, there is also a different kind of street style in Paris. This particular street style I don''t believe is given enough credit. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">It is an art which has fed my inspiration and the inspiration of many other. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Street art. Our street style of the day. The artists are unknown. Anonymous. This is an underground society of artists that are truly talented and who have done this for years. Sometimes I wonder how many layers of art are under the one image I capture? Can you imagine? Hundreds, if not thousands...depending upon the age of the wall I suppose. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">It''s not graffiti. Well, to me it''s not. To me, this is a form of art un-touched by economy, industries, money...well, almost. You think of the Berlin wall and my statement has no just. However, its not like there are high-end clubs who attract street artists and sell 700 champagne bottles. At least not to my knowledge. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">So, here you are. My latest inspiration of street art. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Happy Friday everyone et bon weekend. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;">____________</span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below:<span style="color: #000000;">STREET ART</span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Seen: <span style="color: #000000;">All over Paris</span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Photographer:</span> Christan Summers</span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></em></span></em></p>\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </em></em>\n\n<em><em> </