(1628, 4, '2009-11-11 19:17:48', '2009-11-11 18:17:48', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>11.11.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Paris.<span style="color: #ff0000;"> </span>Street Style. </em><em><span style="color: #888888;">Week #9. Post 2.</span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">fabulous</span><span style="font-family: HiraMinPro-W3;"> |fabyls|</span></span></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;"><em>ORIGIN late Middle English (in the sense [known through fable, unhistorical] ): from French <span style="color: #000000;">fabuleux</span> or Latin <span style="color: #000000;">fabulosus</span> ''celebrated in fable,'' from <span style="color: #000000;">fabula</span>. (That''s the <a href="http://www.wikipedia.org/" target="_blank">Wikipedia</a> definition at least...)</em></span></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">A word related to so many different instances, people, places, etc. Descriptive to the max and filled with any amount of emotion you want to say it with. </span><span style="color: #000000;">Like this one:<em>Woo Yeah is Fabulous. </em></span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">That''s not one you see everyday. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">The point exactly. Woo yeah, yes, that is his name and a man who I wish you all could have spoken to as well. Energy, life, excitement and his ''special bag from Korea.'' </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">He is just big ball of fabulousness, and no, that one is not in the Wikipedia.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">To our street style man of the day. Woo Yeah. Every time I write his name I can''t help but smile! </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;">____________</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below:<span style="color: #000000;">WOO YEAH</span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Seen:<span style="color: #000000;">Blvd Raspail</span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Photographer:</span> Christan Summers</span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="colo