(1664, 4, '2009-11-16 20:05:33', '2009-11-16 19:05:33', '<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>11.16.09</em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em>Paris.<span style="color: #ff0000;"> </span>Street Style. </em><em><span style="color: #888888;">Week #10. Post 1.</span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">We had a photo shoot over the weekend,shot in the Tuileries Jardin, just next to the Louvre and then moved toward the Eiffel Tower, as requested by the photographer </span><a href="http://www.kendrarae.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Kendra Rae</span></a><span style="color: #000000;">. </span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">Model, Ellen Scholten, transformed behind the camera and as a beginner in the industry I am happy to project, she will be successful. A classic beauty with an edge. Can''t ask for much more. She braved the cold and even a carousel in motion (they started it on us when we were shooting and we were stuck until the ride was over!). Eva, our maquilleuse (make-up artist) was wonderful and of course Erin! My absolute fantastic assistant! Help me put the shoot together and see it through until the end!</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Fantastic team. Exceptional shoot. Unexpected results. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">The pics below are just a "behind the scenes" view, these are shots I took, we will have to wait a bit until we receive the final shots from Kendra. </span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Merci  l''quipe. C''tait merveilleux de travailler avec vous tous.</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;">____________</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Below: Ellen, Kendra, Erin &amp; Eva. Tuileries Photo Shoot. </span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Seen:<span style="color: #000000;">Tuileries Jardin</span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Photographer:</span> Christan Summers</span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Wearing: <span style="color: #000000;">For the shoot Ellen wore a <a href="http://www.christian-lacroix.fr/" target="_blank">Christian Lacroix</a> coat, Joolay chemise, &amp; <a href="http://www.prada.com/" target="_blank">Prada Shoes</a>. The second outfit was a mix of vintage <a href="http://www.dior.com/" target="_blank">Christian Dior</a>, small boutique purchases and <a href="http://www.prada.com/" target="_blank">Prada shoes</a>. As for CinSummer jewelry, Ellen wore<a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/lisa-levine-waterfall-chain-earrings.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine''s Waterfall Chain earrings</a>,<a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/#/shop/product/AN002" target="_blank"> Any NY gradient gold necklace</a> &amp; <a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/zhen-un-solid-18k-gold-and-gold-citri18.html" target="_blank">Zhen U.N. 18k gold &amp; citrine earrings</a>. </span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><em><span style="color: #888888;"><em><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></span></em></span></em></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_1672" align="aligncenter" width="350" caption="Ellen et les arbres dan Jardin des Tuileres"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1672" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/11/16/paris-jardin-des-tuileries-photo-shoot/ellen-dans-le-tuileres-2/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1672  " title="Ellen-dans-le-Tuileres" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-dans-le-Tuileres1.jpg" alt="Ellen et les arbres dan Jardin des Tuileres" width="350" height="682" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_1666" align="aligncenter" width="378" caption="Behind the eyes of the photographer"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1666" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/11/16/paris-jardin-des-tuileries-photo-shoot/ellen-et-kendra-la-photographe/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1666   " title="Ellen-et-Kendra-la-photographe" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-et-Kendra-la-photographe.jpg" alt="Behind the eyes of the photographer" width="378" height="684" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;"><span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span></p>\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> </em></span>\n\n<em> </em>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1665" align="aligncenter" width="432" caption="Ellen &amp; Eva. Touching up."]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1665" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/11/16/paris-jardin-des-tuileries-photo-shoot/ellen-eva-tuileres-shoot-makeup/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1665   " title="Ellen-&amp;-Eva-Tuileres-shoot-makeup" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-Eva-Tuileres-shoot-makeup.jpg" alt="Ellen &amp; Eva. Touching up." width="432" height="359" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1673" align="aligncenter" width="245" caption="Erin. I finally caught a picture!"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1673" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/11/16/paris-jardin-des-tuileries-photo-shoot/erin-la-assistante-irreplacable/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1673 " title="Erin la assistante irreplacable" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Erin-la-assistante-irreplacable.jpg" alt="Erin. I finally caught a picture!" width="245" height="382" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1674" align="aligncenter" width="224" caption="Le femme avec les mains magic! "]<a rel="attachment wp-att-1674" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/11/16/paris-jardin-des-tuileries-photo-shoot/eva-la-maquilluese/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1674 " title="Eva la Maquilluese" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Eva-la-Maquilluese.jpg" alt="Le femme avec les mains magic! She makes people beautiful :)" width="224" height="484" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_1675" align="aligncenter" width="338" caption="Second outfit."]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-Paris-Shoot-For-CInSummer.jpg"><img class="size-large wp-image-1675 " title="Ellen Paris Shoot For CInSummer" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-Paris-Shoot-For-CInSummer-422x1024.jpg" alt="" width="338" height="819" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_1676" align="aligncenter" width="347" caption="Ellen &amp; Le Eiffel"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-Le-Eiffel.jpg"><img class="size-large wp-image-1676  " title="Ellen-&amp;-Le-Eiffel" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Ellen-Le-Eiffel-552x1024.jpg" alt="" width="347" height="645" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>', 'Paris. Jardin Des Tuileries. Photo Shoot.', 'This post is going to be another exception. I had a photo shoot over the weekend and everyone involved was working together for the first time. Although things went extremely well, there were different times each one of us had to accept the situation and work with it.\nWe shot in the Tuileries Jardin, just next to the Louvre and then moved toward the Eiffel Tower, as requested by the photographer Kendra Rae. Our model, Ellen, transformed behind the camera and as a beginner in the industry I am happy to project, she will be successful. A classic beauty with an edge. Can''t ask for much more. She braved the cold and even a carousel in motion (they started it on us when we were shooting and we were stuck until the ride was over!). Eva, our maquilleuse (make-up artist) was wonderful and of course Erin! My absolute fantastic assistant! Help me put the shoot together and see it through until the end!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-jardin-des-tuileries-photo-shoot', '', '', '2009-11-16 20:05:33', '2009-11-16 19:05:33', '', 0, 'https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?p=1664', 0, 'post', '', 0);
