(2206, 4, '2009-12-13 19:33:28', '2009-12-13 18:33:28', '12.14.09\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://www.fashiontalents.it/home.php" target="_blank">Italian Fashion Talents 2009 Contest.</a></span><a href="http://www.fashiontalents.it/home.php" target="_blank"> </a>Week #13. Post 1.</span>\n\n<span style="color: #888888;"><span style="color: #000000;">Yesterday, I received an e-mail from model and friend </span><a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/blog/?page_id=762" target="_blank"><span style="color: #000000;">Michaela Bruno </span></a><span style="color: #000000;">asking me to visit the website for the Italian Fashion Talents contest and vote for her photographer friend. Of course I visited, and proceeded to spend a reasonable amount of my evening viewing all the other contestants. Fantastic talent. Some not so good. </span></span>\n\n<span style="color: #000000;">My favorites are below. Check out the others and vote as well! </span>\n\n<span style="background-color: #ffffff;" title="Fashion Talents  il primo concorso rivolto a gruppi di giovani talenti della moda ideato e organizzato da Nina Koklar in collaborazione con Canon Italia, MAC Cosmetics, Style.it e TONI&amp;GUY.">Talents Fashion is the first competition aimed at groups of young talents in fashion conceived and organized by Nina Kokla Italy in cooperation with Canon, MAC Cosmetics, Style.it and TONI &amp; GUY.</span>\n\n<span style="background-color: #ffffff;" title="Fashion Talents  il primo concorso rivolto a gruppi di giovani talenti della moda ideato e organizzato da Nina Koklar in collaborazione con Canon Italia, MAC Cosmetics, Style.it e TONI&amp;GUY.">_________________</span>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #888888;">Name of Group:<span style="color: #000000;"> BROKE BUT BEAUTIFUL</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #888888;">Stylist: <span style="color: #000000;">Aysha Bilgrami</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #888888;">Photographer:</span> Daniela Benedetti</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #888888;">Make-up/Hair: <span style="color: #000000;">Vanessa Davoli/Oriana Dattilo</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #888888;">Model: <span style="color: #000000;">Vanna Quattrini</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff;" title="L''hair stylist che realizzer la migliore acconciatura avr l''opportunit di partecipare gratuitamente al corso avanzato di Creative Cutting &amp; Colouring della durata di 3 giorni nella prestigiosa Accademia presso il Palazzo delle Stelline in Corso Magenta 63 a Milano."><span style="color: #888888;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff;" title="Suburban Knight"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #999999;">Title of Project:</span> Broke But Beautiful</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<span style="background-color: #ffffff;" title="L''hair stylist che realizzer la migliore acconciatura avr l''opportunit di partecipare gratuitamente al corso avanzato di Creative Cutting &amp; Colouring della durata di 3 giorni nella prestigiosa Accademia presso il Palazzo delle Stelline in Corso Magenta 63 a Milano."><span style="line-height: normal; font-size: small;">\n</span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #808080;">''</span><span style="color: #808080;">Things: a focus, an attitude and a way of life, we don''t posses them , they posses us, and even in a economical crisis, we prefer them over everything else.</span></span></span>\n\n<span style="background-color: #ffffff;" title="L''hair stylist che realizzer la migliore acconciatura avr l''opportunit di partecipare gratuitamente al corso avanzato di Creative Cutting &amp; Colouring della durata di 3 giorni nella prestigiosa Accademia presso il Palazzo delle Stelline in Corso Magenta 63 a Milano."><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #808080;">''</span><em><span style="color: #808080;">Cose: una messa a fuoco, un atteggiamento e una scelta di vita. Non sono di nostro posseso, siamo noi che siamo posseduti da loro, e anche in periodo di crisi economica, li preferiamo su tutto il resto.''</span></em></span></span>\n\n[caption id="attachment_2208" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption="Broke but Beautiful"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-2208" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/12/13/a-grande-lot-of-artists-italian-contest-2009/broke-but-beautiful-intro/"><img class="size-full wp-image-2208 " title="broke-but-beautiful-intro" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/broke-but-beautiful-intro.jpg" alt="Broke But Beautiful 1" width="600" height="401" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_2209" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption="Broke But Beautiful Accessorized"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-2209" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/12/13/a-grande-lot-of-artists-italian-contest-2009/broke-but-beautiful-1/"><img class="size-full wp-image-2209 " title="broke-but-beautiful-2" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/broke-but-beautiful-1.jpg" alt="Broke But Beautiful Accessorized" width="600" height="450" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_2210" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption="Broke But Beautiful Shopping"]<a rel="attachment wp-att-2210" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2009/12/13/a-grande-lot-of-artists-italian-contest-2009/broke-but-beautiful-2/"><img class="size-full wp-image-2210 " title="broke-but-beautiful-2" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/broke-but-beautiful-2.jpg" alt="Broke but Beautiful " width="600" height="401" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: left;">To view more images, click<a href="http://www.fashiontalents.it/gallery_gruppo.php?id=128" target="_blank">HERE</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">__________________</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: