(3100, 4, '2010-02-24 10:28:07', '2010-02-24 09:28:07', '<em>2.24.10</em>\n\n<em>Valentine''s Day Pop-up Shop. Boston. The results.<span style="color: #888888;">Week #21. Post 1.</span></em>\n\nIt''s all in the name: Boldfacers. And this pop-up shop was the point of definition.\n\nI had no idea what I was getting into when I accepted the invitation to participate in the <a href="http://www.boldfacers.com/index.cfm?page=happening&amp;happening_id=81" target="_blank">Boldfacers Valentine''s Day Pop-Up Shop</a>. I was simply going home to Boston for a quick trip, so why not bang out a show while I''m home?\n\n[caption id="attachment_3101" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption=" The congregated crowd of the Sex!Love!Toys! Boldfacers Pop-up Shop"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-pop-up-shop-boston-icuinparis.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3101" title="boldfacers pop up shop boston icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-pop-up-shop-boston-icuinparis.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="399" /></a>[/caption]\n\nWell, the show, the Pop-Up Shop, was not just any show. When I walked in the door to set up my table I was a bit surprised to see a table full of dildos to my left and a bondage station to my right. No kidding.\n\n[caption id="attachment_3104" align="aligncenter" width="527" caption=" Angela Mitchell, dildo in hand bathing in a tub of condoms. "]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/Angela-Mitchell-boldfacers-popo-up-shop.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3104" title="Angela Mitchell boldfacers popo up shop" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/Angela-Mitchell-boldfacers-popo-up-shop.jpg" alt="" width="527" height="399" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_3114" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption=" Robyn Holman learns the art of bondage from Bound in Boston"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-boston-bondage.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3114" title="boldfacers boston bondage" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-boston-bondage.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="399" /></a>[/caption]\n\nHappily, I found a bit of simplicity in Andrea Halliday''s table who is the owner of <a href="http://tableandtulip.com/home.html" target="_blank">Table and Tulip</a> and her exotic flower selection and arrangements put me a bit at ease....that was until I saw that she had made nipple pasties out of orchids. ey, yay, yay!\n\n[caption id="attachment_3103" align="aligncenter" width="602" caption="Andrea Halliday, owner Table and Tulip"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-pop-up-shop-andrea-hallday-table-and-tulip-owner.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3103" title="boldfacers pop up shop andrea hallday table and tulip owner" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-pop-up-shop-andrea-hallday-table-and-tulip-owner.jpg" alt="" width="602" height="399" /></a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_3113" align="aligncenter" width="598" caption=" Rachel Branwen, Sarah Petras, and Andrea Halliday, owner Table and Tulip"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-pop-up-shop-table-and-tulip-owner-andrea-halliday.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3113" title="boldfacers pop up shop table and tulip owner andrea halliday" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-pop-up-shop-table-and-tulip-owner-andrea-halliday.jpg" alt="" width="598" height="399" /></a>[/caption]\n\nBut the shock continued and situated next to Andrea, was <a href="http://www.mssavannah.com/Home.html" target="_blank">Ms. Savannah</a>, a professional dominatrixand her ''sex slave,'' Brutus.\n\n[caption id="attachment_3107" align="aligncenter" width="360" caption="Ms. Savannah, Boston Dominatrix &amp; profiled Boldfacer"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/ms.-savannah-boston-dominatrix.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3107" title="ms. savannah boston dominatrix" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/ms.-savannah-boston-dominatrix.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="493" /></a>[/caption]\n\nMelissa Bennett, owner of <a href="http://www.frenchdressinglingerie.com/" target="_blank">French Dressing boutique</a> was also there with beautiful lingerie and a grande selection of<a href="http://www.frenchdressinglingerie.com/" target="_blank">Hanky Panky</a> at prices that were almost too good.\n\n[caption id="attachment_3106" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption="Melissa Bennett, owner of French Dressing boutique"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-for-icuinparis.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3106" title="boldfacers for icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldfacers-for-icuinparis.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="399" /></a>[/caption]\n\nDespite the racy vendors and the shock, attendees absolutely loved the event. Everyone sold inventory like hot cakes (not sure about the dominatrix...) and we were all impressed by the way <a href="http://www.boldfacers.com/index.cfm?page=aboutus" target="_blank">Lisa Pierpont</a>, owner and founder of <a href="http://www.boldfacers.com/?page=happening&amp;happening_id=81" target="_blank">Boldfacers</a> was able to push all of our comfort level buttons but keep the room full and crowd pleased.\n\n[caption id="attachment_3108" align="aligncenter" width="600" caption="Friend &amp; photographer for I C U - In Paris Ian Barnard &amp; his wife, Ting"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/boldacers-ian-branard-and-wife-ting.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-3108" title="boldacers ian branard and wife ting" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2