(3135, 4, '2010-03-04 12:04:52', '2010-03-04 11:04:52', '<em>3.04.10</em>\n\n<em>Slowing it down. Speeding it up. <span style="color: #888888;">Week #22. Post 1.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="font-style: normal;">So, things are a bit crazy over here. Plates are full, site is finally moving along and soon, oh so soon we will have a store back on the web. </span></em>\n\n<em><span style="font-style: normal;">In the midst of this all, life keeps spinning, turning, and throwing all kinds of ''stuff'' our way to keep us quite in the occupied state of mind. </span></em>\n\nThis being said, the blog posts are coming less often simply because we have less time to create them. However, we are leaning towards a new method and creating one post/week at the end of each week which will highlight the best of the best we wish to share.\n\nToday''s post is an exception, one, for announcing this and two, I just found this video through a friend and I find it too cool not to share.\n\nEspecially since this weeks <a href="http://www.anous.fr/" target="_blank">ANOUS</a> (free Paris metro magazine) is highlighting Japan and the level of cool which Tokyo produces.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/anous-japan.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3129" title="anous japan" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/anous-japan.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="500" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">If Viewing From Your E-mail Box, Click Links To View Video.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="425" height="344" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/GzKgjmrqmRI&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1&amp;" /><param name="allowfullscr