(3337, 4, '2010-04-09 11:57:01', '2010-04-09 09:57:01', '<em>4.08.10</em>\n\n<em><a href="http://lightkitchen.net/english/contact_english.htm" target="_blank">Light Kitchen</a> &amp; ICU.</em><em> Week #26. Post 4.</em>\n\nLast weekend we were delighted with the opportunity to work with the young and talented photographer, <a href="http://harrynizard.110mb.com/" target="_blank">Harry Nizard </a>inside the AMAZING <a href="http://lightkitchen.net/english/contact_english.htm" target="_blank">Light Kitchen</a> studio of Paris.\n\nModel, Erwan Sands charmed us with both his humor and sultry looks to create a simply perfect shoot for our <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/#/mens" target="_blank">Giles &amp; Brother</a> men''s collection.\n\nA behind the scenes video from the shoot, acouple sneak peak shots from behind the scenes, post production and post production play...\n<p style="text-align: center;"><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="560" height="340" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/g5zeluEth4M&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1&amp;" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="560" height="340" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/g5zeluEth4M&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1&amp;" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"> </embed></object>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/photo-shoot-paris-light-kitchen-in-action.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3342" title="photo shoot paris light kitchen in action" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/photo-shoot-paris-light-kitchen-in-action.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="319" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/icu-photo-shoot-in-paris.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3343" title="icu photo shoot in paris" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/icu-photo-shoot-in-paris.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="359" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/icu-phot-shoot-in-paris-light-kitchen-studio.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3341" title="icu phot shoot in paris - light kitchen studio" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/icu-phot-shoot-in-paris-light-kitchen-studio.jpg" alt="" width="336" height="505" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">A bit of the post production result...</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/brac-cufflink-ring-giles-and-brother.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3339" title="brac, cufflink, ring giles and brother" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/brac-cufflink-ring-giles-and-brother-942x1024.jpg" alt="" width="362" height="393" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="font-style: normal;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Giles-Brother-brass-ring.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3345" title="Giles &amp; Brother brass ring" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Giles-Brother-brass-ring-1024x1008.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="424" /></a></span></em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="font-style: normal;"> </span></em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Giles-and-Brother-silver-pin.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-3348" title="Giles and Brother silver pin" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog