(4003, 7, '2010-09-17 19:09:50', '2010-09-17 17:09:50', '9.17.2010. Week #38. Post 2.\n\nNew Designer Love!\n\nThis is just a sneak peak of ICU''s newest designer additions for the October Boutique launch. Two Parisian designers who are definitely on the rise...\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"></h2>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Coralie De Seynes</h2>\nCoralie De Seynes''s 2010-2011 collection described as Urban Chic by Eclat de Mode Magazine has just won a space at Galleries Lafayette (one of the biggest high end department stores in Paris). We love here pieces because they are easy to where and wonderful to layer, well made from genuine leather and silver/gold plated and on top of it all - affordable. We expect to see just about every Parisian lady wearing Coralie in the months to come.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/Collier-Mors-marron-1600x1200.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-4013" title="Collier Mors marron [1600x1200]" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/Collier-Mors-marron-1600x1200-634x1024.jpg" alt="" width="406" height="655" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/Collier-Licol-gris-argent-1600x1200.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-4015" title="Collier Licol gris argent [1600x1200]" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/Collier-Licol-gris-argent-1600x1200-471x1024.jpg" alt="" width="471" height="1024" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/Look-Book-Attelage-Hiver-2011-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-4016" title="Look Book Attelage Hiver 2011" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/Look-Book-Attelage-Hiver-2011-11-671x1024.jpg" alt="" width="537" height="819" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/coralie-headband.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4027" title="coralie headband" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/coralie-headband.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="630" /></a></p>\n\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Lamia Benalycherif</h2>\nLamia Benalycherif - a Parisian with a heart for New York is changing the scene of recyclable, innovative, hand made jewelry. The designer works with materials you never imagined could be so perfect for jewelry and the colors - oh the colors are fabulous! From upper arm bracelets with hot pink fringe, to chunky beaded necklaces mixed with chains and ribbons... Lamia is off to a running start.\n\n<a style="text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/lamia-necklace.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4017" title="lamia necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/lamia-necklace.jpg" alt="" width="660" height="792" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/lamia-green.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-4025" title="lamia green" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/lamia-green-771x1024.jpg" alt="" width="771" height="1024" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/nkl-red-ribbon.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4022" title="icuinparis lamia benalycherif" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/nkl-red-ribbon.jpg" alt="" width="770" height="781" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/lamia.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4021" title="lamia" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/lamia.jpg" alt="" width="491" height="737" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Two new designers, two very unique styles. Both expressing the idea of ICU - IN PARIS</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Bringing you Independent, Curated, &amp; Unique pieces of jewelry.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Not available to purchase just yet... Coming soon, coming soon.</p>', 'ICU New Designer Love ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'icu-new-designer-love-%e2%99%a1', '', '', '2010-09-17 19:09:50', '2010-09-17 17:09:50', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4003', 0, 'post', '', 2),
