(4363, 4, '2010-10-22 13:06:01', '2010-10-22 11:06:01', '10.22.2010. Week #43. Post 3\n\nICU''s beloved Mademoiselle <a href="http://www.sophiemhabille.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff00ff;">Sophie Mhabille</span></a> has been making quite the Street Style strides since the last time she appeared in the ICU Blog!\n\nFrom New York Fashion Week to London and back to Paris we are on the edge of our chairs each week to see what street style gems Sophie is finding and snapping. Never disappointed and always pleasantly inspired.\n\nBelow, Sophie''s look for today (yes, that is her) and click <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2010/10/22/icus-favorite-finds-by-sophie-mhabille/" target="_blank">HERE</a> to check out a few of our fav''s that she snapped across the ocean and here in Paris.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8470-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4367" title="img_8470-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8470-small.jpg" alt="http://www.sophiemhabille.com/" width="520" height="780" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8488-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4368" title="img_8488-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8488-small.jpg" alt="Sophie Mhabille" width="520" height="780" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8498-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4369" title="img_8498-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8498-small.jpg" alt="http://www.sophiemhabille.com/" width="520" height="347" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">What Sophie has to say about her outfit:</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>J''ai dnich cette veste en fourrure d''Oslo, vintage, sortie tout droit des annes 70, dans une nouvelle petite boutique : Rtro Chic 4, place du March Sainte Catherine  Paris, dans le 4 arrondissement. Son effet est tonnant. Elle a vraiment du style. Tout accessoire semble superflus  cot... quoique, une jolie ceinture Herms  clous est tout  fait la bienvenue. Le tout : Rtro Chic.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="color: #888888;">I found this Oslo fur jacket from the 70''s in small new boutique called: Retri Chic 4 at Place du March Sainte Catherine in Paris''s 4th arrondissement. It''s effect was amazing - just the perfect style. All the accessories seam unnecessary paired with it... however, a nice Herms belt of nails is always welcomes ; ) </span></em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="color: #888888;">\n</span></em></p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8495-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4370" title="img_8495-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8495-small.jpg" alt="http://www.sophiemhabille.com/" width="520" height="347" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">To view more street style by Sophie visit: <span style="color: #ff00ff;">http://www.sophiemhabille.com/index.php/</span></p>', 'Mlle. Sophie is back....', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mlle-sophie-is-back', '', '', '2010-10-22 13:06:01', '2010-10-22 11:06:01', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4363', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4380, 4, '2010-10-22 13:05:28', '2010-10-22 11:05:28', '10.22.2010. Week #43. Post 4\n\nLovin this... all of it.\n\nIf you want to see the full image click more info on what each person is wearing and more fabulous street style, go to Sophie''s Blog at: <a href="http://www.sophiemhabille.com" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff00ff;">http://www.sophiemhabille.com</span></a>\n\n[gallery link="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2010/10/22/4380/" orderby="rand"]', 'ICU&#039;s Favorite Finds By, Sophie Mhabille', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'icus-favorite-finds-by-sophie-mhabille', '', '', '2010-10-22 13:05:28', '2010-10-22 11:05:28', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4380', 0, 'post', '', 0);
