(4445, 6, '2010-10-28 15:29:45', '2010-10-28 13:29:45', '<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/jean-michel-basquiat-radiant.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4452" title="jean-michel-basquiat" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/jean-michel-basquiat-radiant.jpg" alt="" width="582" height="200" /></a>Il signait SAMO, pour Same Old Shit.../<span style="color: #808080;">He used to sign SAMO for Same Old Shit...</span>\n\n<strong>Depuis le 15 octobre et jusqu''au 30 janvier 2011, le Muse d''ArtModerne de la Ville de  Paris consacre unevaste rtrospectiveau peintre graffeur new  yorkais,Jean-Michel Basquiat.\n</strong>\n\nN  Brooklyn en 1960, <strong>Jean-Michel Basquiat</strong> aurait eu 50 ans cette anne.\n\nVous pourrez ainsi dcouvrir une centaine de peintures, dessins ou  objets provenant de diffrents muses europens ou amricains.\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><strong>Since october the 15 and till january 30, the Muse d''art moderne de la Ville de Paris (MAM) is diplaying a large retrospectiv of the New Yorker street artist Jean Michel Basquiat.</strong></span>\n\n<span style="color: #808080;">Born in Brooklyn in 1960, <strong>Jean Michel Basquiat</strong> would have been 50 this year. </span>\n\n<span style="color: #808080;">There''s over a hundred paintings, drawing or objects coming from differents europeen or americain museums.</span>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/jean-michel-basquiat-retrospective.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4453" title="jean-michel-basquiat" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/jean-michel-basquiat-retrospective.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="606" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/DSCN7567.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4454" title="expo basquiat" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/DSCN7567.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="480" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/DSCN7560.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4455" title="basquiat" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/DSCN7560.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="480" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/2_-Sans-Titre.1981.Basquiat_Untitled_Ba_21.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4456" title="Basquiat" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/2_-Sans-Titre.1981.Basquiat_Untitled_Ba_21.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="947" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/3_Sans-Titre-1981.md03..jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4457" title="basquiat" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/3_Sans-Titre-1981.md03..jpg" alt="" width="800" height="885" /></a>\n\nPour se faire une ide de ce gnie prolifique, regardez ces vidos\n\n<span style="color: #808080;">To figure you how genius he was, you can check on thoses videos.</span>\n\nLa commissaire de l''exposition, Marie-Sophie Carron de la Carrire,  prsente en exclusivit 4 oeuvres de Basquiat, extraites de la  rtrospective au MAM\n\n<span style="color: #808080;">The Curator of the exhibition, Marie-Sophie Caron de la Carrire, is presenting 4 masterworks of the artist, coming from the retrospective.</span>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="480" height="270" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.dailymotion.com/swf/video/xfaix4_basquiat-sa-vie-en-4-yuvres_creation?additionalInfos=0" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="480" height="270" src