(4469, 4, '2010-10-29 14:30:36', '2010-10-29 12:30:36', '10.29.2010. Week #44. Post 3\n\nWe told you she was back, as fabulous or outrageous she can be I can''t help myself but love the style she posts about.\n\nThis week is black and for <a href="http://www.sophiemhabille.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff00ff;">Sophie Mhabille,</span></a> and quite outrageously back... maybe she had some inspiration from Halloween.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8340-small-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4470" title="img_8340-small-1" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8340-small-1.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="780" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8372-small-small.jpg"></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8372-small-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4471" title="img_8372-small-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8372-small-small.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="780" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8385-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4472" title="img_8385-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_8385-small.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="347" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Sophie on her outfit:</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Je me la joue un peu thtrale, c''est ma tenue qui veut a ! Une petite robe noire trs 80''s avec une pochette et un chapeau en fourrure vintage. Le tout : chez Rtro Chic, 4, Place du Marche Sainte Catherine  Paris.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #999999;"><em>I look a little overrated but that''sonly because ofthe outfit! A little black 80''s dress, a clutchbag and a vintage fur hat. The outfit: Rtro Chic, 4, place du March Sainte Catherine in Paris. </em></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">_________________________________________________</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\nAnd my favorite her street style victim from the past week... NYC ; )\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7211-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4473" title="img_7211-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7211-small.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="780" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7215-small.jpg"></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7215-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4474" title="img_7215-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7215-small.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="347" /></a>\n\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4476" title="img_7219-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7219-small.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="347" /><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7216-small.jpg"></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7216-small.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4475" title="img_7216-small" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/img_7216-small.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="347" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff00ff;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">For more street style shots visit Sophie''s blog at:</span> <a href="http://www.sophiemhabille.com/" target="_blank"><span style="color: #ff00ff;">www.sophiemhabille.com</span></a></strong></span></p>', 'Sophie Mhabille &#039;Black is Back&#039; Street Style', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sophie-mhabille-black-is-back-street-style', '', '', '2010-10-29 14:30:36', '2010-10-29 12:30:36', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4469', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4481, 6, '2010-11-03 18:30:00', '2010-11-03 17:30:00', 'Dans quelques jours, le lancement de notre nouveau site....Nous ne sommes pas peu fiers de vous prsenter les crateurs de talents qui vont rejoindre la boutique en ligne.\n\nAujourd''hui je voudrais vous parler d''<strong>Unsurcinq</strong>. Dniches lors de nos nombreuses promenades virtuelles, nous sommes ravis d''accueillir <strong>Elisa Le Merrer </strong>et<strong> Valrie Le Page</strong>, les cratrices qui se cachent derrire la marque.\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><em>In a few, our new website will be launch. We are pretty damn proud of introducing you the new designers that are going to be feature on the e-shop.</em></span>\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><em>Today, I want to talk about <strong>Unsurcinq</strong>. Digged out during our many virtual promenades, we are welcoming <strong>Elisa Le Merrer </strong>et <strong>Valrie Le Page</strong>, the two designers hidden behind the brand.</em></span>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/0696sansbijou.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4482" title="unsurcinq" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/0696sansbijou.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="216" /></a>\n\nElisa Le Merrer et Valrie Le Page naiment pas les bijoux...Normalement!\n\nElles aiment les dcors et les accessoires.\n\nLes deux comdiennes, formes dans des coles dart dramatique, se connaissent depuis de longues annes. Deux comdiennes et deux amies, laddition est vite pose. Rsultat: 1 sur 5.\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Elisa Le Merrer et Valrie Le Page don''like jewels...Usually.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">They like decors and props.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> The two comedians, both trained in drama schools, know each other from a long time.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Two friends, two actresses - as a result of their addition : 1/5.</span></em>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/dypteddy.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4483" title="unsurcinq" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/dypteddy.jpg" alt="" width="790" height="375" /></a>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="480" height="385" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/9LSa_CUVda4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="480" height="385" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/9LSa_CUVda4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>\n\nDes bijoux imagins par des filles qui nen portaient pas, fabriqus et assembls  la main, en France.\n\nDans lair du temps et intemporels.\n\nRaffins et patins.\n\nOriginaux et quotidiens.\n\nUne collection accessible et pourtant litiste o lon ne trouve jamais plus de cinq modles semblables..\n\nLa marque voit le jour  dbut 2010 dans latelier parisien de ses cratrices, et grandit  toute  allure avec dj 10 points de vente  Paris et 2 en province.\n\nLa collection 2010 a t  conue comme les bijoux de nos grand-mres, et mixe finement  la  touche rock citadine des cratrices. Fines chanes dor vieilli,  mdaillons-souvenir et alliances pendentifs se patinent, se laquent noir  anar ou gris souris... Clyde le voyou, Albert le pote, Eddy le tombeur  : chaque modle sinspire dun artiste ou personnage clbre.\n\nPour les dbuts de leur marque, les unsurcinq, en anciennes tudiantes en thtre, dclament Musset  leur faon.\n\n"Toutes les femmes sont perfides, artificieuses, vaniteuses, curieuses et dpraves"\n\nMais pas seulement.\n\nRomantiques et ludiques\n\nAndrogynes et fminines\n\nFoldingues et virginales\n\nHors-la-loi et sensibles\n\nSauvages et coquettes\n\nLes femmes unsurcinq  multiplient les facettes, les brillances et les zones dombre, empilent  les personnalits, accumulent dorures prcieuses, laitons patins et  punk vieilleries.\n\nCet hiver, la nostalgie se  fera plus industrielle : la prochaine collection quittera les malles de  grenier pour descendre dans lappentis de pp. Aux sautoirs et tours de  cou se joindront bagues et bracelets. De quoi composer des panoplies  fantaisies, assorties... toujours un brin dcales.\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Jewels imagined by girls who didn''t use to wear any, handmade.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Fashionable and timeless.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Refined and patinated.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Original and easy to wear.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">An accessible collection but nevertheless elitist : you will only find "5 items of each pattern".</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> The  brand is born at the beginning of this year in their parisian workroom  and grows at top speed with, at the moment, 9 boutiques in Paris and 5  in "province".</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> </span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">This  year collection has been designed as "our granny''s jewels" and finely  mixed with the urban and trendy touch of the creators. Thin, old golden  chains, opening medallious, pendant wedding rings are either patinated  or lacquered anarchy black, mid grey... Clyde the bandit, Albert the  poet, Eddy the crooner : each model is inspired by an artist or a famous  character.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> The UnsurCinq declaim Musset their own way.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> "All women are perfidious, cunning, vain, curious, depraved"</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">But not only.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Romantic and playful.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Androgyn and feminine.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Crazy and pure.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Outlaw and sensitive.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">Wild and coquettish.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> Females  wearing UnsurCinq multiply facettes of shine and shadow zones, add  different personalities, accumulate precious gilt patinated punk old  fashioned brass.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"> This  winter, nostalgy will be more industrial : the collection will leave  the trunks of the attic to go down to grandad''s penthouse. Rings and  bracelets will be added to necklaces, enough to compose fancy matched  panoplies always inventive...</span></em>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/dypteddy.jpg"></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Meddy1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4484" title="unsurcinq" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Meddy1.jpg" alt="" width="358" height="535" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/alferd.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4485" title="alfred unsurcinq" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/alferd.jpg" alt="" width="357" height="535" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/clyde.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4486" title="clyde" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/clyde.jpg" alt="" width="357" height="535" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/cassius.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4487" title="cassius" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/cassius.jpg" alt="" width="356" height="535" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/eddy-2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4488" title="eddy-2" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/eddy-2.jpg" alt="" width="357" height="535" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/malcom-2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4489" title="malcom-2" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/malcom-2.jpg" alt="" width="354" height="531" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/charlotte.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4490" title="charlotte" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/charlotte.jpg" alt="" width="355" height="532" /></a>', 'Bientt le nouveau site D&#039;ICU-In Paris : voici les nouveaux crateurs! Soon, the new ICU-In Paris website : here are the new designers!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bientot-le-nouveau-site-dicu-in-paris-voici-les-nouveaux-createurs-soon-the-new-icu-in-paris-website-here-are-the-new-designers', '', '', '2010-11-03 18:30:00', '2010-11-03 17:30:00', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4481', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4503, 6, '2010-11-04 20:20:16', '2010-11-04 19:20:16', '<p style="text-align: center;">Aujourd''hui, laissez-moi vous prsenter l''lue de notre cur,</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #808080;"><em>Let me introduce you to our beloved,</em></span></strong></p>\n\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a></h1>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/retouche1-3_copier1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4504" title="charlotte martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/retouche1-3_copier1.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="367" /></a>\n\nAlors d''ordinaire, les jeunes filles pleine de talents, je ne suis pas fan. Nan, c''est vrai, elles sont pnibles  russir comme a... Mais bon, l, force est de constater que cette fille l, wwwhhhoa....., elle est terrible.\n\na faisait un petit moment que la surveillais du coin de l''il et j''tais dj tombe en amour de sa <span style="color: #003300;"><strong>prcdente collection</strong></span>, qui avait tout particulirement touche la renarde que je suis.\n\n<strong><span style="color: #808080;"><em>For usually, I''m not a big fan of talented young girl.. right? they''re such a pain, always successful...blabla. But one has to admit: this girl rocks!</em></span></strong>\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">I have been watching her for quite a while</span></strong></em><strong><span style="color: #808080;"><em> and I was already in love with her <span style="color: #333300;">last collection</span>, that particulary touched my foxy heart.</em></span>\n</strong>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/autres.jpg-1-sur-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4505" title="charlotte martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/autres.jpg-1-sur-1.jpg" alt="" width="633" height="950" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/gold-and-silver-plated-rings.jpg-7-sur-7.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4506" title="charlotte martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/gold-and-silver-plated-rings.jpg-7-sur-7.jpg" alt="" width="950" height="633" /></a>\n\nAprs un petit tour sur son<strong><a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/blog/" target="_blank"> blog</a></strong> , j''avais dcouvert un univers Martin Parresque, du bric  brac gentiment kitsch, des photos romantiques mais pas godiches et surtout un culte aux <span style="color: #333300;"><strong>Cabinets de curiosits</strong></span>. Ce que j''apprcie chez elle, c''est qu''elle aime et respecte les objets, pas seulement pour leur design et leur fonction, mais aussi pour leur me et les histoires qu''ils renferment... Et l...Je ne peux qu''applaudir des deux pattes.\n\nLes cabinets de curiosits+ le fait qu''elle se fasse appeller "Martyr", dj, rien que pour a, je me voyais lui faire parvenir une moiti de <a href="http://www.ykone.com/dressing/article/pendentif" target="_blank">pendentif</a> en cur avec grav "Best Friend Forever"dessus ou un bracelet brsilien...\n\nSa <span style="color: #333300;"><strong>nouvelle collection</strong></span> ne trahit pas son parcours, avec <span style="color: #333300;"><strong><a href="http://www.mademoisellequincampoix.com/2010/08/12/collection-curiosite-mirabilia-charlotte-martyr/" target="_blank">Curiosit&amp;Mirabilia</a></strong></span>, la cratrice lyonnaise nous livre de superbes objets, justement. Son amour des belles pices, de l''artisanat et du bon gout en font une collection de bijoux qui se transmettront de gnrations en gnrations.\n\n<strong><span style="color: #333300;">Bientt sur <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU-In Paris</a></span></strong>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"><strong>I went to see her blog, I discovered her whole personnal universe, Martin Parr-like, a bric--brac kindly rococo, some romantic but not soppies pictures and above all a truly cult devoted to </strong><strong><span style="color: #333300;">Cabinets of curiosities</span>. What I like about the girl is simple: she likes objects, not only for theirs design and their function but also for their "souls" and the stories they contain. I have to say: hats off!</strong></span></em>\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">The Cabinets of curiosities+ the fact that her name is "Martyr", just for those reasons, I was already seeing myself sending her a half of a heart pendant engraved "BFF" or a friendship bracelet...</span></strong></em>\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">Her <span style="color: #333300;"><a href="http://charlottemartyr.bigcartel.com/products" target="_blank">new collection</a></span> is in the continuity, with <span style="color: #333300;"><a href="http://www.mademoisellequincampoix.com/2010/08/12/collection-curiosite-mirabilia-charlotte-martyr/" target="_blank">Curiosit&amp;Mirabilia</a></span>, the young designer from Lyon reveals some stunning objects. Her love for the art&amp;craft and for the good taste make her collection timeless, almost like it''s been in your family for ages.</span></strong></em><strong>\n</strong>\n\n<strong><em><span style="color: #808080;">Soon on <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU-In Paris</a>... in the meantime to see more from Charlotte, check out her <a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/blog/" target="_blank">blog</a> full of creative imagery and videos. </span></em></strong>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/01-864-500x333.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4507" title="charlotte Martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/01-864-500x333.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="333" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/33534_148333965178280_100000050312178_461869_8281293_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4508" title="charlotte martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/33534_148333965178280_100000050312178_461869_8281293_n.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="720" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/39854_148334485178228_100000050312178_461889_5165566_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4509" title="charlotte martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/39854_148334485178228_100000050312178_461889_5165566_n.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="480" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/39802_148333941844949_100000050312178_461863_725159_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4511" title="charlotte martyr" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/39802_148333941844949_100000050312178_461863_725159_n.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="480" /></a><em></em></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Model:Sofia Sanzyprast\nPhotos: Pierre Dal Corso</em></p>', 'Bientt sur le nouveau site D&#039;ICU-In Paris : Charlotte Martyr.', 'Bientt sur le nouveau site D''ICU-In Paris : Charlotte Martyr.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bientot-sur-le-nouveau-site-dicu-in-paris-charlotte-martyr', '', '', '2010-11-04 20:20:16', '2010-11-04 19:20:16', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4503', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4522, 7, '2010-11-11 17:59:51', '2010-11-11 16:59:51', '10.29.2010. Week #46. Post 1\n\nLast week, we introduced you to some of the newest ICU-in Paris featured Designers: <strong><a title="unsurcinq website" href="http://www.unsurcinq.com/unsurcinq/Un_sur_cinq%3A_homepage.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq</a></strong><strong>, <a title="Charlotte Martyr Website" href="http://www.charlottemartyr.bigcartel.com/" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a></strong><strong>, <a title="Bena website" href="http://bena.bigcartel.com/" target="_blank">Bena</a>, </strong><strong><a href="http://vernetlaurene.blogspot.com/2010/05/blog-post.html" target="_blank">Laurene Vernet</a></strong><strong>...</strong> this week, shooting at LightKitchen Studios with <a href="http://www.christiangeisselmann.com/" target="_blank">Christian Geisselmann</a>.\n\nNot bad, not bad.... and here a little sneak into whats shakin in Paris.\n\n[gallery link="file"]\n\n<strong>\n</strong>', 'ICU Photoshoot. Christian Geisselmann. Light Kitchen Studios Paris.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'icu-photoshoot-christian-geisselmann', '', '', '2010-11-11 17:59:51', '2010-11-11 16:59:51', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4522', 0, 'post', '', 3),
(4560, 6, '2010-11-16 16:38:59', '2010-11-16 15:38:59', '"Le premier concours de stylisme sur Internet" lance  sa premire EDITION BIJOUX en partenariat avec The Box, l''univers  Accessoires et bijoux du Salon du Prt  Porter de Paris.\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">The first design contest on the net is launching its first JEWEL EDITION brought to you by The BOX, from the Salon du Prt  Porter de Paris.</span></em>\n\nAprs une premire slection de 10 nomins par le Jury du concours, les candidats sont soumis aux votes des internautes. Celle  qui remportera le plus de voix, se verra attribuer un stand sur le  Salon du Prt  Porter de Paris en janvier 2011.\n\nLa collection du Laurat sera distribue en exclusivit sur <a href="http://www.atelierdelamode.com/" target="_blank">l''atelier de la mode</a>.\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">After a first selection of ten nominated by the contest Jury, the candidates are submitted to the internet users ''s vote. The most successful candidate will win a booth on the fashion fair le "Salon du Prt  Porter de Paris" in january 2011.</span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;">THe collection of the winner will be sold on the </span></em><a href="http://www.atelierdelamode.com/" target="_blank">l''atelier de la mode</a>.\n<h3>A ICU, nous sommes ravis, car deux de nos cratrices chouchoutes sont slectionnes: <a href="http://www.coraliedeseynes.com/" target="_blank">Coralie de Seynes </a>et <a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/blog/" target="_blank"><strong></strong>Charlotte Martyr</a></h3>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Sautoir-Rne-Bracelet-Mors-sur-mannequin.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4563" title="coralie de seynes" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Sautoir-Rne-Bracelet-Mors-sur-mannequin.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="737" /> </a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/retouche1-3-800x533.jpg"><img clas