(4666, 6, '2010-12-07 18:08:45', '2010-12-07 17:08:45', 'Il est temps de vous prsenter le showroom<strong> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100001719014453" target="_blank">La Cour</a></strong> avec lequel nous collaborons depuis peu...\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">It''s about time to present you the parisian showroom <span style="color: #333333;">La Cour</span> with which we collaborate recently...</span></strong></em>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/71723_123336671057253_122873284436925_164785_6107812_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4669" title="la cour" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/71723_123336671057253_122873284436925_164785_6107812_n.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="470" /></a>\n\nCest un nouvel espace showroom qui promeut des crateurs et   artistes indpendants, comme nous, tout pareil! videmment on aime, videmment on y va!\n\nEn ce moment, que du lourd : <a href="http://gaelleconstantini.bigcartel.com/" target="_blank">Gaelle  Constantini</a>, <a href="http://warmi.fr/" target="_blank">Warmi</a>, <a href="http://www.morgane-et-salome-creations.fr/" target="_blank">Morgane &amp; Salom</a>, <a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a>, <a href="http://www.unapresmididechien.fr/" target="_blank">un  aprs-midi de chien</a>\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">It''s a brand new showroom, that promote young designers and independant artists. Just like us! Of course, we like it, of course, we''re going!</span></strong></em>\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">On display now, check it out: <a href="http://gaelleconstantini.bigcartel.com/" target="_blank">Gaelle  Constantini</a>, <a href="http://warmi.fr/" target="_blank">Warmi</a>, <a href="http://www.morgane-et-salome-creations.fr/" target="_blank">Morgane &amp; Salom</a>, <a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a>, <a href="http://www.unapresmididechien.fr/" target="_blank">un  aprs-midi de chien</a></span></strong></em>\n\n<a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/"><strong>Charlotte  Martyr</strong></a>,  jewellery designer, et le collectif/webzine Blackzlem y ont organis une  soire le 3 dcembre dernier afin de nous prsenter leur collaboration:\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><strong><em><a href="http://charlottemartyr.com/"><strong>Charlotte  Martyr</strong></a>,  jewellery designer and the collectif/webzine Blackzlem just organized a party last friday to present their collaboration:</em></strong></span>\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Visions of Fear</h1>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://s753.photobucket.com/albums/xx176/noiretexture/?action=view&amp;current=croix-gif.gif" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://i753.photobucket.com/albums/xx176/noiretexture/croix-gif.gif" border="0" alt="Photobucket" width="500" height="500" /></a></p>\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-20" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?attachment_id=20">\n</a>\n\nVisions  of Fear est une collection de  bijoux et daccessoires inspire des  instincts bestiaux et complexes de  ltre humain, des terreurs nocturnes  et du film de Wes Craven , Les  Griffes de la nuit.\n\nPour l''occasion, le showroom s''est vu transform:\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"><strong>Visions of Fear is a collection of jewellery and accessories inspired from the bestial and elaborate instincts of humanity and nightmare fears of Wes Craven''s movie: A Nightmare on Elm Street.</strong></span></em>\n\n<em><span style="color: #808080;"><strong>For the occasion, the showroom has been transformed:</strong></span></em>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/154377_181618001849876_100000050312178_667491_5807392_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4670" title="la cour" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/154377_181618001849876_100000050312178_667491_5807392_n.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="577" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/154871_181618431849833_100000050312178_667495_2045366_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4671" title="la cour" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/154871_181618431849833_100000050312178_667495_2045366_n.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="540" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/155210_181618238516519_100000050312178_667492_7533388_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4672" title="la cour" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/155210_181618238516519_100000050312178_667492_7533388_n.jpg" alt="" width="502" height="720" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/47632_181619285183081_100000050312178_667507_2021215_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4673" title="la cour" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/47632_181619285183081_100000050312178_667507_2021215_n.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="540" /></a>crdits photos:Blackzlem\n\nCharlotte  Martyr et Blackzlem ont accueillis leurs amis <strong><a href="http://www.myspace.com/solpornblues">Sol</a></strong><a href="http://www.myspace.com/solpornblues"> <strong>&amp;</strong> </a><strong><a href="http://julienlangendorff.com/">Julien Langendorff</a></strong> pour un concert acoustique shoegaze/folk/lo fi, ainsi que  lquipe du magazine<strong><a href="http://www.viceland.com/fr/"><strong> Vice</strong></a></strong> aux platines.\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong>Charlotte  Martyr and Blackzlem hosted their friends <strong><a href="http://www.myspace.com/solpornblues">Sol</a></strong><a href="http://www.myspace.com/solpornblues"> <strong>&amp;</strong> </a><strong><a href="http://julienlangendorff.com/">Julien Langendorff</a></strong> for a shoegaze/folk/lo fi, acoustic concert and<strong><a href="http://www.viceland.com/fr/"><strong> Vice</strong></a></strong> magazine for a DJ set.</strong></em></span>', 'La Cour X Charlotte Martyr X Blackzlem = Rocking party!', 'It''s about time to present you the parisian showroom La Cour with which we collaborate recently...', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'la-courxcharlotte-martyrxblackozlem-rocking-party', '', '', '2010-12-07 18:08:45', '2010-12-07 17:08:45', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4666', 0, 'post', '', 0),
