(4718, 6, '2010-12-14 15:37:22', '2010-12-14 14:37:22', '<h1 style="text-align: center;">Take Me Out</h1>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="TAke me out" src="http://www.clarkmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/33717_444816908653_555398653_5103212_1348798_n-380x268.jpg" alt="" width="380" height="268" /></p>\n<a href="http://takemeout.fr/"><strong>TAKE ME OUT</strong></a>, un salon qui depuis un an su se dmarquer par un mix percutant "so 2010" de mode, d''art et de musique, prpare une dition de nol les <strong>18 et 19 dcembre 2010</strong>.\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong> </strong></em></span><strong><a href="http://takemeout.fr/"><strong>TAKE ME OUT</strong></a> </strong><span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong>is a fair trade that knows how to mix effictively fashion, art and music. Don''t miss the Christmas special edition, the <span style="color: #333333;">18 and 19 of december.</span></strong></em></span>\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">UN PROGRAMME QUI PROMET/<span style="color: #808080;">A PROMISING PROGRAMME</span>:</h2>\n<a href="http://takemeout.fr/"><strong>TAKE ME OUT,</strong></a><strong> </strong>cest 50 crateurs dont <a href="http://www.andreacrews.com/"><strong>Andrea Crews</strong></a> ou <strong><a href="http://www.leslie-david.com/">Leslie David</a></strong>; les concerts des groupes de pop rock de <a href="http://www.theparisians.com/"><strong>The Parisians</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.cqfd.com/evergreen/"><strong>We were evergreen</strong></a>, et <a href="http://moonengineer.com/"><strong>Moonengineer</strong></a>; les dfils de<strong> Is Not Dead</strong> et <strong>Les N.A.I.S.</strong> et des djs comme <strong>Les chats Perchs</strong> et <strong>Pain O Chokolat</strong>.... plus une expo photo et d''autres surprises comme les tattoos de <strong>Inker tattoo</strong>.\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong><strong><a href="http://takemeout.fr/"><strong>TAKE ME OUT</strong></a>,</strong>It''s 50 designers, <a href="http://www.andreacrews.com/"><strong>Andrea Crews</strong></a> or <strong><a href="http://www.leslie-david.com/">Leslie David</a> </strong> among others; concerts of groups like <a href="http://www.theparisians.com/"><strong>The Parisians</strong></a> , <strong><a href="http://www.cqfd.com/evergreen/"><strong>We were evergreen</strong></a></strong><strong><a href="http://moonengineer.com/"><strong>Moonengineer</strong></a></strong> ; catwalks from<span style="color: #333333;"> <strong> Is Not Dead </strong></span>and <span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Les N.A.I.S.</strong></span> and Djs like <span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Les chats Perchs</strong></span> and<span style="color: #333333;"> <strong>Pain O Chokolat</strong></span>.... plus one photo exhibit and other surprises</strong></em></span> <span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong>like the tattoos of </strong></em></span><em><strong>Inker tattoo</strong>.</em>\n<h2>Take me out or be square!</h2>\n<a href="http://takemeout.fr/"><strong>TAKE ME OUT</strong></a> samedi 18 et dimanche 19 dcembre - 3 et 5 ds 15h\n<a href="http://www.letrianon.fr/"><strong>Le Trianon</strong></a> - 80 Bl. Rochechouart 75018 Paris', 'Take me out!', 'TAKE ME OUT, un salon qui depuis un an su se dmarquer par un mix  percutant "so 2010" de mode, d''art et de musique, prpare une dition de nol les 18 et 19 dcembre 2010.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'take-me-out', '', '', '2010-12-14 15:37:22', '2010-12-14 14:37:22', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4718', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(4724, 6, '2010-12-22 12:10:59', '2010-12-22 11:10:59', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU-in Paris</a> est fier de vous prsenter sa nouvelle recrue :</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #808080;"><em><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU in Paris</a></em><em> is proud to present :</em></span></strong></p>\n\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Laurent_Desgrange_logo.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4725" title="Laurent_Desgrange_logo" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Laurent_Desgrange_logo.jpg" alt="" width="439" height="142" /></a></h1>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/biopic.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4726" title="laurent desgrange" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/biopic.jpg" alt="" width="193" height="244" /></a>\n\nLe jeune styliste peut se vanter d''avoir le vent en poupe, les boutiques les plus branches s''arrachent ses crations, en France et  l''international. Laurent nous fait l''honneur de participer  l''aventure <strong>ICU- in Paris</strong>, retrouvez ds  prsent ses clbres nuds et Tee-shirts sur notre site. C''est par<span style="color: #333300;"><strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/advanced/result/?name=&amp;description=&amp;short_description=&amp;sku=&amp;price[from]=&amp;price[to]=&amp;designer[]=67" target="_blank">ici</a></strong></span>!\n\nLaurent sort du renomm <strong>Studio Berot</strong>, il commence sa carrire chez <a href="http://www.ykone.com/marques/article/thierry-mugler" target="_blank"><strong>Thierry Mugler</strong> </a>en tant que styliste maroquinerie&amp;accessoires pendant trois ans. Aprs avoir lanc sa marque en 2006, le succs est immdiat: il remporte le concours Myspace Boudoir et se voit offrir de nombreuses opportunits.\n\nIl commence sa carrire avec l''accessoire qui va faire sa renomme: le Nud Pap''. Il le rinvente vritablement, lui fait perdre son ct kitsch "mariage de Tonton en 79" et lui confre un genre dfinitivement Hype... La crme de la crme du Papillon:\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><strong><em>The young Fashion designer is on the crest, the hypest shops are fighting to get his design,in France, but also international. Laurent chooses <span style="color: #333333;">ICU</span>! To find his tee-shirts and bows, it''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/advanced/result/?name=&amp;description=&amp;short_description=&amp;sku=&amp;price[from]=&amp;price[to]=&amp;designer[]=67" target="_blank">here</a>!</em></strong></span>\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><strong><em>He studied fashion at the renowned <span style="color: #333333;">Studio Berot</span>. After 3 years at <span style="color: #333333;">Thierry Mugler</span>, designing leather goods and accessories, he launched his own ready to wear brand in 2006 and won first prize in the Myspacecontest that opened many doors to his brand, such as the famous and renowned tradeshows Whos Next and Prt  Porter Paris.</em></strong></span>\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><strong><em>He began his career with the accessory that makes his reputation, the bow tie. He is reinventing it completely, make it loose its kitsch side, and confer it a definitely hype side: the crme de la crme of the bow tie!</em></strong></span>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/look-book-standing-collection2011.jpg"></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Laurent_Desgrange_PDF-1.pdf-Adobe-Reader.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4728" title="Laurent_Desgrange_" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/Laurent_Desgrange_PDF-1.pdf-Adobe-Reader.jpg" alt="" width="824" height="774" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/men.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4729" title="men" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/men.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="450" /></a>\n\nMais Laurent Desgrange c''est aussi un artiste. Passionn par le travail de collage, il mlange avec dlice des figures de l''hraldique, des symboles sotriques, des gravures anciennes et des images de publicit. Son univers surraliste ainsi cre, il le transpose sur des tee-shirts, srigraphis et imprims artisanalement  Paris, peints  la main dans son atelier.\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong>But Laurent Desgrange is also an artist. He''s passionated about collage : he''s mixing heraldic and esoteric symbols with ancient engravering and advertising images. You can find his surrealist''s world on tee-shirts, screen printed and hand painted in his atelier in Paris.</strong></em></span>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/cover4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4730" title="lauren desgrange" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/cover4.jpg" alt="" width="317" height="450" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/illusup01.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4731" title="laurent desgrange" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/illusup01.jpg" alt="" width="440" height="450" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/laurent-desgrange-icuinparis.jpg"></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/laurent-desgrange-icuinparis.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4732" title="laurent desgrange icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/laurent-desgrange-icuinparis-285x300.jpg" alt="" width="285" height="300" /></a>\n\nSon style mlange avec subtilit urbanisme et dandysme, chic et pop. Cerise sur le gteau: il pense la mode en <strong>unisexe</strong>... Alors, WELCOME LAURENT!\n\n<strong><em><span style="color: #808080;">His style is mixing urbanism and dandysm, chic and pop. Lucky for us, his fashion is <span style="color: #333333;">unisexe</span>... WELCOME LAURENT!</span></em></strong>', 'Please Welcome Laurent Desgrange!', 'laurent desgrange', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'please-welcome-laurent-desgrange', '', '', '2010-12-22 12:10:59', '2010-12-22 11:10:59', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4724', 0, 'post', '', 0);
