(4833, 6, '2011-02-05 00:02:40', '2011-02-04 23:02:40', '<span style="color: #808080;"><em><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal;">Last week, our visits to the Paris salons...</span></span><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/28491348251.jpg">\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4836" title="2849134825" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/28491348251.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="480" /></a></strong></em></span>\n\n<em><strong> </strong></em>\n\nEn premier lieu, nous avons rejoint <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies.html?designer=30&amp;limit=12" target="_blank"><strong>Coralie de Seynes</strong></a>, l''heureuse gagnante du Concours de style de <strong>l''Atelier de la mode</strong> (voir <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2010/12/08/and-the-winner-is/" target="_blank">ici</a>)  "<strong>The Box</strong>" o elle avait gagn un stand et prsentait sa nouvelle collection:\n\n<em><strong><span style="color: #808080;">First, we went to see <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies.html?designer=30&amp;limit=12" target="_blank"><strong>Coralie de Seynes</strong></a>, who won the <span style="color: #333333;"><strong>Atelier de la mode</strong></span> (see t<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2010/12/08/and-the-winner-is/" target="_blank">his post</a>) contest, at "<span style="color: #333333;"><strong>The Box</strong></span>", where she had a booth and presented her new collection:</span></strong></em>\n\nAprs un petit tour au Salon du <strong>PAP </strong>et au <strong>WSN</strong>, une fois n''est pas coutume, nous sommes alles nous promener au <strong>Mess around</strong>, au <strong>Be street Ice shop</strong>, pour tre plus prcises, pour y retrouver une de nos chouchoute... <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=charlotte+martyr" target="_blank"><strong>Charlotte Martyr</strong></a>!\n\n<span style="color: #808080;"><strong><e