(4892, 4, '2011-02-11 19:01:32', '2011-02-11 18:01:32', 'For apart of the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com">ICU - IN PARIS</a> creative profile video series, we sat down with photographer, Christian Geisselmann for an exclusive insider view on what makes this creative mind tick.<br/>\nOriginally from Bavaria in the southeast of Germany, Christian re-located to Paris with the goal to make his passion his career. Now, 14 years later Christian not only has co-opened a studio in Paris called Light Kitchen Studios (www.lightkitchenstudio.net), but also created a name for himself in the one of the toughest fashion capitals of the world.<br/>\nHaving shot for fashion publications such as; Cosmopolitan, Vogue, Marie Claire, Muteen &amp; many others we were ecstatic to sit down with Christian at the end of 2010 for this interview - not to mention shooting with him for the last two ICU catalogues!Needless to say, there is a lot more to come, a lot more images to create and cities to be inspired by.<br/>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p align="center">\n<iframe title="YouTube video player" width="640" height="510" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/JmJVUnmdmc4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n\n<div style="text-align: center;"><strong>A film by, Laetitia Gadan</strong></div>\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="text-align: center;">Special thanks, Christian Geisselmann &amp; Light Kitchen Studios</div>\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.christiangeisselmann.com/" target="_blank">http://www.christiangeisselmann.com/</a></div>\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.lightkitchen.net/" target="_blank">http://www.lightkitchen.net/</a></div>\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">http://www.icuinparis.com/</a></div>\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="text-align: center;">An ICU - IN PARIS production</div>\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="text-align: center;"> 2010 ICU - IN PARIS all rights reserved.</div>', 'ICU Exclusive Interview with Christian Geisselmann', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'icu-exclusive-interview-with-christian-geisselmann', '', '', '2011-02-11 19:01:32', '2011-02-11 18:01:32', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=4892', 0, 'post', '', 0);
