(5048, 4, '2011-03-07 18:11:37', '2011-03-07 17:11:37', 'It''s hard to deny the absolute beauty and creation that walk the streets during Paris Fashion Week. Between the shapes, layers, colors, patterns, textures... c''est absolument magnifique.\n\nFor <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_self">ICU</a>, Fashion Week is about the art of expression - your expression - your creativity - your unique style.\n\nBelow, the first look into our collaborationwith photographer <a href="http://www.facebook.com/christiangeisselmann" target="_blank">Christian Geisselmann</a> to find, snap &amp; love a snippet of 2011''s Paris Fashion Week''s Street Style.\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Paris-fashion-week-street-style 2011" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Paris-fashion-week-street-style7-682x1024.jpg" alt="Paris-fashion-week-street-style 2011" width="546" height="819" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Kenneth</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Fashion Editor, BAZAAR</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Singapore</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Paris-fashion-week-street-style36.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5086" title="Paris-fashion-week-street-style" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Paris-fashion-week-street-style36.jpg" alt="Paris-fashion-week-street-style 2011" width="648" height="433" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Paris-fashion-week-street-style34.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5085" title="Paris-fashion-week-street-style 2011" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Paris-fashion-week-street-style34-682x1024.jpg" alt="Paris-fashion-week-street-style 2