(5155, 8, '2011-03-23 23:09:15', '2011-03-23 22:09:15', 'For <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> very first Style Profile, we sat down with Laura G over carrot cake and pair juice, to discuss her style philosophy and ICU faves. Below is a sweet, bite-sized sample for you to chew on, just as sweet as the delectable bites we sampled at Sugarplum Cake Shop. To hear all the rest of what charms this charming flower darling watch the video!\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/homepage-style-profile-laura-g.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5169" title="homepage-style-profile-laura-g" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/homepage-style-profile-laura-g.jpg" alt="" width="598" height="294" /></a></p>\n<strong>From:</strong> Perth, Australia. The west side: the better side.\n\n<strong>Age:</strong> 24\n\n<strong>Job:</strong> I work in Fashion Forecasting, currently working on some designs for children and also illustrations.\n\n<strong>Favorite Parishangout:</strong> Sugarplum Cake Shop, 68 rue du Cardinal Lemoine.\n\n<strong>Your style:</strong> I have an extreme affinity for things that are flowery or sparkly, or have something about them that reminds me of floral parks and summer days.\n\n<strong>ICU picks:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Flower Mirror Brooch</a> (in gold and silver), <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-tea-cup-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Gold Mirror Tea Cup Brooch</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-necklace-albert.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq Albert Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-lucien.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq Lucien Bracelet</a>.\n\n<strong>Why?</strong> The Bena brooches, I think they''re just big and beautiful and I could put them with anything. The little necklace obviously have to choose cause it''s just so adorably sweet. The bracelet is beautiful cause it''s really delicate, really simple.\n\n<strong>Why shop independent design?</strong> Because it''s really nice to have something that you know somebody put time into, and that you know other people aren''t going to be wearing. If you have something a bit more special you''ve got a bit more of a connection to it and you''re a bit more proud to wear it.\n\nTo cop Laura''s look go after her ICU favorites and explore other treasures on the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU </a>site!\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><iframe width="560" height="345" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/MOBrlYcpcD0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-lucien.html">\n</a>\n\nCheck out Laura''s ICU jewelry picks from the video!\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">BENA Gold Flower Brooch</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5178" title="bena gold flower mirror brooch" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch-682x1024.jpg" alt="bena gold flower mirror brooch" width="491" height="737" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/bena-flower-necklace.html" target="_blank">BENA Etched Wood Flower Necklace</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/bena-flower-necklace.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5183" title="bena flower necklace etched wood necklace, icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/bena-flower-necklace-etched-wood-necklace-icuinparis-682x1024.jpg" alt="bena flower necklace etched wood necklace, icuinparis" width="477" height="717" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/bena-silver-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">BENA Silver Flower Brooch</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/bena-silver-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5179" title="bena silver flower pin" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/bena-silver-flower-pin-682x1024.jpg" alt="bena silver flower pin" width="477" height="717" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/unsurcinq-bracelet-hugh.html" target="_blank">UNSURCINQ Hugh Bracelet</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/unsurcinq-bracelet-hugh.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5182" title="unsurcinq charlotte bracelet, icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/unsurcinq-charlotte-bracelet-icuinparis-558x1024.jpg" alt="unsurcinq charlotte bracelet, icuinparis" width="446" height="819" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/unsurcinq-necklace-albert.html" target="_blank">UNSURCINQ Albert Necklace</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/unsurcinq-necklace-albert.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5181" title="albert nkl blue, unsurcinq, icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/albert-nkl-blue-unsurcinq-icuinparis.jpg" alt="albert nkl blue, unsurcinq, icuinparis" width="517" height="917" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">All jewelry available on:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', 'Paris Style Profile with Laura G: the Flower Darling', 'Paris style profile, icuinparis profiles Laura for her creative and flower loving style. Bena brooches and unsurcinq parisian designs take the cake for the style profile rendez-vous.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-style-profile-with-laura-g-the-flower-darling', '', '', '2011-03-23 23:09:15', '2011-03-23 22:09:15', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5155', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(5187, 8, '2011-03-25 17:06:26', '2011-03-25 16:06:26', 'With a beautiful and sunny week now behind us here in Paris, it''s time to start thinking about the weekend. The good news is there''s only more sun to enjoy! Check outICU''s styling tips to maximize your Parisian Springtime looks.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5198" title="paris style, street style in paris, icuinparis.com, icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Saturday-Greys1-851x1024.jpg" alt="Parisian springtime style " width="596" height="717" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Saturday-Greys.jpg">\n</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Partly cloudy and 17 degrees (that''s 62 for those of you in fahrenheit), means you can finally break out that mid-weight leather jacket you''ve been waiting to wear all winter. Mix it with a palette of off-greys and gunmetal, from a textured skirt to glittery nails, perfect to accent with the standout <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ladies/necklaces/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Ginger Necklace</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-caroline-ring.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5199" title="paris style, street style in paris, icuinparis.com, icuinparis" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Sunday-Monochrome2-1024x991.jpg" alt="Parisian Springtime Style" width="641" height="620" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Sunday-Monochrome1.jpg">\n</a>For Sunday brunch under the sun with your girlfriends, dip your toes into spring''s monochrome trend. 15 degrees (59 fahrenheit), means it''s time for your favorite white tee to come out of hiding. Layer it with a mix of saffron spiced pieces: all the way from caramel wedges, marigold carryall and dip-dyed socks, to a tangerine pout. Finish the look with some golden treasure with the<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-caroline-ring.html">Caroline Ring from Charlotte Martyr</a>.</p>\nSaturday''s look: nail polish Estee Lauder, skirt Mikkat Market, jacket Bottega Veneta, boots Forever21, Fiona Paxton necklace <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/">ICU-IN PARIS</a>.\n\nSunday''s look: shirt The Row, boots Zara, bag Baggu, socks Mikkat Market, lipstick Shiseido, Charlotte Martyr ring <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/">ICU-IN PARIS.</a>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'With a beautiful and sunny week now behind us here in Paris, it''s time to start thinking about the weekend forecast.  The good news is there''s only more sun to enjoy! Here''s how you can bring ICU-IN PARIS favorites Fiona Paxton and Charlotte Martyr, along with you for all the accessory fun...', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast', '', '', '2011-03-25 17:06:26', '2011-03-25 16:06:26', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5187', 0, 'post', '', 0),
