accessory respite.  Each Monday, ICU founder Christan Summers gives you her favorite item of the week, in order to help beat those Monday blues by offering you a little morsel of style inspiration.  Lately, Christan can''t seem to take off Unsurcinq''s Albert Necklace.  Why?  Good question!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'christans-pick-of-the-week', '', '', '2011-03-28 23:19:19', '2011-03-28 21:19:19', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5233', 0, 'post', '', 0),
