(5301, 8, '2011-04-03 21:31:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Last Monday, ICU founder Christan gave you her <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/28/christans-pick-of-the-week/" target="_blank">pick of the week</a> and told you why she can''t stop wearing Unsurcinq''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-necklace-albert.html" target="_blank">Albert Necklace</a>. Now, one week later, see what she''s wearing it with.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/DSCN0721.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5302" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/DSCN0721-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="484" height="645" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">How would you wear it?</p>', 'Christan + Albert = Love', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2011-04-03 21:31:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5301', 0, 'post', '', 0),
