(5326, 8, '2011-03-31 12:27:07', '2011-03-31 10:27:07', 'You already know the jewelry we love, now get to know what else we love. From time to time we like to turn the cameras around and give you a sneak peak at what ICU is wearing. Check out Ariane, happily shedding winter layers in favor of some crimson silk and spotted pony hair flats. A lover of all things gold, she mixes her grandmother''s necklace with Charlotte Martyr''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/jay-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Jay</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-caroline-ring.html" target="_blank">Caroline</a> rings, and her favorite street-purchased ghetto gold hoops.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5328" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/U-C-ICU-Ariane-1-680x1024.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="737" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5339" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/U-C-ICU-Ariane-3-680x1024.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="737" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Ariane, Media Relations &amp; Design at ICU-IN PARIS.</p>', 'You See ICU', 'You already know the jewelry we love, now get to know what else we love.  From time to time we like to turn the cameras around and give you a sneak peak at what ICU is wearing.  Check out Ariane, happily shedding winter layers in favor of some crimson silk and spotted pony hair flats.  A lover of all things gold, she mixes her grandmother''s necklace with Charlotte Martyr''s Jay and Caroline rings, and her favorite street-purchased ghetto gold hoops.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'you-see-icu', '', '', '2011-03-31 12:27:07', '2011-03-31 10:27:07', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5326', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5357, 8, '2011-04-01 11:28:27', '2011-04-01 09:28:27', 'Here at ICU we look for inspiration in every nook and cranny, and find that the greatest inspiration comes from you! We like to see what you fall in love with, what you''re wearing, and how you wear it. We want to pay homage to those of you that inspire us, to say thanks for making our sartorial heart skip a beat and get our creative juices flowing.\n\nSo, in the first entry of many, we share with you our muse of the week: the always chic and never predictable Jane Aldridge of <a href="http://seaofshoes.typepad.com/" target="_blank">Sea of Shoes</a>. Her eclectic mixes of vintage and designer, and her lighthearted sense of whimsy have captured our hearts and eyes, and inspired us to imagine our ICU pieces floating happily in a Sea of Shoes.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://seaofshoes.typepad.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5374" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/seas-of-shoes-banner-1024x408.jpg" alt="" width="659" height="262" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5359" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/sea-of-shoes-boho-look-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">For a beautifully sunlit boho safari, a single stunning necklace is all you need to complement a flowing cream blouse and loose french braids. <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-18k-gold-and-silver-bead-necklace.html" target="_blank">ebb.and.pflow Polished Silver Pearl Necklace.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5372" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/blank.jpg" alt="" width="756" height="50" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5360" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/sea-of-shoes-treasure-trove-1024x743.jpg" alt="" width="652" height="472" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">We love how Jane piles layers of eclectic gold over a simple palette of neutrals. Drip yourself in gold with a mix of classic and elegant chains with quirky pendants and bold bracelets.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Charlotte Martyr <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-vlady-rabbit-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gold Vlady Rabbit Necklace</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Bracelet</a>, Noot <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html" target="_blank">Wing Necklace</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Gold Bangle Bracelets</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-hugh.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq Hugh Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/pear-rose-gold-necklace.html" target="_blank">Tracy Matthews Rose Gold Pear Necklace</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5372" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/blank-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="824" height="54" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5361" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/seas-of-shoes-sweetness-1024x747.jpg" alt="" width="659" height="481" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">A sweet fifties inspired party look is perfectly paired with a single delicate necklace and fun, girly bow in the hair.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-toile-de-jouy-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange Toile De Jouy Bow</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-necklace-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Knot Necklace</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5372" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/blank.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="45" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Thank you <a href="http://seaofshoes.typepad.com/" target="_blank">Sea of Shoes</a>!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', 'Blogger of the Week', 'So, in the first entry of many, we share with you our muse of the week: the always chic and never predictable Jane Aldridge of Sea of Shoes.  Her eclectic mixes of vintage and designer, and her lighthearted sense of whimsy have captured our hearts and eyes, and inspired us to imagine our ICU pieces floating happily in a Sea of Shoes.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week', '', '', '2011-04-01 11:28:27', '2011-04-01 09:28:27', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5357', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5382, 8, '2011-04-01 19:36:53', '2011-04-01 17:36:53', 'Weekend is on the brain once again, and ICU is here to make sure you get through Saturday and Sunday looking just as fab and fashionable as you feel. Follow our tips below to let ICU''s accessories accompany you through another Parisian weekend.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Saturday-april2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5385" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Saturday-april2-1024x1020.jpg" alt="" width="577" height="574" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">After a grey and rainy few days it''s time to kick off the weekend with tons of sun and a whopping 23 degrees (73fahrenheit). Accent a long and flirty blush colored skirt with a perfect white tank, fun flats and a rosey-pink pout. Tie the look up in a bow with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Silver Knot Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-tahitian-turquoise-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange''s Tahitian Turquoise Bow</a>.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Sunday-april3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5386" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Sunday-april3-1007x1024.jpg" alt="" width="577" height="586" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Rain, rain go away, and if you must come again another day please bring us some light turquoise wellies and a coral accented umbrella. Keep the look simple with a dip-dyed poncho, skinny jeans, and a cozy crochet hat. Even though it''s raining, keep Springtime close to your heart with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-flower-necklace.html" target="_blank">Bena''s Flower Necklace</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Saturday''s Look: tank American Vintage, skirt The Row, <a href="http://warmi.fr/" target="_blank">shoes Warmi</a>, lipstick Estee Lauder, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-tahitian-turquoise-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange Bow ICU-IN PARIS</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot Ring ICU-IN PARIS</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Sunday''s Look: top Mikkat Market, jeans Levis, boots Tretorn, umbrella Urban Outfitters, hat Ariane Haas, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-flower-necklace.html" target="_blank">Bena Necklace ICU-IN PARIS</a>.</p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'Weekend is on the brain once again, and ICU is here to make sure you get through Saturday and Sunday looking just as fab and fashionable as you feel.  Follow our tips below to let ICU''s accessories accompany you through another Parisian weekend.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-2', '', '', '2011-04-01 19:36:53', '2011-04-01 17:36:53', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5382', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(5398, 4, '2011-04-01 17:02:29', '2011-04-01 15:02:29', 'ICU - IN PARIS recently took our camera to the streets to ask one question: how does Noot''s eyelash necklace inspired you? (view photos <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/30/street-style-eyelash-play/" target="_blank">here</a>)\n\nNow its time to hear from the designer herself how she was inspired to create the necklace the streets of Paris are falling head over heels for.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/noot_icu_gold_eyelash_necklace_03-2.jpg"><img src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/noot_icu_gold_eyelash_necklace_03-2.jpg" alt="Noot Eyelash Necklace" title="noot_icu_gold_eyelash_necklace_03-2" width="700" height="525" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5410" /></a>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p><p align="center"><iframe title="YouTube video player" width="640" height="390" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/7abTM70_k80" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">Shop the Noot Eyelash Necklace in the <a title="noot eyelash necklace" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">ICU - IN PARIS Online Boutique</a></p>\n&nbsp;', 'A Designer&#039;s Inspiration: Noot Bijoux Eyelash Necklace', 'ICU - IN PARIS recently took our camera to the streets to ask one questions: how does Noot''s eyelash necklace inspired you? Now its time to hear from the designer herself how she was inspired to create the necklace the streets of Paris of falling head over heels for.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-designers-inspiration-noot-bijoux-eyelash-necklace', '', '', '2011-04-01 17:02:29', '2011-04-01 15:02:29', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5398', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5414, 8, '2011-04-06 14:48:05', '2011-04-06 12:48:05', 'After two full days spent at <a href="http://www.lightkitchen.net/" target="_blank">Lightkitchen Studio</a> with photographer <a href="http://christiangeisselmann.com/" target="_blank">Christian Geisselmann</a>, the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU</a> team is basking in the post-photoshoot glow. The months of forecasting, searching and successfully finding paid off after the ICU team chose the top 7 independent designers for this 2011 summer style. The looks were outstanding (merci  La Cour pour tous les vetments!), hair and makeup by<a href="http://kazukokitaoka.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Kazuko Kitaoka</a> and<a href="http://mayumiodamake-up.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Mayumi ODA</a> was superb as usual andphotography by <a href="http://www.christiangeisselmann.com" target="_blank">Christian Geisselmann</a> to its creative finest... all under the guidance of our fearless leader - and part time superhero - <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/31/find-out-more-about-christan-summers-icu-founder/" target="_blank">Christan Summers.</a>\n\nNow it''s time to let our hair down, kick our heels up, and revel in the amazing results... which we will share in the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">boutique</a> soon. Here''s a behind the scenes glimpse of what went down and what <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> has in store for you this summer.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8545.jpg">\n</a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8449.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5417" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8449-685x1024.jpg" alt="" width="479" height="717" /></a></p>\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8493.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5418" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8493-685x1024.jpg" alt="" width="479" height="717" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8343-copy.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5416" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8343-copy-796x1024.jpg" alt="" width="491" height="631" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8327.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5415" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC8327-1024x685.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="428" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/At-LightKitchen-Studios.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5420" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/At-LightKitchen-Studios-685x1024.jpg" alt="" width="479" height="717" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC_0149.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5422" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC_0149-680x1024.jpg" alt="" width="476" height="717" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC_0024b.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5421" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC_0024b-1024x680.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="425" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC85451.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5428" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/DSC85451-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="360" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">A big MERCI to Christian, Jael, Lia, Paloma, Caidy, Clement, Kazuko, Mayumi and the whole ICU team!</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Behind The Scenes at the ICU Photoshoot', 'After two long days spent at the Lightkitchen Studio with photographer Christian Geisselmann, the ICU team is basking in the post-photoshoot glow.  Stunning pieces from new designers and new pieces from ICU favorites inspired a beautiful photoshoot with the amazing hair and makeup of Kazuko Kitaoka and Mayumi ODA, styling, and photography, all under the guidance of our fearless leader- and part time superhero- Christan Summers.  Now it''s time to let our hair down, kick our heels up, and revel in the amazing results.  Here''s a behind the scenes glimpse of what went down and what ICU has in store for you this summer.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'behind-the-scenes-at-the-icu-photoshoot', '', '', '2011-04-06 14:48:05', '2011-04-06 12:48:05', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5414', 0, 'post', '', 0),
