(5452, 8, '2011-04-08 11:55:16', '2011-04-08 09:55:16', 'Five full days of sunshine in Paris have given us an extra skip in our step. Say <em>sayonara</em> to those winter coats, and <em>adios</em> to those mid-season jackets-- this weekend the layers come off and the ''tude comes out!\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rackkandruin-speed-of-sound-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5453" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/April-9-SAT-copy-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="620" /></a></p>\nAmp up your street edge Saturday and contrast the 21 degree sunshine with a dark palette and novelty prints. Accent your zebra, bananas, and <a href="http://www.naco-paris.com/" target="_blank">"Karl Who"</a> with the perfect black carryall from <a href="http://www.makr.com/" target="_blank">Makr</a> and a smokey pine eye. Top it all off with the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rackkandruin-speed-of-sound-necklace.html" target="_blank">Rackk And Ruin Speed of Sound Necklace</a> for equal parts shine and attitude.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5454" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/April-10-SAT-copy-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="620" /></a></p>\nSunday, with sunshine and 23 degrees, why not go after the summer trends two at a time? Create your look with layers and colorblocking in mind, by topping a long blue dress with a watermelon hued tank, bright yellow bag, purple loafers and green nails. Don''t stop there! Colorblock and stack your metals too with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Thin Stackable Rings</a> in gold and silver.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nSaturday''s Look: tee shirt <a href="http://www.naco-paris.com/" target="_blank">Naco Paris</a>, leggings Topshop, bag <a href="http://www.makr.com/" target="_blank">Makr Carry Goods</a>, eyeshadow Sephora, shoes Zara, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rackkandruin-speed-of-sound-necklace.html" target="_blank">Rackk And Ruin Necklace at ICU-IN PARIS</a>.\n\nSunday''s Look: dress American Vintage, shoes Urban Outfitters, top Topshop, bag Urban Outfitters, nail polish Barielle Shades, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Noot Rings at ICU-IN PARIS</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nDoes the weather in your city not match the Paris sun? Create your own forecast, send it to us, and we''ll put it on the blog!', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'Five full days of sunshine in Paris have given us an extra skip in our step.  Say sayonara to those winter coats, and adios to those mid-season jackets-- this weekend the layers come off and the ''tude comes out!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-3', '', '', '2011-04-08 11:55:16', '2011-04-08 09:55:16', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5452', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5464, 4, '2011-04-11 16:08:10', '2011-04-11 14:08:10', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/P1140482.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5466" title="P1140482" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/P1140482-1024x228.jpg" alt="" width="915" height="203" /></a></p>\nAnother Monday - another start to the week... we know Mondays can be a downer, especially after the beautiful weekend of weather we''ve had here in Paris (record breaking temp of 27C yesterday!), but here we are to give you a little style inspiration to brighten up the day.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/31/find-out-more-about-christan-summers-icu-founder/" target="_blank">Christan Summers</a>, ICU''s founder, has shared with us her fav pick for this week. Inspired by the arrival ofSpring, Christan seems to be all about flowers, Bena flowers to be exact. Beautiful, gold, shiny Bena Flower brooch to be even more exact! (See who else fell in love with the Bena Flower Brooch in the <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/23/paris-style-profile-with-laura-g-the-flower-darling/" target="_blank">ICU Style Profile</a> video.)\n\nChristan says, "This is the perfect touch of all that glitters! I love the way the brooch gives each outfit a fresh and elegant feel. Its perfect to layer with any gold or silver piece since the gold coloring of the flower doesn''t overwhelm the eye. Plus, its like giving yourself a flower that never dies, and what girl doesn''t love being treated to a flower?"\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Bena-gold-flower-mirror-pin-cover.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5465" title="Bena gold flower mirror pin cover" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Bena-gold-flower-mirror-pin-cover.jpg" alt="" width="353" height="554" /></a>Shop the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Flower Brooch</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/P1140482.jpg"><img title="P1140482" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/P1140482-1024x228.jpg" alt="" width="915" height="203" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', 'Christan&#039;s Pick of the Week', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'christans-pick-of-the-week-2', '', '', '2011-04-11 16:08:10', '2011-04-11 14:08:10', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5464', 0, 'post', '', 0),
