(5501, 8, '2011-04-13 18:17:00', '2011-04-13 16:17:00', '<p style="text-align: left;">What''s better than a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena </a><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Flower</a> Mirror Brooch? A <span style="color: #ff00ff;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>free</strong> Bena Flower Mirror Brooch! </span></span>Yup that''s right, you heard me, but I''ll say again a little louder so you actually believe it: a <span style="color: #ff00ff;"><strong>free</strong></span> Bena Flower Mirror Brooch!</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">We''re giving away a Bena Flower Mirror Brooch to one lucky lady (or fella), and it''s so easy all you have to do is make a couple clicks. First, you have to "like" us on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/icuinparis" target="_blank">facebook</a>. Then, you have to "like" our profile picture. As we promised, two clicks and you''re done-- automatically entered to win a Bena Flower Mirror Brooch in either silver or gold. We can hear the gasps now: "Free <em>and</em> we get to choose the color? ICU, you''re crazy!" It''s true, we are crazy. Crazy for flowers! While you''re there feel free to leave us a comment, the funnier your comment the more likely you are to be chosen.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Make sure to "like" us and "like" our profile pic by Wednesday the 20th of April because we''ll choose the winner on Thursday the 21st.</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #808080;">\n</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #808080;">\n</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Screen-shot-2011-04-13-at-5.27.33-PM.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5505" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Screen-shot-2011-04-13-at-5.27.33-PM.png" alt="" width="413" height