(5523, 8, '2011-04-14 15:17:51', '2011-04-14 13:17:51', 'It is once again time to reflect on the great style of one of our favorite bloggers, and today we''re honoring <a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Adeline Rapon</a>. With looks that range from delicate and understated to eclectic and layered, we can''t get enough of how this Parisian girl balances her individual flare with classic French aesthetic. She already rocks jewels from <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>''s own Charlotte Martyr, and now see which other <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> designers fit her unique and elegant street chic.\n\n<a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5528" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Screen-shot-2011-04-14-at-2.09.44-PM.png" alt="" width="606" height="166" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/adeline-rapon-tough-boho.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5526" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/adeline-rapon-tough-boho-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">We love how effortlessly <a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Adeline</a> mixes boho layers with a tough leather pant. The perfect way to soften an all black outfit is by mixing multiple long necklaces in earthy and antiqued hues with a gold cuff and simple ring.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Unsurcinq <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-necklace-eugene.html" target="_blank">Eugene Necklace</a>, Ebb.and.pflow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/necklaces/ebb-and-pflow-vientiane-necklace.html" target="_blank">Vientiane Necklace</a>, Charlotte Martyr <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/bracelets/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Cuff</a>, Noot <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/rings/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Thin Gold Stackable Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5527" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank1.jpg" alt="" width="113" height="99" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/adeline-rapon-rocker.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5524" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/adeline-rapon-rocker-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Create the perfect eclectic mix of silver jewelry full of playful rocker personality just like <a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Adeline</a>: pair and mix of tough and delicate necklaces with silver and grey leather bracelets. Top off the look with a handful of different rings, mixing polished silver with antique finishes and even a touch of lavender.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Lisa Levine <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/necklaces/double-spike-necklace.html" target="_blank">Double Spike Necklace</a>, Coralie De Seynes <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/bracelets/coralie-de-seynes-bracelet-mors-grey-leather-gun-metal.html" target="_blank">Grey Leather &amp; Silver Chain Bracelet</a>, Rackk And Ruin <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rackkandruin-speed-of-sound-necklace.html" target="_blank">Speed of Sound Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/bracelets/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot Silver Bangle Bracelets</a>, Shamila <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Light Purple Amethyst Ring</a>, Ebb.and.pflow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">Striate Grandissimo Ring</a>, Charlotte Martyr <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/jay-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Jay Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladimir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Vladimir Ring</a>, Unsurcinq <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/rings/unsurcinq-ring-charlotte.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5527" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank1.jpg" alt="" width="126" height="110" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/adeline-rapon-smart.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5525" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/adeline-rapon-smart-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="468" /></a>For a smart look like <a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Adeline</a>''s lace skirt and blazer make a simple jewelry statement with a vintage inspired necklace and two gold bracelets.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Unsurcinq <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/necklaces/unsurcinq-necklace-eddy.html" target="_blank">Eddy Necklace</a>, Noot <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/bracelets/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Gold Bangle Bracelets</a>, Unsurcinq <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/bracelets/unsurcinq-bracelet-hugh.html" target="_blank">Hugh Bracelet</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Please enjoy all pictures of Adeline in their original form on her wonderful <a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">blog</a>, and shop all jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icu.com</a>.</p>\n&nbsp;', 'Blogger of the Week', 'It is once again time to reflect on the great style of one of our favorite bloggers, and today we''re honoring Adeline Rapon.  With looks that range from delicate and understated to eclectic and layered, we can''t get enough of how this Parisian girl balances her individual flare with classic French aesthetic. She already rocks jewels from ICU''s own Charlotte Martyr, and now see which other ICU designers fit her unique and elegant street chic.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-2', '', '', '2011-04-14 15:17:51', '2011-04-14 13:17:51', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5523', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5535, 8, '2011-04-14 15:08:06', '2011-04-14 13:08:06', '<p style="text-align: left">ICU is giving away one <span style="color: #cc99ff">FREE</span> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Flower Mirror Brooch</a>!</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Screen-shot-2011-04-13-at-5.27.33-PM-21.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5537" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Screen-shot-2011-04-13-at-5.27.33-PM-21.png" alt="" width="273" height="349" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: left">To enter to win this brooch for free just follow these two easy steps:</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">1. "Like" us on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/icuinparis" target="_blank">facebook</a>. (If you''re already our fan on facebook you can skip this step.)</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">2. "Like" our profile picture.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Now you can sit back, relax and start planning all the outfits you''re going to wear when you win the Bena Flower Mirror Brooch. What are you waiting for? Offer ends <strong>Thursday, April 21st</strong> so click <a href="http://www.facebook.com/icuinparis" target="_blank">here</a> to get started!</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>', 'FREE Jewelry Giveaway', 'ICU is giving away one FREE Bena Flower Mirror Brooch!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'free-jewelry-giveaway', '', '', '2011-04-14 15:08:06', '2011-04-14 13:08:06', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5535', 0, 'post', '', 0);
