(5546, 8, '2011-04-15 18:52:52', '2011-04-15 16:52:52', '<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/forecast-17-april-1024x991-1.jpg">\n</a>A grey week in Paris has lead to a hopeful and optimistic ray of sunshine for the weekend. Layering brights, darks and neutrals with a few <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> favorites will ensure that you have a happy and well dressed Saturday and Sunday.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/forecast-16-april.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5547" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/forecast-16-april-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="620" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">For mostly sunny Saturday errands keep the outfit simple with a canvas tote and bold contrasting colors like bright coral and royal blue. Make sure your jewelry is just as bold as your color palette by clasping a large crystal-inspired gold cuff by <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a> to your wrist.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/forecast-17-april-1024x991-1.jpg"><img title="forecast-17-april-1024x991-1" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/forecast-17-april-1024x991-1.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="620" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Kick up your eclecticism Sunday with a mix of the hottest trends for mid-season. Layer a white shirt dress with a contrasting black jersey jacket, purple tie-dye tights, brown work boots, and a chunky glitter nail. To push your look from everyday mix-and-match to a true sartorial statement, add <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>''s newest addition to the boutique: the playful and edgy street-chic <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/04/13/street-style-king-of-the-jungle/" target="_blank">Resin Lion Necklace from Lenaklax</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Saturday''s Look: tee Andrea Crews, lipstick Flirt!, bag Naco Paris, jeans Urban Outfitters, shoes Industry of All Nations, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Bracelet Charlotte Martyr</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Sunday''s Look: dress Mikkat Market, boots Zara, jacket American Vintage, nail polish Milani Jewel FX, tights Top Shop, <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/04/13/street-style-king-of-the-jungle/" target="_blank">Resin Lion Necklace Lenaklax</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div></div>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'A grey week in Paris has lead to a hopeful an optimistic ray of sunshine for the weekend.  Layering brights, darks and neutrals with a few ICU favorites will ensure that you have a happy and well dressed Saturday and Sunday.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-4', '', '', '2011-04-15 18:52:52', '2011-04-15 16:52:52', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5546', 0, 'post', '', 0),
