(5573, 8, '2011-04-19 11:26:14', '2011-04-19 09:26:14', 'Once again, ICU founder <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/31/find-out-more-about-christan-summers-icu-founder/" target="_blank">Christan Summers</a> is bringing you her favorite item from the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU boutique</a>, and this week she''s head over heels for <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-lady-tee-shirt.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange''s Lady Tee</a>. With summer just around the corner and temperatures rising it''s no wonder she''d choose a comfortable arm baring cotton tee. And if the forecast wasn''t enough incentive here''s her personal styling tip: "I''m loving this cool comfy <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-lady-tee-shirt.html" target="_blank">Lady Tee</a> with a pair of rolled up men''s suit pants, cuffed sleeves, and skyscraper high heels."\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-lady-tee-shirt.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5574" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/laurent-desgrange-icuinparis-973x1024.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="626" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-lady-tee-shirt.html" target="_blank">Shop the Lady Tee here!</a></p>', 'Christan&#039;s Pick of the Week', 'Once again, ICU founder Christan Summers is bringing you her favorite item from the ICU boutique, and this week she''s head over heels for Laurent Desgrange''s Lady Tee.  With summer just around the corner and temperatures rising it''s no wonder she''d choose a comfortable arm baring cotton tee.  And if the forecast wasn''t enough incentive here''s her personal styling tip: "I''m loving this cool comfy Lady Tee with a pair of rolled up men''s suit pants, cuffed sleeves, and skyscraper high heels."', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'christans-pick-of-the-week-3', '', '', '