(5604, 8, '2011-04-21 15:20:52', '2011-04-21 13:20:52', 'Another week another muse! This week <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is honoring <a href="http://www.etpourquoipascoline.fr/" target="_blank">Coline</a>, of <em><a href="http://www.etpourquoipascoline.fr/" target="_blank">etpourquoipascoline</a></em>, for her laid back and chic style. She adds the perfect touch of simple and elegant jewelry to her clean and well paired ensembles, all brought to life by her unique and artistic tattoos. <a href="http://www.etpourquoipascoline.fr/" target="_blank">Coline''s</a> understated glamour and charming pictures have captured us, and make her a perfect fit for the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> jewels.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.etpourquoipascoline.fr/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5610" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Screen-shot-2011-04-21-at-1.27.08-PM.png" alt="" width="631" height="135" /></a></p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/etpourquoipascoline1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5606" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/etpourquoipascoline1-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Create the perfect fresh faced summer look just like <a href="http://www.etpourquoipascoline.fr/" target="_blank">Coline</a>''s by pairing a classic white tee with a delicate gold chain necklace and three thin silver rings.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Noot <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-necklace-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Gold Knot Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Knot Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Thin Stackable Rings</a>, ebb.and.pflow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-delicado-ring.html" target="_blank">Striate Delicado Two-Toned Ring</a>.</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5605" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank3-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/etpourquoipascoline3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5608" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/etpourquoipascoline3-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">For a dreamy sun-lit look, complement a white cotton blouse with an eclectic mix of jewels, including feather earrings, a large silver statement cuff, and a delicate stone ring.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shamila <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Light Purple Amethyst Ring</a>, Lisa Levine <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/calico-earrings.html" target="_blank">Violet Purple Feather Earrings</a>, Charlotte Martyr <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-sabrina-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Silver Sabrina Crystal Bangle</a>.</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5605" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank3-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/etpourquoipascoline2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5607" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/etpourquoipascoline2-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">We love how easily <a href="http://www.etpourquoipascoline.fr/" target="_blank">Coline</a> mixes eclectic jewelry with a classic bow. Play with pr