(5626, 8, '2011-04-22 18:47:10', '2011-04-22 16:47:10', 'It''s the hottest weekend of the year in Paris! Take those layers off, get the sunscreen out, put your sunglasses on, and go dance in the sunshine! Make sure to follow<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"> ICU</a>''s tips to mix your clothes with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">our jewels</a> for guaranteed sweet sartorial success.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5633" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/sunday-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="575" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Stick to a pastel palette for Saturday''s 26 degree scorcher and pair ruffly knit shorts with a simple grey tee, rosey sandals, lavender tips, and a whimsical tote. Top off the look with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-necklace-long.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Long Popcorn Necklace</a> for a chic and easy, sunny statement.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5634" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/sunday2-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="575" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Sunday is one of those truly mystifying mid-season mashups of hot sun and cold rain. Take a retro approach with a peach knit, classic denim shorts, bowed clogs, bowed hair, and bright turquoise nails. Jazz up the look with by adding a bit of sparkle and shine with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/necklaces/mouse-necklace-gold.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Gold Mouse Necklace</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">Shop the Paris style forecasts here!</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="tex