(5644, 8, '2011-04-28 14:42:53', '2011-04-28 12:42:53', 'This week <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU - IN PARIS</a> is truly inspired by the sweet, smart and picturesque stylings of <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Leeloo from Le Dressing de Leeloo</a>. With a simple and feminine aesthetic, <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Leeloo</a> never shies away from a flower in her hair and isn''t afraid of adding strong dashes of color. Her jewelry always adds an extra flare to her look, and the girl is just wild about bows! Below, check out <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> styling of Leeloo, our Blogger of the Week. Get the look by following the links to the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU boutique</a>.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5647" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Le-dressing-de-Leeloo.jpeg" alt="" width="577" height="197" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5649" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/ledressingdeleeloo-icuinparis-prep-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">For <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Leeloo''s</a> modern prep, create your own feminine dandy look by mixing a clean white blouse and bowler hat with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-african-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent''s</a> primary printed bowtie, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot''s</a> thin silver bangle, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s</a> cute, quirky animal ring.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop the look:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-african-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange African Batik Bow</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Cat Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot Silver Bangle Bracelet</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5646" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank4-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5648" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/ledressingdeleeloo-icuinparis-bowtastic-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Attack of the bows! We love <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Leeloo''s</a> fearlessness when it comes to mixing bows. Pile them on with a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-toile-de-jouy-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent</a> floral bow for your hair, a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-victorian-bow-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena</a> mirrored bow for your lapel, and a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/feather-bow-ring.html" target="_blank">Laure Mory</a> feather bow for your hand. Top them off with a feminine knotted bracelet from <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Noot</a> and a mother of pearl brooch from <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-carbone-60-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop the look:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-toile-de-jouy-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange Toile de Jouy Bow</a>, Bena <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-gold-victorian-bow-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Gold Victorian Bow Mirror Brooch</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-carbone-60-brooch.html" target="_blank">Carbone 60 Brooch</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Knot Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/feather-bow-ring.html" target="_blank">Laure Mory Papillon Feather Bow Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5646" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank4-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5650" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/ledressingdeleeloo-icuinparis-weekend-thrift-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Create the ultimate casual weekend style like <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Leeloo</a> with loose jeans, two thick silver rings by <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cloud-ring.html" target="_blank">Noot</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">ebb.and.pflow</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-triangle-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena''s </a>hand carved wooden brooch on your favorite old leather jacket, and of course, the essential <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-graphic-gold-summer-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent </a>bow for your hair.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop the look:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-graphic-gold-summer-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange Graphic Gold Summer Bow</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-triangle-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Triangle Mother of Pearl Brooch</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cloud-ring.html" target="_blank">Noot Cloud Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">Ebb.and.pflow Striate Grandissimo Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5646" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/blank4-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Please enjoy all pictures of <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Leeloo</a> on her adorable <a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">blog</a>, and shop all jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>\n&nbsp;', 'Blogger of the Week: Le Dressing de Leeloo', 'This week ICU - IN PARIS is truly inspired by the sweet, smart and picturesque stylings of Leeloo from Le Dressing de Leeloo.  With a simple and feminine aesthetic, Leeloo never shies away from a flower in her hair and isn''t afraid of adding strong dashes of color.  Her jewelry always adds an extra flare to her look, and the girl is just wild about bows!  Below, see the looks that we love to look at from Leeloo, our Blogger of the Week, and how you can love her style with ICU.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-le-dressing-de-leeloo', '', '', '2011-04-28 14:42:53', '2011-04-28 12:42:53', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5644', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5657, 4, '2011-04-28 18:41:17', '2011-04-28 16:41:17', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5658" title="royal-wedding-fever_icuinparis.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/royal-wedding-fever_icuinparis.com_-561x1024.jpg" alt="Shop Bena Queen Brooch to style for the Royal Wedding of Kate &amp; Will" width="561" height="1024" /></a></p>', 'We&#039;ve got the Royal Wedding Fever with Bena&#039;s Queen Brooch!', 'Bena Queen of England Brooch\n\nA charming addition to your accessory collection, the Bena Queen of England Brooch is sure to bring a bit of humor and a touch of London style.  Hand-etched from cherry wood, it makes a perfect statement when worn alone or mixed with other Bena brooches. Shop Bena''s Queen of England Brooch and other new fashion styles at www.icuinparis.com', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'weve-got-the-royal-wedding-fever-with-benas-queen-brooch', '', '', '2011-04-28 18:41:17', '2011-04-28 16:41:17', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5657', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(5662, 8, '2011-04-29 13:45:27', '2011-04-29 11:45:27', 'Time to recover from this week''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Royal Wedding fever</a>... with more <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Royal Wedding</a> fever! Keep the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Queen</a> with you all weekend long, through mild Paris temperatures and spots of rain. Follow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> tips below for a truly splendid and royal fashion statement worthy of a fairytale weekend.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5663" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/0430-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="575" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">In honor of the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Queen</a> get ready to rock some royal blue jeans! For a cool and casual look, pair them with white leather slip-ons, a yellow and blue straw bag, and tied up blouse. Stay dry during sporadic rain showers with a straw fedora, and stay fabulous with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena''s Queen Brooch</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5666" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/0501b-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="575" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Take the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Queen</a> out with you Sunday afternoon for a colorful nod to the British dandies. Create a quirky mix of saturated colors and traditional prints: bright cherry oxfords with lavender dip-dyed socks, and a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-toile-de-jouy-bow.html" target="_blank">Toile de Jouy bow from Laurent Desgrange </a>with a chromatic plaid confection. Top off the look with Elizabeth herself by pinning on <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena''s Queen Brooch</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;">Saturday''s Look: jeans by J Brand, bag and hat by J Crew, top by Mikkat Market, shoes by Keds, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Queen Brooch by ICU - IN PARIS</a>.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000;">Sunday''s Look: shoes by Urban Outfitters, shirt by J Crew, shorts by Cheap Monday, socks by Mikkat Market, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-toile-de-jouy-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange Toile de Jouy Bow by ICU - IN PARIS</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-queen-of-england-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Queen Brooch by ICU - IN PARIS</a>.</span></p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'Time to recover from this week''s Royal Wedding fever... with more Royal Wedding fever!  Keep the Queen with you all weekend long, through mild Paris temperatures and spots of rain.  Follow ICU''s tips below for a truly splendid and royal fashion statement worthy of a fairytale weekend.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-5', '', '', '2011-04-29 13:45:27', '2011-04-29 11:45:27', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5662', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5674, 8, '2011-05-03 14:16:26', '2011-05-03 12:16:26', 'Back again to find out which accessories <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> founder <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/03/31/find-out-more-about-christan-summers-icu-founder/" target="_blank">Christan Summers</a> is wild about right now! With Mother''s Day just around the corner (May 8, for those of you in the United States), Christan is channeling her own mother''s style and selecting <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Thin Stackable Rings</a> for a nostalgic nod to her creative role model. Find out why these <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">thin geometric rings</a> remind Christan of her mom:\n\n"All of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=noot" target="_blank">Noot''s</a> designs remind me of my mom. Noot''s whole message and what inspires her to design is the poetry of life, the little things. And my mom has always been a firm believer in remembering what life is really about: life, love, people, experiences. The <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Stackable Rings</a> have a really soft organic feel to them, yet they''re also very elegant. I like simple jewelry because I like to mix and stack, and these are perfect for mixing in with other pieces. My mom''s style is boho, comfortable and eclectic, which has always been a huge inspiration to me, and which is why I know she would wear and love Noot''s<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Stackable Rings</a>."\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5677" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/NOOT-gold-and-silver-artisan-rings-geomteric-rings-icuinparispsd1.jpg" alt="" wi