(5706, 8, '2011-05-04 12:42:52', '2011-05-04 10:42:52', '<p style="text-align: left">For those of you in the U.S., Mother''s Day is less than a week away. If you (like most of us), still don''t have a gift for dear old Mom, fear not because <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is here to help! It takes a special item to sum up a year''s worth of "thanks, Mom" and "I love you, Mom", and there''s no better way to express all of those feelings than with jewelry: it''s timeless, it''s unique, it''s special-- it''s Mom. Follow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> guide to getting the perfect piece of jewelry for your mom.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5714" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/NOOT-gold-and-silver-artisan-rings-geomteric-rings-icuinparispsd2.jpg" alt="" width="521" height="322" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>The Boho Mom</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Perfect for the free spirit mom, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Thin Stackable Rings</a> strike the perfect balance between classic and organic. Their simplicity makes them ideal for mixing in with old eclectic favorites from a lifetime of travel.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5724" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank.jpg" alt="" width="1458" height="98" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-necklace-albert.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5708" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/albert-nkl-black-icuinparis.col_.jpg" alt="" width="278" height="628" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>The Romantic Mom</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">If your mama is the sugar in your tea cup then there''s no better gift than the sweetest of all heart lockets: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-necklace-albert.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq''s Albert Necklace</a>. Give her maternal pride a boost by putting your favorite mother-daughter photo inside the locket.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5724" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank.jpg" alt="" width="1458" height="98" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-natural-diamond-structure-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5710" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Bena-mother-of-pearl-and-wood-constellation-necklace-.jpg" alt="" width="446" height="670" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>The Playful Creative Mom</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">If your mom loves going to markets and decorative arts museums, wears her favorite dress for no particular reason, and growing up always made sure you had a box of crayons within reach, then your mom needs <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-natural-diamond-structure-necklace.html" target="_blank">Bena''s Natural Diamond Structure Necklace</a>. A unique juxtaposition of wood grain and mother of pearl, it is a must have for the decorative mom.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5724" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank.jpg" alt="" width="1458" height="98" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/grey-diamond-cluster-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5713" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/gorjana-grey-diamond-necklace.jpg" alt="" width="405" height="471" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>The Classic Chic Mom</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">An elegant necklace for an elegant mom, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/grey-diamond-cluster-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gorjana''s Grey Diamond Cluster Necklace</a> is the perfect go-to accessory for a chic and carefully put together woman. Nothing says classic and unique like a cluster of delicate faceted diamonds.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Find these gifts and more Mother''s Day jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>', 'Mother&#039;s Day Gift Guide', 'For those of you in the U.S., Mother''s Day is less than a week away.  If you (like most of us), still don''t have a gift for dear old Mom, fear not because ICU is here to help!  It takes a special item to sum up a year''s worth of "thanks, Mom" and "I love you, Mom", and there''s no better way to express all of those feelings than with jewelry: it''s timeless, it''s unique, it''s special-- it''s Mom.  Follow ICU''s guide to getting the perfect piece of jewelry for your mom.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mothers-day-gift-guide', '', '', '2011-05-04 12:42:52', '2011-05-04 10:42:52', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5706', 0, 'post', '', 2),
