(5735, 8, '2011-05-05 17:31:29', '2011-05-05 15:31:29', 'This week <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is inspired by Seaghna of <a href="http://lightsdrivemysoul.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">www.lightsdrivemysoul.com</a>, and her cool California attitude. Her unique style perfectly mixes equal parts rocker, hippie, and trendy-- all wrapped up in a powerful, 90''s-tinted free spirit. The fabulous combination of her trademark flowing beach blonde waves and harder glam rock accessories makes her the ideal match for <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>''s brand new collection of crystal rock jewelry: handmade by <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=astraleye" target="_blank">Astraleye</a> in Singapore, and handpicked by <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU- IN PARIS</a>. Follow the styles below to tap into your inner fashion chakra by shopping <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>''s crystal rock jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5737" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/lightsdrivemysoul-1-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Create a free spirited, head-to-toe color statement like <a href="http://lightsdrivemysoul.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Seaghna''s</a> lavender look by starting with a distressed tie-dye tee from Seaghna''s own collection <a href="http://lightsdrivemysoul.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Sea of Style</a>, and adding <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/amethyst-necklace.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Amethyst Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/purple-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Purple Quartz Ring</a>, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethy