(5794, 8, '2011-05-12 12:57:59', '2011-05-12 10:57:59', 'For this week''s Blogger of the Week, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is traveling to Indonesia to celebrate <a href="http://brownplatform.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Anastasia of Brown Platform</a>. If there''s one thing for certain it''s that this girl knows her accessories! <a href="http://brownplatform.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Anastasia''s</a> got her finger on the pulse of feminine fashion trends, and between her love of shoes and her well crafted jewelry combinations, it''s no doubt that she''s a sartorial inspiration.\n\nBelow see how perfectly her sweet stylings from <a href="http://brownplatform.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Brown Platform</a> fit with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> own jewelry. Want these looks for yourself? They''re all yours, just click <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">HERE</a> to start shopping!\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5801" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/brown-platform1-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Dress yourself in a simple summer look just like <a href="http://brownplatform.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Anastasia''s</a> by pairing nature-inspired necklaces with a sugary colored skirt. Start by layering Astraleye''s Gold Dipped Agate Necklaces in <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-grey-agate-necklace.html" target="_blank">Grey</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-purple-agate-necklace.html" target="_blank">Purple</a>, and top it off with a multitude of gold and silver stacked geometric<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Bangles from Noot</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5800" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank2-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5802" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/brown-platform2-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Not sure what to wear to a delicious tea party? Follow <a href="http://brownplatform.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Anastasia''s</a> lead and complement a feminine blouse with a trio of fashionable statement rings. Start with Charlotte Martyr''s fairytale rabbit <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vlady-rabbit-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Vlady Ring</a>, and mix real and faux crystals together with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s White Quartz Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-caroline-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Gold Caroline Ring</a>. Finish off the look with a single <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle.html" target="_blank">Large Handcrafted Gold Bangle from Anna Beck</a>.</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5800 alignnone" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank2-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5803" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/brown-platform3-1024x748.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="434" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">We adore <a href="http://brownplatform.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Anastasia''s</a> girly and sophisticated, carefree combination. Accent your own blouse, skirt and killer 