(5832, 8, '2011-05-13 12:21:00', '2011-05-13 10:21:00', '<p style="text-align: left;">It''s the weekend of <a href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">SOON FAMOUS</a>! Are you coming?Finally your chance to get to feel, touch, try, smell (hmmm... kind of weird) but anyway, we will be there so come to complete your weekend look and shop with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>!</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">This weekend we continue our love affair withthe newest member of the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU boutique</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=astraleye" target="_blank">Astraleye</a>,whosedelicate crystal jewels prove to be endlessly versatile and inspire a closet full of looks. Get ready because it''s time to rock out with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> rock jewelry.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-grey-agate-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5833" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/0514-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="518" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Create a high drama look Saturday that will last you through the day and into the night, by wearing <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-grey-agate-necklace.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Gold Dipped Grey Agate Necklace</a> over a strong hued top with similar subtle streaks and gradations of color. Contrast black jeans with tangerine ballerinas and lipstick, and a yellow clutch. A dark outfit, bright accessories and the organic beauty of grey agate are the perfect combination to guarantee you a look that really pops!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-crystal-rock-double-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5834" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/0515-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="518" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Leave sweet and subtle in the closet on Sunday and dress with attitude and edge! Create a striking palette of mustard yellow and teal green, and contrast it with black and white snakeskin leggings and a sparkling snakeskin clutch. Top it off with the ultimate eye-catcher, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-crystal-rock-double-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s exquisite Rainbow Crystal Rock Double Ring</a>-- the only accessory powerful enough to bring harmony to an outfit so wild.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Saturday''s Look: shoes and clutch Zara, top <a href="http://www.stylesofia.com/LookBook.aspx" target="_blank">stylesofia.com</a>, lipstick Make Up For Ever, jeans Cheap Monday, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-grey-agate-necklace.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Necklace ICU - IN PARIS</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Sunday''s Look: shoes Asos, leggings <a href="http://www.mikkatmarket.com/" target="_blank">Mikkat Market,</a> top American Vintage, nail polish RGB Polish, clutch Top Shop, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-crystal-rock-double-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Ring ICU - IN PARIS</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Shop the weekend looks at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a> and come visit us at <a href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous</a> to shop the pieces in person!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Soon Famous</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">66 rue Ren Boulanger Paris 10e</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Sat - Sun: 11 - 19h</p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'Another weekend of outfits to plan and ICU is here to help!  This weekend we continue our love affair with Astraleye, the newest member of the ICU boutique.  Her delicate crystal jewels prove to be endlessly versatile and inspire a closet full of looks.  Get ready because it''s time to rock out with ICU''s rock jewelry.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-7', '', '', '2011-05-13 12:21:00', '2011-05-13 10:21:00', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5832', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5844, 8, '2011-05-16 15:18:13', '2011-05-16 13:18:13', 'This week,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> founder Christan Summers has more than just a pick of the week for you-- it''s a pair of the week! Having spent the weekend presenting<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> at<a href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous</a>, situated next to the vintage attiredMorgan, of<a href="http://morganours.com/" target="_blank">planB blog</a>, Christan is in a retro kind of mood.\n\nPairing<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s White Quartz Ring</a>, with<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-retrodots-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange''s Retro Dot Bow</a>,is a unique combination sure to give you an original and nostalgic look, with an oh-so-perfect touch of crystal sparkle.She advises,"Wear the<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-retrodots-bow.html" target="_blank">Retro Dot Bow</a> on the waistband of a high waisted skirt and then add a little shine by putting on the<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">White Quartz Ring</a>. The subtle purple iridescence in the crystal really bring out the purple tones of the bow, for a surprising but harmonious combination."\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5845" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/astraleye_quartz-ring_crystal-jewelry_01-690x1024.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="396" /></a></p>\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-retrodots-bow.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5846" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/IMG_0186-1.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="320" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Shop Christan''s ICU picks of the week <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">here</a>:</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">White Quartz Ring</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-retrodots-bow.html" target="_blank">Retro Polka Dot Bow</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">To view all of Christan''s ICU picks click <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?s=christan+pick+of+the+week" target="_blank">here</a></p>', 'Christan&#039;s Pick of the Week', 'This week, ICU founder Christan Summers has more than just a pick of the week for you-- it''s a pair of the week!  Having spent all weekend at Soon Famous set up next to the vintage attired Morgan, of planB blog, Christan is in a retro kind of mood: she''s styling Astraleye''s White Quartz Ring, with Laurent Desgrange''s Retro Dot Bow. It''s a unique combination sure to give you an original and nostalgic look, with an oh-so-perfect touch of crystal sparkle.  ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'christans-pick-of-the-week-5', '', '', '2011-05-16 15:18:13', '2011-05-16 13:18:13', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5844', 0, 'post', '', 0),
