(5870, 8, '2011-05-20 17:10:56', '2011-05-20 15:10:56', 'This week <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is continuing to pay hommage to Mother Nature''s amazing crystals. Summer is here again with warm temperatures and sunshine. Whether you''re perusing the shops or lunching with friends, follow the tips below to rock crystal rocks all weekend long with a complimentary palette of earth tones.<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/amethyst-crystal-earrings.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5871" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/0521-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="575" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Start the weekend off with a non-color color range in shades of mocha, creme and beige. Balance an off-white tank and sandals with cinamon carryall and long pleated skirt. Add <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/amethyst-crystal-earrings.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Amethyst Earrings</a> for a touch of color and a truly organic and earthy statement.</p>\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-crystal-rock-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5872" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/0522-1024x991.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="575" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Nothing says summer like an outfit of all whites! Don''t be afraid to mix shades with a super white drapey blouse, creme colored shorts, and a pale grey tote. For a subtle touch of color top off the look with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-crystal-rock-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s White Crystal Rock Ring</a> which magically sparkles to reflect all the colors of the rainbow.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Saturday''s Look: tank American Vintage, nail polish Essie, bag Top Shop, skirt Romwe, sandals Asos, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/amethyst-crystal-earrings.html" target="_blank">Astraleye earrings ICU - IN PARIS.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Sunday''s Look: top Mikkat Market, bag Makr Carry Goods, shorts Urban Outfitters, shoes Boutique 9, nail polish Sally Hansen, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-crystal-rock-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye ring ICU - IN PARIS.</a></p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'This week ICU is continuing to pay hommage to Mother Nature''s amazing crystals.  Summer is here again with warm temperatures and sunshine.  Whether you''re perusing the shops or lunching with friends, follow the tips below to rock crystal rocks all weekend long with a complimentary palette of earth tones.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-8', '', '', '2011-05-20 17:10:56', '2011-05-20 15:10:56', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5870', 0, 'post', '', 0),
