(5907, 8, '2011-05-26 12:46:34', '2011-05-26 10:46:34', '<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is back in the blogosphere, and this week we''re inspired by the always chic and ever quirky Valentine from<em><a href="http://www.helloitsvalentine.com/" target="_blank">helloitsvalentine</a></em>. With a bevy of looks that range all the way from precious and embellished to simple summer picnic, it''s no doubt that she''s our pick for Blogger of the Week. Below see how <a href="http://www.helloitsvalentine.com/" target="_blank">Valentine''s</a> subtle color palette and signature silver jewels mingle with the hottest items from <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> summer collection.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5910" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/helloitsvalentine-1.jpg" alt="" width="644" height="470" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">For a breezy spring day follow <a href="http://www.helloitsvalentine.com/" target="_blank">Valentine''s</a> style mix for the perfect accessory look. Start with a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/crochet-summer-scarf-blue.html" target="_blank">Crochet Summer Scarf by Ariane Haas</a>, and dazzle your fingers with an airy melange of silver and white rings: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Silver Knot Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Silver Wing Ring</a>, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s White Quartz Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5909" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank3.jpg" alt="" width="1458" height="98" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5911" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/helloitsvalentine-2.jpg" alt="" width="644" height="470" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">We are smitten with <a href="http://www.helloitsvalentine.com/" target="_blank">Valentine''s</a> picnic vibe! Create your own relaxed summer look by starting with a unique statement necklace like <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-la-ruche-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Two-Tone Geometric Necklace</a>. Accent with a mix of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Silver Bangle Bracelets</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Popcorn Bracelet</a>, and top off the look with two eye catching rings, perfect for summer: Noot''s dreamy <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cloud-ring.html" target="_blank">Cloud Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/turquoise-magnetic-key-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s playful Magnetic Key Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5909" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/blank3.jpg" alt="" width="1458" height="98" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5912" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/helloitsvalentine-3.jpg" alt="" width="644" height="470" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Not sure how to add a touch of sparkle and individuality to a classic Parisian look? Be inspired by <a href="http://www.helloitsvalentine.com/" target="_blank">Valentine</a> and add a cocktail of silver gems: Send a message with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/diamond-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Diamond Bracelet</a>, and create an eclectic mix of rings by pairing a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Geometric Stackable Ring from Noot</a>, with the magical charm of Charlotte Martyr''s Jay Ring and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s White Wing Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Check out <a href="http://www.helloitsvalentine.com/" target="_blank">helloitsvalentine</a> and shop all looks at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Hello It&#039;s Valentine!', 'ICU is back in the blogosphere, and this week we''re inspired by the always chic and ever quirky Valentine from helloitsvalentine. With a bevy of looks that range all the way from precious and embellished, to simple summer picnic it''s no doubt she''s our pick for Blogger of the Week.  Below see how Valentine''s cheery color palette and signature silver jewels mingle with the hottest items from ICU''s summer collection.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-hello-its-valentine', '', '', '2011-05-26 12:46:34', '2011-05-26 10:46:34', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5907', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5932, 8, '2011-05-27 12:56:19', '2011-05-27 10:56:19', 'Clear your schedule Saturday because there should be only one thing on your agenda: <a href="http://viensdansmondressing.com/" target="_blank">Viens Dans Mon Dressing</a>. Instead of browsing the usual shops waiting for something exciting to jump out at you, come support independent design and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>, where you''re guaranteed to find something perfectly on trend and unique to make your summer wardrobe pop. The sun is peeking through the clouds giving Paris the perfect mild temperatures for a relaxed weekend outdoors. Follow our tips below to make your last May weekend a stylish one by accessorizing with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> newest designer to the boutique <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=emily+rothschild" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild</a>.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/medical-usb-locket.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5933" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/0528.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Saturday is all about fierce and innovative styling! Dip yourself in a pool of liquid metal creating an allover silver glow: top sequin shorts with a soft grey tee and black boots, accenting with a purple clutch and merlot lips. Give yourself a uniquely innovative edge with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/medical-usb-locket.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Medical USB Locket</a>, plated in black rhodium and fully equipped with a 2GB USB key-- it''s the perfect mix of old, new and rocker chic.</p>\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5934" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/0529.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Soften up after Saturday''s hard look with a neutral palette and styling worthy of a Greek Goddess. Pair a nude colored blouse , polkadot skirt and gold sandals, with warm orange toned makeup. Top off the look with a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">White Wing Ring from Emily Rothschild </a>on each hand and you''re set to fly away with Sunday''s warm temps.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://viensdansmondressing.com/" target="_blank">VIENS DANS MON DRESSING</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Bastille Design Center</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">74 bld Richard Lenoir, 75011</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left">For a full credit of items and to see more styling tips from ICU, check us out on <a href="http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/profile?id=2475640" target="_blank">Polyvore.</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<div>11h-19h</div>\n</div>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'Clear your schedule Saturday because there should be only one thing on your agenda: Viens Dans Mon Dressing.  Instead of browsing the usual shops waiting for something exciting to jump out at you, come support independent design and ICU, where you''re guaranteed to find something perfectly on trend and unique to make your summer wardrobe pop.  The sun is peeking through the clouds giving Paris the perfect mild temperatures for a relaxed weekend outdoors.  Follow our tips below to make your last May weekend a stylish one by accessorizing with ICU''s newest designer to the boutique Emily Rothschild.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-9', '', '', '2011-05-27 12:56:19', '2011-05-27 10:56:19', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5932', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5939, 8, '2011-05-30 10:38:33', '2011-05-30 08:38:33', '<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> founder, Christan Summers, can''t help but be smitten with the innovative designs of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=emily+rothschild" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild</a>, newest member to the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU - IN PARIS</a> boutique. This week she''s obsessed with Emily''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/medical-usb-locket.html" target="_blank">Medical USB Locket</a>: what appears to be a cool vintage-looking necklace at first glance, is actually a cleverly designed locket containing a 2GB USB key, intended to hold anything from emergency medical information to personal pictures and memories. Below, read why this innovative and smart necklace is Christan''s Pick of the Week!\n\n"I''ve turned into a bit of a computer nerd since starting <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU - IN PARIS</a>, but obviously my first love is jewelry. So to be able to carry around a USB key full of images, and have it all contained in a beautifully made locket is like the best of both worlds. Between the impressive craftsmanship, the clever design, and the substantial weight of the pendant I feel like I''m really wearing something valuable and special.\n\nSince the weather in Paris has been so up-and-down the last couple of weeks, I would wear the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/medical-usb-locket.html" target="_blank">Medical USB Locket</a> with acid wash skinny jeans and an Ysterike tee for a casual rock ''n'' roll kind of vibe. Then when it warms up a bit I''ll pair it with cut-off jean shorts, Converse, and a grey tank. The locket itself is so cool I can keep the rest of the outfit laid back and comfortable."\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/medical-usb-locket.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5941" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/20