(5979, 8, '2011-06-01 11:50:00', '2011-06-01 09:50:00', 'Whatever your style, whatever the occasion, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=emily+rothschild" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Wing Collection for ICU</a> will have you flying high. From formal affairs, to fun with friends, follow our guide below to make sure you''ve got the right wings for your style.\n\nShop all jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">WORKWEAR</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5989" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-01-at-11.41.49-AM.png" alt="" width="514" height="496" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Achieve the ultimate breezy summer work wardrobe by sticking to a palette of neutrals from camel to sand to dirty greys. Compliment the soft tones with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Gold Wing Rings</a>, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-18k-gold-and-silver-bead-necklace.html" target="_blank">ebb.and.pflow''s Two Tone Raw Silver and Gold Necklace</a>-- the perfect additions to stay on trend and sophisticated.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5980" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">WEEKEND CASUAL</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-wing-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5988" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-01-at-11.40.03-AM.png" alt="" width="514" height="423" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">High temps this summer mean weekends are spent in your favorite denim shorts and a choice selection of airy light printed tanks. Add an animal purse, white sandals, and tortoise sunnies. For a truly eye catching twist, pair one of summer''s hottest nail colors with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Silver Wing Rings</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5980" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">BEACH GETAWAY</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-mini-pinky-wing-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5987" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-01-at-11.38.09-AM.png" alt="" width="499" height="509" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">No boho beach outfit is complete without a small gold wing adorning your pinky to let your imagination and style fly free. Layer a printed bathing suit and white maxi dress with green sandals and pale petal sunglasses. Take cover under a floppy hat, and accent delicately with Emily Rothschild''s charming <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-mini-pinky-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Mini Pinky Wing Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5980" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">SUMMER COCKTAILS</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5986" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-01-at-11.36.24-AM.png" alt="" width="507" height="517" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Break the conservative rules of summers past by mixing crimson, tangerine, plum and fuschia, with one of summer''s hottest cocktail looks. Accent the bare shoulders of your sweet sartorial confection with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html" target="_blank">Gold Wing Earrings from Emily Rothschild</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5980" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/blank-1024x68.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="39" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">INTO THE NIGHT</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5985" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-01-at-11.34.29-AM.png" alt="" width="525" height="472" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">For a formal nighttime event create a stunning look with the classic palette of black and white. Keep the blacks soft and smudging into smokey powders and tarnished gold, and contrast with the stark and stunning white of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s White Wing Rings</a>. Top off the look with two tone <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-bang-na-limon-earrings.html" target="_blank">Bang Na Limon</a> teardrops for a unique and sophisticated elegance.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">SHOP ALL JEWELRY: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU - IN PARIS</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">View all looks: <a href="http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/profile?id=2475640" target="_blank">Polyvore</a></p>', '5 Ways to Fly!', 'Whatever your style, whatever the occasion, Emily Rothschild''s Wing Collection for ICU will have you flying high.  From formal affairs, to fun with friends, follow our guide below to make sure you''ve got the right wings for your style.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '5-ways-to-fly', '', '', '2011-06-01 11:50:00', '2011-06-01 09:50:00', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5979', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(5993, 8, '2011-06-02 15:20:50', '2011-06-02 13:20:50', 'Moving across the globe, this week <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> has found its muse in Poland. <a href="http://alicepoint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Alice Point</a> effortlessly mixes up her look by pairing casual with formal, prints with solids, and brights with blacks, and always topping off each ensemble with a fierce combination of accessories. As a local fashion leader, her edgy street style keeps us on our toes and makes her our Blogger of the Week. Check out <a href="http://alicepoint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Alice''s</a> style below and see how it inspires <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5994" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/alice-point-1-1024x855.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="496" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">The best casual 90s-inspired looks culminate in layers of big silver jewelry. Follow <a href="http://alicepoint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Alice''s</a> lead by starting out with a long statement necklace, like <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/medical-usb-locket.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Medical USB Locket</a>, and following up with a mix of bold rings:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-wishyouwell-ring.html" target="_blank"> Charlotte Martyr''s Wishyouwell Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-skeleton-ring.html" target="_blank">Skeleton Ring</a>, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cloud-ring.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Cloud Ring</a>.</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5995" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/alice-point-2-1024x855.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="496" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Irony never looked so sweet! The perfect sartorial sensation, <a href="http://alicepoint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Alice</a> caps off a skeletal statement with three simple and bold silver accessories. ICU''s recommended trifecta: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-silver-trixy-bracelet-13.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton''s Trixy Cuff</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Silver Wing Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Silver Caroline Ring.</a></p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-5996" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/alice-point-3-1024x855.jpg" alt="" width="595" height="496" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">We love <a href="http://alicepoint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Alice''s</a> nighttime vibe, it''s the perfect mix of sweet, sass, and edge. Add some sparkle to a little black dress by mixing your materials and metals. Start with a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/coralie-de-seynes-bracelet-mors-grey-leather-gun-metal.html" target="_blank">Grey Leather and Silver Chain Bracelet from Coralie de Seynes</a>, and the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Bracelet from Charlotte Martyr</a>. Top off the look with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">ebb.and.pflow''s Striate Grandissimo Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s White Quartz Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s White Wing Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Please enjoy <a href="http://alicepoint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Alice''s blog</a> and shop all looks at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>HURRY</strong>! From now until tomorrow at midnight all products at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a> are <strong>15%</strong> off!</p>\n&nbsp;', 'Blogger of the Week: Alice Point', 'Moving across the globe, this week ICU has found its muse in Poland.  Alice Point effortlessly mixes up her look by pairing casual with formal, prints with solids, and brights with blacks, and always topping off each ensemble with a fierce combination of accessories.  As a local fashion leader, her edgy street style keeps us on our toes and makes her our Blogger of the Week.  Check out Alice''s style below and see how it inspires ICU.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-alice-point', '', '', '2011-06-02 15:20:50', '2011-06-02 13:20:50', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=5993', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6001, 8, '2011-06-03 11:36:51', '2011-06-03 09:36:51', 'We are officially into June now and the temperatures are up! With a weekend ranging from a hot 28 to a wet 23, there''s no reason to stay inside anymore. Grab a towel and head to a park, sit on your stoop to watch the people pass, or just walk around and enjoy the sweet smell of sun. Whatever you do make sure to take <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> along for the ride.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6002" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0604.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">You don''t have to get a tan to feel sun kissed! Rock a range of sun dried colors from soft peach all the way to deep cherry. Keep the accessories simple and fun for your silky retro pajama look, and add on <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Double Sided Spinner Necklace</a>, a delicate little medallion that spins to illustrate a sweet dancing couple.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/diamond-bracelet.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6003" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0605.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Give the rain something to fear by dressing with attitude on Sunday. For a colorful street vibe mix bright cut-off shorts, with a bright cut-off vest, and your favorite old trusty white tee and sneaks. Then ask yourself one question: is it the thought or the value that counts most? Answer it with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/diamond-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Diamond Bracelet</a>. With "Diamond" spelled out in stainless steel, it is in fact the thought that counts.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">For a full list of forecast items and more styling tips from <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> check out <a href="http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/profile?id=2475640" target="_blank">Polyvore.</a></p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'We are officially into June now and the temperatures are up!  With a weekend ranging from a hot 28 to a wet 23, there''s no reason to stay inside anymore.  Grab a towel and head to a park, sit on your stoop to watch the people pass, or just walk around and enjoy the sweet smell of sun.  Whatever you do make sure to take ICU along for the ride.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-10', '', '', '2011-06-03 11:36:51', '2011-06-03 09:36:51', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6001', 0, 'post', '', 0),
