(6013, 8, '2011-06-06 11:28:35', '2011-06-06 09:28:35', 'There''s no better way to start your week than with a story, and there''s no better way to tell a story than with jewelry. <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> founder, Christan Summers, is keeping herself stylishly entertained with her pick of the week,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html" target="_blank"> Emily Rothschild''s Double-sided Dancing Couple Spinner Necklace</a>.\n\n"I love the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html" target="_blank">Dancing Couple Spinner Necklace</a> because it has movement and animation and tells the story of a swing dancing couple. When you spin the medallion it looks like the man and woman from either side are dancing together."\n\nWhat else is Christan wearing her <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html" target="_blank">spinner necklace</a> with?\n<p style="text-align: left;">"I love to layer the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html" target="_blank">Dancing Couple Spinner Necklace</a> with other long chains. And the gold finish on the medallion makes it really nice to mix with other metals, like the silver <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladimir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Vladimir Ring from Charlotte Martyr</a>. The antique silver finish of the ring is a perfect contrast to the smooth gold and enamel of the necklace. I''m sticking with the 50s vibe of the dancers and rocking my two picks of the week with a silky blouse and high-wasited cigarette pants."</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6016" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/icuinparis_emily-rothschild_reversible-medallion-necklace_02-copy1.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="557" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Shop Christan''s picks of the week here:</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spin-off-medallion-necklace-dancing-couple.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild Double-Sided Dancing Couple Spinner Necklace</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladimir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Vladimir Ring</a></p>', 'Christan&#039;s Pick of the Week', 'There''s no better way to start your week than with a story, and there''s no better way to tell a story than with jewelry.  ICU founder, Chrstian Summers, is keeping herself stylishly entertained with her pick of the week, Emily Rothschild''s Double-sided Dancing Couple Spinner Necklace.  ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'christans-pick-of-the-week-7', '', '', '2011-06-06 11:28:35', '2011-06-06 09:28:35', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6013', 0, 'post', '', 0),
