(6040, 8, '2011-06-09 12:00:35', '2011-06-09 10:00:35', 'For <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> Blogger of the Week, we''re keeping cool in New York celebrating the sumptuous styling of Gabi from <a href="http://www.youngfatandfabulous.com/" target="_blank">Young, Fat, &amp; Fabulous</a>. From her sassy street looks to glamorous poolside vibe, she shows an unwavering love for bold fashion statements and equally bold jewels. Gabi''s ability to embrace what makes her unique, and express her individuality and joy through styling is what has inspired <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> fabulous summer mixes.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6041" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/youngfatfab-1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Put yourself at the top of the fashion food chain with <a href="http://www.youngfatandfabulous.com/" target="_blank">Gabi''s</a> stylish animal inspiration. Compliment a spotted top with the chunky chain and lion head of Lenaklax''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/resin-lion-necklace-grey.html" target="_blank">Resin Lion Necklace</a>. Stay gilded with the combination of Fiona Paxton''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-brass-trixy-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Trixy Cuff </a>and Noot''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Gold Bangles</a> on one hand, and a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-crystal-ring.html" target="_blank">Gold Wishyouwell Ring</a> from Charlotte Martyr on the other.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Shop the look:</strong> Lenaklax<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/resin-lion-necklace-grey.html" target="_blank">Resin Lion Necklace</a>,Fiona Paxton<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-brass-trixy-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Trixy Cuff</a>,Noot<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Gold Bangles</a>, Charlotte Martyr<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-crystal-ring.html" target="_blank">Gold Wishyouwell Ring</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6042" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/youngfatfab-2.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\nFollow <a href="http://www.youngfatandfabulous.com/" target="_blank">Gabi''s</a> lead to score the ultimate in glamorous poolside style. Embrace your curves with three strong gold pieces that are sure to draw attention and compliments: Philip Crangi''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/philip-crangi-leaf-screen-earrings.html" target="_blank">Leaf Screen Earrings</a> will frame your face perfectly, while Charlotte Martyr''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Sabrina Cuff</a> and Emily Rothschild''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Wing Ring</a> will add an elegant flourish below.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:</strong> Philip Crangi<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/philip-crangi-leaf-screen-earrings.html" target="_blank">Leaf Screen Earrings</a>,Charlotte Martyr<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Sabrina Cuff</a>,Emily Rothschild<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Wing Ring</a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6043" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/youngfatfab-3.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\nWe love <a href="http://www.youngfatandfabulous.com/" target="_blank">Gabi''s</a> eclectic layering of necklaces against a textured black top. Add color to your look with the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-purple-agate-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gold Dipped Purple Agate Necklace</a> from Astraleye and mix in Noot''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-necklace-long.html" target="_blank">Popcorn Necklace </a>and the fine chain work of Lisa Levine''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/double-spike-necklace.html" target="_blank">Double Spike Necklace</a>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: </strong>Astraleye<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-dipped-purple-agate-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gold Dipped Purple Agate Necklace</a>,Noot<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-necklace-long.html" target="_blank">Popcorn Necklace</a>,Lisa Levine<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/double-spike-necklace.html" target="_blank">Double Spike Necklace</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;">Check out Gabi''s style at <a href="http://www.youngfatandfabulous.com/" target="_blank">Young, Fat &amp; Fabulous</a> and shop all jewelry at <a title="icuinparis.com" href="www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Gabi of Young, Fat and Fabulous', 'For ICU''s Blogger of the Week, we''re keeping cool in New York celebrating the sumptuous styling of Gabi from Young, Fat, &amp; Fabulous.  Three small words with three big meanings, and she embodies them all!  From her sassy street looks to glamorous poolside vibe, she shows an unwavering love for bold fashion statements and equally bold jewels.  Her ability to embrace what makes her unique, and express her individuality and joy through styling is what has inspired ICU''s fabulous summer mixes.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-young-fat-and-fabulous', '', '', '2011-06-09 12:00:35', '2011-06-09 10:00:35', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6040', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6056, 8, '2011-06-10 19:33:28', '2011-06-10 17:33:28', 'Lately the weather has been a rollercoaster of ups-and-downs, but this weekend is a welcome change! A steady 21-22 degrees makes it the perfect weekend to kick off the picnic season! Make sure you''re rocking <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s </a>fabulous summer jewels to ensure standout style from atop your picnic blanket.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6064" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0611.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Start your weekend with a profusion of flowers: you can browse your nearest botanical market or head out for a wild forest adventure. Whatever you do make sure to stop and smell the roses! For a festive floral look rock rose printed shorts and a ruffle top in shades of red and fuschia. Contrast with an accessory palette of soft aqua sandals, teal sunnies, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/turquoise-magnetic-key-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Turquoise Magnetic Key Ring.</a></p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6065" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0612.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">No picnic is complete without a visit from some furry woodland creatures, so come prepared with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vlady-rabbit-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Gold Rabbit Ring</a>. To compliment the golden hare, mix neutral shades of denim with white lace and rafia. Top off your seasonally sensational look with a mix of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Gold and Silver Geometric Bangles from Noot</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">See all weekend looks at <a href="http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/profile?id=2475640" target="_blank">Polyvore</a>, and shop all weekend jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'Lately the weather has been a rollercoaster of ups-and-downs, but this weekend is a welcome change!  A steady 21-22 degrees makes it the perfect weekend to kick off the picnic season!  Make sure you''re rocking ICU''s fabulous summer jewels to ensure standout style from atop your picnic blanket.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-11', '', '', '2011-06-10 19:33:28', '2011-06-10 17:33:28', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6056', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6068, 8, '2011-06-13 13:03:14', '2011-06-13 11:03:14', '<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> founder Christan Summers is feeling the picnic spirit! In honor of Paris'' picnic kickoff weekend she''s sporting a feminine and picturesque look. Here to help take that look to the next level are two of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> best summer accessories: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vintage-gold-floral-brooch.html" target="_blank">Laure Mory''s Vintage Gold Floral Brooch</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Wing Necklace</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n"I''m wearing the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vintage-gold-floral-brooch.html" target="_blank">Vintage Gold Floral Brooch</a> because it''s classically feminine and delicate, and I love how the hanging chains create movement when I walk. It goes perfectly with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Wing Necklace</a> because they both have timeless designs. The wings of the necklace and the thin chain give it an airy and ethereal quality that is just fabulous for summer. In keeping with the soft and elegant feel of the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vintage-gold-floral-brooch.html" target="_blank">Vintage Gold Floral Brooch</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html" target="_blank">Wing Necklace</a>, I''m loving layering over vintage silk blouses and woven espadrille wedges.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vintage-gold-floral-brooch.html"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6070" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/lore-mory_icuinparis_gold-flower-brooch_02-682x1024.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="400" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6071" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/NOOT-bijoux-wings-necklace-gold-icu-in-paris--C.-Geisselmann.jpg" alt="" width="298" height="446" /></a>Click to shop:</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vintage-gold-floral-brooch.html" target="_blank">Laure Mory Vintage Gold Floral Brooch</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot Wing Necklace</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">And <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?limit=all&amp;style=145" target="_blank">click here to shop all of ICU''s summer Picnic styles!</a></p>', 'Christan&#039;s Pick of the Week: June 13th 2011', 'ICU founder Christan Summer''s is feeling the picnic spirit!  In honor of Paris'' picnic kickoff weekend she''s sporting a feminine and picturesque look.  Here to help take her look to the next level are two of ICU''s best summer accessories: Laure Mory''s Vintage Gold Floral Brooch and Noot''s Wing Necklace.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '6068', '', '', '2011-06-13 13:03:14', '2011-06-13 11:03:14', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6068', 0, 'post', '', 0),
