(6090, 8, '2011-06-15 12:30:35', '2011-06-15 10:30:35', 'Summer has arrived and so has the picnic season along with it. Regardless of what time zone you''re in it''s time to grab those blankets, pack up those baskets, and head out with good friends and a good menu. Follow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?style=145" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> tips below to make sure your picnic style is up to par whether you''re feeling sweet, sassy, vintage or classy.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6098" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-13-at-4.031.jpg" alt="" width="607" height="558" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">On Trend On the Grass</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">For perfectly on trend attire it''s essential to mix this summer''s key elements: from espadrille soles to ditsy florals and dewy petal pink makeup. Keep cool in a pair of short shorts with a navy top and low wedges, sunshine gold and silver stud earrings and a gold wing necklace.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/wing-necklace.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Gold Wing Necklace.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/two-toned-sonrisa-limon-studs.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Sunshine Limon Earrings.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6097" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-13-at-4.021.jpg" alt="" width="631" height="435" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Where Romance Was Born</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">For sweet summer nights pile on a neutral palette of ruffles in cascades and tiers. Combine an off white blouse with pale lilac skirt for a delicate look and spice it up with romantic red lips and a touch of emerald around the toes. Accessorize elegantly with a long and graceful Popcorn Necklace, and the charming hand-tied silver chain Knot Ring.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-necklace-long.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Popcorn Necklace</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Silver Knot Ring.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6099" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-13-at-4.041.jpg" alt="" width="521" height="515" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Free Spirits</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Nothing says freedom like a golden sunset warming a chilled drink in the grass. Embrace nature''s metallic glow by sporting a golden maxi skirt and brown suede fringe vest. Accentuate with even more gold by adding on a thin tubular Gold Bar Necklace and a few Geometric Stackable Rings. ICU''s jewels will give you a golden sheen even the sun would be jealous of.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bar-necklace.html" target="_blank">Click here to shop Gold Bar Necklace.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Click here to shop Geometric Stackable Rings.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6100" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-13-at-4.071.jpg" alt="" width="455" height="413" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Vintage Feel</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Channel a 1940s starlet with soft waves in your hair, wedge platforms and tailored floral trousers. Keep the palette simple with creams and reds, and a touch of tan and green. For delicate yet eye catching glamour feature the Gold Eyelash Necklace against a plain white background, and compliment the old hollywood look with an arm of jingling bangles and a dreamy cloud ring.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Gold Eyelash Necklace.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Geometric Bangles.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cloud-ring.html" target="_blank">Click to shop Cloud Ring.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?style=145" target="_blank">Shop all of ICU''s summer picnic jewels here!</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Screen-shot-2011-06-13-at-4.07.jpg">\n</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>', 'Life&#039;s a Picnic!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lifes-a-picnic', '', '', '2011-06-15 12:30:35', '2011-06-15 10:30:35', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6090', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(6108, 8, '2011-06-16 12:30:55', '2011-06-16 10:30:55', 'In honor if <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?style=145" target="_blank">picnic hommage</a> we have a very special Blogger of the Week. Full of color, style and pizzaz, Shanshan333 from <a href="http://webblog.tinytoadstool.com/" target="_blank">Tinytoadstool</a> makes us want to jump up and down in celebration of summer weather and afternoons spent laying out in the sun with a full spread of delicious edibles. Below, follow <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> tinytoadstool-inspired steps to a harmoniously varied set of jewels to accent your summer sun!\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6109" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/tinytoadstool-1.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="585" /></a>\n\nJump for joy in a pretty petticoated skirt and sweet polka dot blouse. Put a modern twist on Shanshan''s classic 50s nod with a mix of colors and textures. Start with a bold bracelet statement, mixing golds on one wrist with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-fifi-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton''s Fifi Cuff </a>and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-hugh.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq''s Hugh Bracelet</a>, and letting fringe mix and mingle on the other wrist with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=fringe+bracelet" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif''s Fringe Bracelets</a> in Pink and Black. Focus on one statement ring with the fly away summer sensation <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Gold Wing Ring by Emily Rothschild</a>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-pink-fringe-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif Pink Fringe Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=lamia+benalycherif" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif Black Fringe Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-fifi-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Fifi Cuff</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild Gold Wing Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-hugh.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq Gold Hugh Bracelet</a>.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6110" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/tinytoadstool-2.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="585" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">We love Shanshan''s playful take on feminine classics. With striped over-the-knee socks, a polka dot dress and flowered hat keep the accessories simple with a trio of whimsical rings. Sport the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/feather-bow-ring.html" target="_blank">Papillon Feather Bow Ring from Laure Mory</a>, and balance out the dramatic black and gold with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/purple-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Purple Quartz Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/turquoise-magnetic-key-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Turquoise Magnetic Key Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/purple-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Purple Quartz Ring</a>, E<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/turquoise-magnetic-key-ring.html" target="_blank">mily Rothschild Turquoise Magnetic Key Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/feather-bow-ring.html" target="_blank">Laure Mory Papillon Feather Bow Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6111" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/tinytoadstool-3.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="585" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Create a perfect ode to summer by starting your look with a dramatic floral kimono top and your favorite trusty denim shorts. Add a striking element of texture and color with the beaded <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-pink-fringe-necklace.html" target="_blank">Pink Fringe Necklace by Lamia Benalycherif</a>. For the perfect touch of sparkle and shine mix in <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-brass-trixy-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton''s Trixy Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Geometric Bangles</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Blue Quartz Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot Geometric Bangle</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-pink-fringe-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif Pink Fringe Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-brass-trixy-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Trixy Cuff</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Blue Quartz Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Check out Shanshan''s style at <a href="http://webblog.tinytoadstool.com/" target="_blank">Tinytoadstool</a> and shop all Picnic Jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?style=145" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Tiny Toadstool', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-tiny-toadstool', '', '', '2011-06-16 12:30:55', '2011-06-16 10:30:55', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6108', 0, 'post', '', 0),
