(6157, 8, '2011-06-17 12:30:49', '2011-06-17 10:30:49', 'With weather that''s breezy one minute and scorching the next it''s important that you stay cool in this summer hottest accessories, and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is here to help. Follow our tips below to let the picnics carry on all weekend long!\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6158" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0618.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nMove your picnic indoors Saturday if the scattered rain showers persist, and take inspiration from the grey weather and spots of sunshine. Create a casual look in a desaturated palette of black and white trousers, a grey tank and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s White Wing Ring</a>. Dial up the pattern play with some leopard print footwear and add a touch of color and warmth with the bright sunshine <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/crochet-summer-scarf-yellow.html" target="_blank">Crochet Summer Scarf from Ariane Haas</a>.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6159" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0619.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nMore is more when it comes to color on Sunday, so don''t be afraid to create unusual mixes that will stand out from a picnic blanket. Pair thick stripes with patterned shorts, all wonderfully clashing summer''s fruity palette of pink, red and tangerine. Throw on a coral hat and caramel shades, and to add a retro flare top off with white woven oxfords and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-retrodots-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange''s Polka Dot Bow Tie</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop the weekend accessories accessories at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop other picnic perfect looks <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?style=145" target="_blank">here</a>!</p>', 'Paris Weekend Weather Forecast', 'With weather that''s breezy one minute and scorching the next it''s important that you stay cool in this summer hottest accessories, and ICU is here to help.  Follow our tips below to let the picnics carry on all weekend long!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-weather-forecast', '', '', '2011-06-17 12:30:49', '2011-06-17 10:30:49', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6157', 0, 'post', '', 0),
