(6173, 4, '2011-06-20 14:23:29', '2011-06-20 12:23:29', 'Back again for a new week of <a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU</a> bejeweling! As per quota, it''s Monday therefore its a pick of the day for Ms. Summers, ICU''s owner and founder. So, this week in honor of this weekend''s <a title="Soon Famous Vernissage" href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous Vernissage</a> Christan has chosen <a title="Laure Mory, icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/reversible-glass-pendant-necklace.html" target="_blank">Laure Mory''s Vintage Double Sided Necklace</a>... however, it is a one of a kind, so we''ll see if it is shows to exhibit at the event!\n\nChristan claims, "I love long necklaces, in French they call this style of necklace a sautoir, I think its fantastic they have a name for this style, in English we just call them long necklaces! : ) Apart from the fact I can layer this piece with everything, I can also flip it and wear the pendant on the side of my choice: either a deep jade green colored cabochon or a silver/gold colored desert image of a man and his camel. Honestly, this piece is sublime - and a total one of a kind!!"\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/rock-n-green-sautoir-a1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6175" title="rock-n-green-sautoir-a1" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/rock-n-green-sautoir-a1.jpg" alt="laure mory vintage sautoir, icuinparis.com" width="350" height="525" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6174" title="laure-mory-vintage-necklace-from-paris_-icuinparis_-long-nkl_-dessert-pendant-b2" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/laure-mory-vintage-necklace-from-paris_-icuinparis_-long-nkl_-dessert-pendant-b2.jpg" alt="laure mory vintage sautoir, icuinparis.com" width="350" height="525" />