(6202, 8, '2011-06-23 18:05:51', '2011-06-23 16:05:51', '<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> has nothing but animals on the brain after our ferocious <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/animal_jewelry.html" target="_blank">Animal Rules</a> photoshoot with French fashion bloggers <a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">Stephanie</a> and <a href="http://www.paulinefashionblog.com/" target="_blank">Pauline</a> where we dish out the rules of wearing animal jewels. Fresh from the jungle,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is absolutely smitten with the delicate styling of <a href="http://www.fashionsalade.com/mellowmayoness/" target="_blank">Mayo Wo from Mellow Mayoness</a>. With chic ensembles comprised of pretty prints, colors, and standout accessories, there''s no better pick for Blogger of the Week than this self proclaimed "granny from Hong Kong". A true appreciator of all things sweet and sassy, check out our styling below to see how <a href="http://www.fashionsalade.com/mellowmayoness/" target="_blank">Mayo Wo</a> fits into <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a> forest of friendly creatures.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6203" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/mellowmayoness-1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="410" /></a></p>\nCreate the perfect high contrast balance between soft and hard by following <a href="http://www.fashionsalade.com/mellowmayoness/" target="_blank">Mayo Wo</a>''s steps to style. Put on a textured black sweater dress and add a selection of striking silver jewelry. Start with a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Cat Ring</a>, stack the shiny <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle-164.html" target="_blank">Handcrafted Bangle</a> with the leather and chain <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-silver-trixy-bracelet-13.html" target="_blank">Trixy Cuff</a>, and add a touch of color with a pair of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/calico-earrings.html" target="_blank">Red Feather Earrings</a>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Cat Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-silver-trixy-bracelet-13.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Silver Trixy Cuff</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle-164.html" target="_blank">Anna Beck Large Handcrafted Bangle</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/calico-earrings.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Feather Earrings</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6204" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/mellowmayoness-2.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\nMixing metals is one of ICU''s favorite pastimes, and<a href="http://www.fashionsalade.com/mellowmayoness/" target="_blank">Mayo Wo</a> has perfected the art of assemblage. Gild your fingers with two statement rings: the crystal inspired <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-caroline-ring.html" target="_blank">Caroline Ring</a>, and the puurrrfect <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Gold Cat Ring</a>. Wrap your wrists in silver with the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Popcorn Bracelet</a> on one arm and a delicate <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver.html" target="_blank">Knot Bracelet</a> on the other. Now all you need is your favorite book to complete the look!\n\n<strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/popcorn-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Noot Popcorn Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot Silve Knot Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-caroline-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Gold Caroline Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Gold Cat Ring</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6205" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/mellowmayoness-3.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\nThe most important rule of all when it comes to jewels: mix and match! Create a cocktail of gold rings with a mixed statement of animals, treasures, and delicate geometry. Layer statement pieces including, but not limited to: the toothy <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-vladimir-ring.html" target="_blank">Vladimir Ring</a>, flighty <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Wing Ring</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-mini-pinky-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Mini Pinky Wing Ring</a>, a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Knot Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vlady-rabbit-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Rabbit Ring</a>, and at least one<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank"> Thin Stackable Ring</a>. Balance it out with a bright necklace of fabric, fringe and beads like this <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-pink-fringe-necklace.html" target="_blank">Pink Fringe Necklace</a>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-pink-fringe-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif Pink Fringe Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-vladimir-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Gold Vladimir Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild Gold Wing Ring</a><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-mini-pinky-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">, Emily Rothschild Mini Pinky Wing Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-ring-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Knot Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vlady-rabbit-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Gold Rabbit Ring</a>, Noot<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Gold Thing Stackable Ring</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">Click <a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">HERE</a> to check out <a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s Animal Rules</a> editorial with Stephanie of<a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank"> </a><a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">leblogdebigbeauty.com</a> and Pauline of <a href="http://www.paulinefashionblog.com/" target="_blank">paulinefashionblog.com</a> to find out more about how to wear your animals.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Check out the delicious styling of <a href="http://www.fashionsalade.com/mellowmayoness/" target="_blank">Mayo Wo at Mello Mayoness.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop all looks at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Mellow Mayoness', 'ICU has nothing but animals on the brain after a ferocious photoshoot with French fashion bloggers Stephanie and Pauline where we dish out the rules of wearing animal jewels.  Fresh from the jungle, ICU is absolutely smitten with the delicate styling of Mayo Wo from Mellow Mayoness.  With chic ensembles comprised of pretty prints, colors, and standout accessories, there''s no better pick for Blogger of the Week than this self proclaimed "granny from Hong Kong".  A true appreciator of all things sweet and sassy, check out our styling below to see how Mayo Wo fits into ICU''s forest of friendly creatures.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-mellow-mayoness', '', '', '2011-06-23 18:05:51', '2011-06-23 16:05:51', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6202', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6220, 4, '2011-06-24 11:24:25', '2011-06-24 09:24:25', '<a title="www.icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"><img class="CtreTexte aligncenter" src="http://img.over-blog.com/598x397/2/84/11/88/06.2011/ICU-by-laure/ICU-by-laure-0148.jpg" alt="ICU-by-laure 0148" width="598" height="397" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nIt was a day for the animals, for the big and small critters of the world... A day for creatives to be creative and to create a very special lookbook of animals for you. <a title="ICUINPARIS.COM" href="http://www.ICUINPARIS.COM/" target="_blank">ICUINPARIS.COM</a> collaborated with two of Paris'' biggest fashion bloggers, Pauline of <a title="PaulineFashionblog.com" href="http://www.PaulineFashionblog.com/" target="_blank">PaulineFashionblog.com</a> and Stphanie of <a title="leblogdebigbeauty.com" href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com" target="_blank">leblogdebigbeauty.com</a> for this exclusive <a title="www.icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ANIMAL RULES</a> photo shoot.\n\nPauline and Stphanie helped capture our animals jewels to present to you, <a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.ICUINPARIS.COM/" target="_blank">ICU''s ANIMAL RULES</a>. Whether you''re chasing a petticoated white rabbit into a wonderland of golden jewels, following the yellow brick road with a heart of lion''s gold or hunting your ultimate shimmering score, ICU has the perfect combination of jewels for you.\n\nBelow, our making of and behind the scenes video of this fantastical day in the heart of a Parisian Jungle.\n\nThanks to the whole team for a wonderful day and a superb job well done.\n\nMaking of Photos by: <a title="lauremcgalloway" href="http://lauremcgalloway.com/" target="_blank">Laure Mcgalloway</a> &amp; <a title="christian geisselmann" href="http://christiangeisselmann.com/" target="_blank">Christian Geisselmann </a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/25481395?title=0