(6233, 8, '2011-06-24 11:35:48', '2011-06-24 09:35:48', 'Summer is finally back in Paris! After weeks of daily threats of rain this weekend is promised to be a welcome scorcher with temps in the very high 20s. Keep your fingers crossed that the weather holds out for two days of great animal accessorizing inspired by <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=charlotte+martyr" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a> and a recent <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/06/24/animal-rules-teaser-an-animalistic-making-of/" target="_blank">ICU photoshoot</a> with Stephanie (<a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">leblogdebigbeauty.com</a>) and Pauline (<a href="http://www.paulinefashionblog.com/" target="_blank">paulinefashionblog.com</a>). To make sure you are on point with the jungle jewelry trend stop by <a href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous</a> to get your hands on some <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU treasures</a>!\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-gold.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6234" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0625.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="454" /></a>\n\nGet catty Saturday night with a sexy look inspired by Stephanie of <a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">leblogdebigbeauty.com</a>. Compliment <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/cat-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Gold Cat Ring</a> by slithering into a leopard body and tight printed skirt. Accent with red lips and vixen heels for the puurrrfect touch of femme fatale.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vlady-rabbit-ring-gold.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6235" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/0626.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="487" /></a>\n\nStar in your very own fairytale Sunday with a jump down the rabbit hole into sweet picnic prints and floaty whites. For a perfect afternoon of shopping <a href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous </a>mix a botanical print with lightweight cottons or silks, and basket weave clogs. Add a sweet blush and make sure to take a forest friend along for the ride: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vlady-rabbit-ring-gold.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Gold Rabbit Ring</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Come shop ICU at Soon Famous</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">June 25 &amp; 26, 10h-19h</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">66 rue Rene Boulanger - Paris 10eme</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">free entry!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">www.soon-famous.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Shop the weekend jewels at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</strong></p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'ummer is finally back in Paris!  After weeks of daily threats of rain this weekend is promised to be a welcome scorcher with temps in the very high 20s.  Keep your fingers crossed that the weather holds out for two days of great animal accessorizing inspired by Charlotte Martyr and a recent ICU photoshoot with Stephanie (leblogdebigbeauty.com) and Pauline (paulinefashionblog.com).  To make sure you are on point with the jungle jewelry trend stop by Soon Famous to get your hands on some ICU treasures!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-12', '', '', '2011-06-24 11:35:48', '2011-06-24 09:35:48', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6233', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6246, 8, '2011-06-28 12:37:42', '2011-06-28 10:37:42', '<p style="text-align: center">We are very proud to introduce<strong>ANIMAL RULES</strong>: a highly anticipated collaborative effort between<a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> and two of Paris'' hottest bloggers; Stephanie of<a title="LeBlogDeBigBeauty.com" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-admin/www.LeBlogDeBigBeauty.com" target="_blank">LeBlogDeBigBeauty.com</a> and Pauline of<a title="Paulinefashioblog.com" href="http://www.Paulinefashioblog.com/" target="_blank">Paulinefashioblog.com</a> plus photos by<a title="http://christiangeisselmann.com/" href="http://christiangeisselmann.com/" target="_blank">Christian Geisselman</a>, resulting in the ultimate must-have guide to styling your animal accessories.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/animal_jewelry.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6255" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/magazine-thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="497" height="349" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Read the magazine <a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/animal_jewelry.html" target="_blank">HERE</a> to join us in our jungle adventures as we encounter fierce felines, birds and bunnies, and a few feathered friends.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Check out the behind the scenes making of <a title="icuinparis.com" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/06/24/animal-rules-teaser-an-animalistic-making-of/" target="_blank">HERE</a></p>', 'Welcome to the Jungle', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome-to-the-jungle', '', '', '2011-06-28 12:37:42', '2011-06-28 10:37:42', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6246', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6257, 8, '2011-06-29 13:23:13', '2011-06-29 11:23:13', '<p style="text-align: left;">This past weekend was <a title="soon famous, paris" href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous No. 2</a> in Paris - if you missed it, well... that is too bad because it was truly a delightful event! This time around the variety of exposers was not only unique but refreshing;ranging from sweet city-girl frocks to a men''s collection of clean and sexy lines, parfums of essences that you never imagined to be bottled to a concept illustration of tees... <a title="ICUINPARIS.COM" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICUINPARIS.COM</a> was of course there as well, happily to be in surrounded by such great talent and creativity.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Big thank you to the ladies who organized the event and the musicians and performers who played, the bloggers (ehem... <a title="http://www.flanelleblog.com/" href="http://www.flanelleblog.com/" target="_blank">Miss Aude FlanelleBlog</a> : ) Don''t miss the next event in July and stay tuned as ICU will be presented during the month of August in Biarritz, South of France for an extension of the Soon Famous events!</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Below a couple of shots taken at the event taken from <a title="soon famous" href="http://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.140343146040342.35587.100001939726593" target="_blank">Soon Famous''s Album</a>:</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/267039_140572832684040_100001939726593_260711_4790537_o.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6274" title="soon famous #2, paris event" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/267039_140572832684040_100001939726593_260711_4790537_o-842x1024.jpg" alt="soon famous #2, paris event" width="595" height="723" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/258726_140490056025651_100001939726593_260393_4808482_o.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6271" title="soon famous #2, paris event" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/258726_140490056025651_100001939726593_260393_4808482_o-842x1024.jpg" alt="soon famous #2, paris event" width="595" height="723" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/258017_140569929350997_100001939726593_260703_2018946_o.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6270" title="soon famous, paris" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/258017_140569929350997_100001939726593_260703_2018946_o-842x1024.jpg" alt="soon famous, paris event" width="595" height="723" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/272597_140572936017363_100001939726593_260712_1099927_o.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6275" title="soon famous #2, paris event" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/272597_140572936017363_100001939726593_260712_1099927_o-842x1024.jpg" alt="soon famous #2, paris event, sweet art shop" width="595" height="723" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/272797_140569826017674_100001939726593_260702_6030930_o.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6276" title="soon famous #2, paris event, unsurcinq" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/272797_140569826017674_100001939726593_260702_6030930_o-842x1024.jpg" alt="soon famous #2, paris event, unsurcinq bijoux" width="595" height="723" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/259727_140572586017398_100001939726593_260708_3949962_o.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-6273" title="soon famous #2, paris event" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/259727_140572586017398_100001939726593_260708_3949962_o-842x1024.jpg" alt="soon famous #2, paris event, Moulin rouge 1889 parfum" width="595" height="723" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5 style="text-align: center;"><strong>And an ode to the participated Designers and Exhibitors: </strong></h5>\n<strong>\n</strong>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://www.hedus-philosophy.com/site/?lang=fr" target="_blank"><strong>Hedus</strong></a></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Men''s clothing line, made in France with style, grace, simplicity and absolute class. Georges and Carol are the two designers behind Hdus with a mission to bring to the men''s fashion scene something classic yet unique. The difference in their clothing - the final touch. </span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Visit the Hdus site:<a title="hdus " href="http://www.hedus-philosophy.com/site/?lang=fr" target="_blank">www.hedus-philosophy.com</a></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.hedus-philosophy.com/site/?lang=fr"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6261" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Hedus.png" alt="" width="700" height="248" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://www.rosatapioca.com/site_eng.html" target="_blank"><strong>Rosa Tapioca</strong></a></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">An absolute darling of a designer, Aurelia Wolff is as sweet in person as are her designs. Simplicity mixed with geometric patterns and colors, Aurelie is not afraid to mix materials and make bolder statements in her cuts. Her latest collection speaks to a edgy boho princess who has finally found her clothing match.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Visit Rosa Tapioca''s site here: <a title="rosatapioca" href="http://www.rosatapioca.com/index.html" target="_blank">www.rosatapioca.com </a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.rosatapioca.com/site_eng.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6263" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/roda-tapioca_02.png" alt="" width="672" height="367" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><strong><a href="http://www.lefoulard.fr/" target="_blank">Le Foulard</a></strong></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Like a quilted comfort on your neck, these triangular scarves are not only unique in pattern but also in shape and design. Handmade with a Parisian touch, Eva Taulois has an eye for a mlange of colors and patterns that you may never have thought possible to combine.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Visit Le Foulard''s site here:<a title="le foulard" href="http://www.lefoulard.fr/" target="_blank">www.lefoulard.fr</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.lefoulard.fr/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6262" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Le-Foulard.jpeg" alt="" width="690" height="141" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://charlottewooning.com/page=site.home" target="_blank"><strong>Charlotte Wonning</strong></a></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Hailing all the way from Holland, Charlotte Wonning''s creations are feminine, sweet yet sophisticated. Carefully sourcing her semi-prcious and precious stones to create a collection of jewels that you will undoubtedly make you feel as charming as the sweet color of the stone.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Visit Charlotte Wonning''s site here: <a title="charlotte wooning" href="http://charlottewooning.com/page=site.home" target="_blank">www.charlottewooning.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://charlottewooning.com/page=site.home"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6260" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/Charlotte-Wooning_02.jpeg" alt="" width="649" height="275" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>\n</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><strong><a href="http://www.boubouteatime.com/" target="_blank">Boubouteatime</a></strong></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Funky, cool, Parisian chic. These tees are not only unique but the prints come directly from emerging illustrators - giving them a chance to be seen and seen ; ) Even the blog is like a museum of Brooklyn artists'' wall murals. </span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span>A fantastic place for a daydream and a teetime.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Visit the Boubouteatime site here:<a title="boubouteatime" href="http://www.boubouteatime.com/" target="_blank">www.boubouteatime.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.boubouteatime.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6258" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/boubouteatime.jpeg" alt="" width="714" height="330" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Don''t miss the next Soon Famous July event! </strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Visit the site <a title="soon famous" href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">HERE</a> for all info</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>\n</strong></p>', 'Soon Famous No. 2 - Fantastically Creative', 'This past weekend was Soon Famous No. 2 in Paris - if you missed it, well... that is too bad because it was truly a delightful event! This time around the variety of exposers was not only unique but refreshing; ranging from sweet city-girl frocks to a men''s collection of clean and sexy lines, parfums of essences that you never imagined to be bottled to a concept illustration of tees... ICUINPARIS.COM was of course there as well, happily to be in surrounded by such great talent and creativity. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'soon-famous-no-2-a-fantastically-creative-weekend', '', '', '2011-06-29 13:23:13', '2011-06-29 11:23:13', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6257', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6284, 8, '2011-06-30 13:59:09', '2011-06-30 11:59:09', '<p style="text-align: left;">After our ferocious <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/animal_jewelry.html" target="_blank">Animal Rules photoshoot</a> with <a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">Stephanie</a> and <a href="http://www.paulinefashionblog.com/" target="_blank">Pauline</a> (<a href="http://www.leblogdebigbeauty.com/" target="_blank">leblogdebigbeauty.com</a> and <a href="http://www.paulinefashionblog.com/" target="_blank">paulinefashionblog.com</a>), <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is thrilled to be wading through the pool of French fashion bloggers! From one chic Parisian muse to another, we''ve found our Blogger of the Week in none other than <a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">With a mix of classic fashion pieces and a "no fear" policy when it comes to accessories of all colors, sizes and textures, <a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a> has <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> smitten with her casual elegance. Follow our jewels below to capture a touch of Punky B''s fresh summer style.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6285" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/punky-b_1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="408" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">For a simple summer look of mixed metals follow <a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a>''s lead to a harmonious accessory balance. Start with a statement by sporting a dangling pair of <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/twisted-drop-earrings.html" target="_blank">Twisted Drop Earrings</a></strong> in sterling silver with gold and rose gold tips. Compliment with a delicate <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/18k-gold-and-single-diamond-circle-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gold and Diamond Circle Necklace</a></strong>, and a mix of simple <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver.html" target="_blank">Knot Bracelets</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Bangle Bracelets</a></strong> in gold and silver.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/twisted-drop-earrings.html" target="_blank">ebb.and.pflow Twisted Drop Earrings</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/18k-gold-and-single-diamond-circle-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gorjana Gold and Diamond Circle Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot Silver Knot Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Knot Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Bangle Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot Silver Bangle Bracelet</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6286" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/punky-b_2.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">We love <a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a>''s neutral springtime palette! Compliment shades of beige with a simple melange of stunning jewelry. On one hand pair a swinging <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-black-fringe-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fringe Bracelet</a></strong> with a luminous <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-blue-topaz-ring.html" target="_blank">Blue Topaz Ring</a></strong>, and on the other hand pair a classic gold <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-lucien.html" target="_blank">Lucien Bracelet</a></strong> and two tone <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">Striate Grandissimo Ring</a></strong>. As always punctuate with a pair of unique eye catching earrings like the stunning silver <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-monaco-earrings.html" target="_blank">Monaco Earrings</a></strong> made of leather and chain.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-monaco-earrings.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Monaco Earrings</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-blue-topaz-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila Blue Topaz Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-bracelet-lucien.html" target="_blank"> Unsurcinq Lucien Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">ebbandpflow Striate Grandissimo Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-black-fringe-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif Black Fringe Bracelet</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6287" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/punky-b_3.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">A classic beauty in stripes with a splash of color, <a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a> knows just how to accessorize with personality and elegance. Create a simple combination of the two tone <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Ginger Necklace</a></strong> and a pair of rock rings: the crystal inspired silver <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Caroline Ring</a></strong> and the genuine crystal <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Blue Quartz Ring</a></strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Ginger Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Blue Quartz Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Check out <a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">The Fashion Diary of Punky B</a>, and shop all<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"> ICU</a> jewels at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>!</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Punky B', 'After our ferocious Animal Rules photoshoot with Stephanie and Pauline (leblogdebigbeauty.com and paulinefashionblog.com), ICU is thrilled to be wading through the pool of French fashion bloggers!  From one chic Parisian muse to another, we''ve found our Blogger of the Week in none other than Punky B.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-punky-b', '', '', '2011-06-30 13:59:09', '2011-06-30 11:59:09', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6284', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6301, 4, '2011-07-01 13:56:37', '2011-07-01 11:56:37', 'Today is day one of the two day marriage between Prince Albert II de Monaco and the South African mermaid, CharleneWittstock. After catching the Prince''s eye 10 years ago during a swimming event in Monaco, the couple is finally getting married and the notorious Bachelor life of the Prince will come to an end.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/charlene-albert.jpg"><img title="charlene-albert" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/charlene-albert.jpg" alt="charlene wittstock and prince albert marry" width="320" height="275" /></a></p>\nSo as it may be... in our world of jewels and all that glitters we have been inspired to post a small tribute to a new princess and the jewels we see fit for the radiant woman she has become. Her style is one that we can relate to quite well at <a title="www.icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU</a>; sporty and strong yet elegant and feminine. These are traits we believe every woman possesses and <a title="vogue america charlene wittstock" href="http://www.vogue.com/magazine/article/fit-for-a-princess-charlene-wittstock/" target="_blank">Vogue</a> did a beautiful job at capturing these qualities in the photo shoot below which we used to style.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img-charlene-wittstock_icuinparis-jewelry.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6314" title="img-charlene-wittstock_icuinparis-jewelry" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img-charlene-wittstock_icuinparis-jewelry.jpg" alt="icuinparis jewelry for charlene wittstock" width="500" height="475" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nShop the look: Emily Rothschild <a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html" target="_blank">Gold Wing Stud Earrings</a>, Noot Stackable <a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Silver and 18k Gold Rings</a> &amp; Gorjana <a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/grey-diamond-cluster-necklace-161.html" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/grey-diamond-cluster-necklace-161.html" target="_blank">18k Gold &amp; Black Diamond Necklace</a>.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/charlene-albert.jpg">\n</a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img-charlene-wittstock_icuinparis-jewelry-for-a-princess.jpg"></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/charlene-albert1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6317" title="charlene-albert" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/charlene-albert1.jpg" alt="icuinparis jewelry for charlene wittstock" width="590" height="423" /></a>Shop the look: Noot <a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Silver &amp; 18k Gold Stackable Bangles</a>, Shamila <a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Violet Amethyst Ring</a>, Zhen U.N. <a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/tourmaline-sapphire-drop-earrings.html" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/tourmaline-sapphire-drop-earrings.html" target="_blank">Full Bloom Tourmaline &amp; Sapphire Dangle Earrings</a></p>', 'Jewels Fit For A Princess', 'Today is day one of the two day marriage between Prince Albert II de Monaco and the South African mermaid, Charlene Wittstock. After catching the Prince''s eye 10 years ago during a swimming event in Monaco, the couple is finally getting married and the notorious Bachelor life of the Prince will come to an end. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jewels-fit-for-a-princess', '', '', '2011-07-01 13:56:37', '2011-07-01 11:56:37', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6301', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6306, 8, '2011-07-01 13:01:40', '2011-07-01 11:01:40', 'It''s nothing but sun this weekend in Paris and we are very excited to keep summer style going with ICU''s animal jewels. Meow, purr, growl-- do whatever you have to to bring out your inner fashion animal and rule the jungle!\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-vlady-rabbit-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6307" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/0702.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">For Saturday''s sun keep to a bold palette of classic contrast. Give a nod to the vintage by cuffing your high waisted shorts and tucking in a black and white tee. Make your feet pop with some cherry red clogs. Add a touch of sparkle with a mischievous little rabbit friend around your neck: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-gold-vlady-rabbit-necklace.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s <strong>Gold Vlady Rabbit Necklace</strong></a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/resin-lion-necklace.html#"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6308" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/0703.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Create a color whirl Sunday by daring to wear every color you have. Think outside the rainbow box and ground your turquoise, yellow, green and watermelon combinations with a bit of black and a simple flat sandal. For that extra oomph to chase away a few scattered clouds, top off your look with the proud <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/resin-lion-necklace.html#" target="_blank"><strong>Blue Lion Resin Necklace</strong> from Lenaklax</a>-- a little dimension and bling for your color clash.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Shop</strong> the weekend accessories at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">HERE</a>!</p>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'It''s nothing but sun this weekend in Paris and we are very excited to keep summer style going with ICU''s animal jewels.  Meow, purr, growl-- do whatever you have to to bring out your inner fashion animal and rule the jungle!', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-13', '', '', '2011-07-01 13:01:40', '2011-07-01 11:01:40', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6306', 0, 'post', '', 0);
