(6322, 8, '2011-07-04 11:22:29', '2011-07-04 09:22:29', 'A very special Pick of the Week for July 4th finds <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> founder Christan Summers celebrating Independence Day with independent design. In honor of the stars and stripes Christan is proudly sporting the red, white and blue of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-african-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange''s <strong>African Batik Bow</strong></a>.\n\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6326" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/african_print_b_def1.jpeg" alt="" width="350" height="287" />\n\nFor perfect beach-to-barbecue style Christan pairs the <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-african-bow.html" target="_blank">African Batik Bow</a> </strong>with a white collared shirt and espadrilles. And of course her favorite denim jacket for that extra oomph of American girl pride. To add a little sparkle top off the look with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/two-toned-sonrisa-limon-studs.html" target="_blank">ebbandpflow''s <strong>Two-Toned Sonrisa Limon Earrings</strong></a>.\n\n"As an American living in Paris I miss out on all the festivities, so I''m doing what I can in red, white and blue. And as a nod to the fireworks I''m missing I''ve got on my <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/two-toned-sonrisa-limon-studs.html" target="_blank">Two-Toned Sonrisa Limon Earrings</a></strong>, because the silver and gold remind me of a burst of fireworks in the sky."\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/two-toned-sonrisa-limon-studs.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6325" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/ebbandpflow-18k-gold-and-silver-two-toned-stud-earrings-sun-stud-earrings-cover.jpg" alt="" width="405" height="269" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">To get C