(6335, 8, '2011-07-06 16:30:27', '2011-07-06 14:30:27', 'School''s out but there''s still time for one more lesson. Prices have dropped for <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=noot" target="_blank">all Noot jewelry </a>from 10%-25% off and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> is giving you an exclusive style guide for bracelets, rings and necklaces all from Noot''s beautiful 18k gold and sterling silver collection based on nature''s organic geometry. Get your pencils sharpened and take notes because it''s time for the ultimate geometry lesson.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-la-ruche-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6337" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-06-at-2.23.48-PM.png" alt="" width="529" height="523" /></a>\n\nFor a sleek and high drama look pair <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-la-ruche-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Two Tone Geometric Necklace </a>with a sheer black dress layered over black shorts. Keep accessories bold and colorful with garnet nails and a deep earth toned bag. Whether framed by a wide scoop neck or paired with a collared neckline the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-la-ruche-necklace.html" target="_blank">Two Tone Geometric Necklace</a> never fails to catch attention!\n\nShop Noot''s Two Tone Geometric Necklace <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-la-ruche-necklace.html" target="_blank">here</a>.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6336" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Screen-shot-2011-07-06-at-1.32.47-PM.png" alt="" width="576" height="581" /></a>\n\nKeep your look casual and comfortable in order to showcase the jingling <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Geometric Bangle Bracelets from Noot</a>. Layer silver and gold for a mixed metal 