(6345, 8, '2011-07-07 15:37:48', '2011-07-07 13:37:48', '<p style="text-align: left">For Blogger of the Week ICU is headed to Hong Kong where we''re taking delight in the delightful stylings of Sam from <a href="http://www.samishome.com/blog" target="_blank">samishome.com</a>. From bold brights to soft greys she knows just how to dress to impress and leave a lasting impression with carefully chosen and well curated accessories. Check out her looks below and ICU''s inspired styling to capture <a href="http://www.samishome.com/blog" target="_blank">Sam''s</a> elegant sartorial sensations.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6346" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/sam-is-home-1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="410" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">For a classic and bold look complement a simple black-grey-white combo with a statement necklace like <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton''s </a>two tone<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank"> Ginger Necklace</a>. Create lapel interest with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-silver-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena''s Silver Mirror Flower Brooch</a> and add a dash of color with <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-blue-topaz-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila''s Blue Topaz Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center">Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Ginger Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-silver-flower-mirror-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Silver Mirror Flower Brooch</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-blue-topaz-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila Blue Topaz Ring</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www