(6439, 8, '2011-07-15 13:22:16', '2011-07-15 11:22:16', 'This weekend is a mixed bag with mild temperatures accompanied by sun on Saturday and early morning showers on Sunday. <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">ICU</a> is styling with bold gold jewels and summer''s favorite sale pieces. Follow our looks below to bring a touch of Parisian street style into your weekend wardrobe.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6440" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/0716.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nFor Saturday''s sun keep your look soft and sweet. Couple a finely knit tank with mustard shorts and woven wedges, and add a retro no fuss touch with a scarf in your hair and lace socks. Fly away with a pair of <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s <strong>White Wing Rings</strong></a> for a true fashion statement. You''re in luck because they''re over 20% off on the <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">ICU boutique</a> right now!\n\n<strong>Shop Emily Rothschild White Wing Ring <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/white-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6441" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/0717.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nEnjoy the last day of your holiday weekend with a celebration of pattern play. Mix leopard with floral, checks and a sheer. With some wedges that pop in royal blue and navy, gold glitter nails and Charlotte Martyr''s crystal inspired <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Bracelet</a></strong> you''re sure to create a memorable look to brighten up a cloudy day.\n\n<strong>Shop Charlotte Martyr Gold Sabrina Bracelet <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong>', 'Paris Weekend Forecast with Charlotte Martyr &amp; Emily Rothschild', 'This weekend is a mixed bag with mild temperatures accompanied by sun on Saturday and early morning showers on Sunday.  ICU is styling with bold gold jewels and summer''s favorite sale pieces.  Follow our looks below to bring a touch of Parisian street style into your weekend wardrobe.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-with-charlotte-martyr-emily-rothschild', '', '', '2011-07-15 13:22:16', '2011-07-15 11:22:16', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6439', 0, 'post', '', 0),
