(6449, 8, '2011-07-20 12:59:28', '2011-07-20 10:59:28', 'We are nearly half way through the summer season and it''s about time we all took a little holiday! <a href="www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU</a> is here to help, whether you''re going breezy boating, trendy boardwalk or scorching sand we''ve got the perfect vacation looks for you. Browse through a sampling of ICU''s wishlist destinations and find the right summer accessories for your beach style.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6451" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/mykonos-beach-look.jpg" alt="" width="597" height="549" /></a>\n\nChannel your inner Greek goddess while sinking your toes into the hot Mykonos sand by adorning yourself in loose drapes of a natural palette with a bright emerald two piece. Fly towards the sun with a nod to Ikarus while wearing <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Gold Wing Earrings</a></strong>-- two little studs with one big impact.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Shop Emily Rothschild Gold Wing Earrings <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-wing-earrings.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6452" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/saint-tropez-beach-look.jpg" alt="" width="625" height="531" /></a>\n\nLeave subtlety behind as you head to the south of France. Cover up your bright one piece with a mix of leopard, zebra and sequins, an eyecatching ensemble rivaled only by the brilliant shine of <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle.html" target="_blank">Anna Beck''s Large Handcrafted Gold Bangle</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Shop Anna Beck Large Handcrafted Gold Bangle <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-skeleton-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6450" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/los-angeles-beach-look.jpg" alt="" width="679" height="583" /></a>\n\nHit up the L.A. beaches in true mix-n-match style by pairing a mismatched printed bikini with printed sandals, a vintage tee and studded shorts. For the ultimate street style edge add the <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-skeleton-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Skeleton Ring</a> </strong>from <strong>Charlotte Martyr</strong>, a unique and enchanting piece that perfectly combines rock attitude with chic design.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Shop Charlotte Martyr Silver Skeleton Ring <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-skeleton-ring.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong>', 'Beach Babe Accessories', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beach-babe-accessories', '', '', '2011-07-20 12:59:28', '2011-07-20 10:59:28', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6449', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6457, 8, '2011-07-21 16:12:35', '2011-07-21 14:12:35', 'Here at <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a></strong> we believe in living a life of chic so it''s no surprise that Ahn from the fabulous blog <strong><a href="http://www.9to5chic.com/" target="_blank">9to5Chic</a></strong> is our choice for <strong>Blogger of the Week</strong>. With impeccable taste, clean style, and an effortless ability to mix high end designer labels with commercial and independent designers she is truly a sartorial muse. Enjoy below, <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a></strong>''s styling imaginations with <strong><a href="http://www.9to5chic.com/" target="_blank">9to5Chic</a></strong>.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6460" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/9to5chic-3.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="410" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Embrace independent design to enhance your work wardrobe just like Ahn. Create a simple trinity by mixing a stack of <strong>Noot''s</strong> delicate <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank"><strong>Knot Bracelets</strong> </a>with two standout mixed metal rings: <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">Striate Grandissimo</a></strong> from <strong>ebbandpflow</strong> and the <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-ring-charlotte.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Ring</a></strong> from <strong>Unsurcinq</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-bracelet-silver-gold-plated.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Knot Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-ring-charlotte.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq Charlotte Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">ebbandpflow Striate Grandissimo Ring.</a></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6458" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/9to5chic-1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Nothing beats a simple palette of greys and there''s no better complement to soft greys than a trio of brilliant standout jewelry. Layer a round neckline with a delicate chain and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/grey-diamond-cluster-necklace.html" target="_blank">Grey Diamond Necklace</a></strong> from <strong>Gorjana</strong>. For a simple ring statement rock the translucent <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Light Amethyst Ring</a></strong> from <strong>Shamila</strong> and the eye-catching crystal inspired <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Bracelet</a></strong> from <strong>Charlotte Martyr</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/grey-diamond-cluster-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gorjana Grey Diamond Cluster Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila Light Amethyst Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Gold Sabrina Crystal Bracelet</a>.</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6459" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/9to5chic-2.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\nNothing says chic like Ahn''s bold color and simple ensemble. Rock your own jewel tones with a subtle and beautiful statement necklace like <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-natural-diamond-structure-necklace.html" target="_blank">Bena''s NaturalDiamond Structure Necklace</a></strong> in cherry wood and abelone. Mix a <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">White Quartz Ring</a> </strong>and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Thin Gold Stackable Ring</a></strong> and a clever and feminine take on traditional i.d. bracelets, with the gold <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/double-ribbon-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Double Ribbon Bracelet</a></strong> from <strong>Tracy Matthews</strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-natural-diamond-structure-necklace.html" target="_blank">Bena Natural Diamond Structure Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye White Quartz Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/double-ribbon-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Tracy Matthews Double Ribbon Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/thin-gold-stackable-rings.html" target="_blank">Noot Thin Gold Stackable Ring</a>.</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">Enjoy Ahn, ICU''s Blogger of the Week on her own blog <a href="http://www.9to5chic.com/" target="_blank">9to5Chic</a>, and shop all looks at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a>.</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: 9to5Chic', 'Here at ICU we believe in living a life of chic so it''s no surprise that Ahn from the fabulous blog 9to5Chic is our choice for Blogger of the Week.  With impeccable taste, clean style, and an effortless ability to mix high end designer labels with commercial and independent designers she is truly a sartorial muse.  Enjoy below, ICU''s styling imaginations with 9to5Chic.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-9to5chic', '', '', '2011-07-21 16:12:35', '2011-07-21 14:12:35