(6466, 8, '2011-07-22 11:22:54', '2011-07-22 09:22:54', 'A week of on-off showers in Paris is leading to a weekend with more of the same. It''s hard to believe it''s the middle of July when you''re back in jeans and boots! Keep<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"> ICU</a></strong> jewelry with you to guarantee a smile on your face despite the grey clouds and condensation.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lisa-levine-vertebrae-necklace.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6467" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/0722.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nKeep things simple on Saturday with the an easy look made up of classic wardrobe essentials. A white tank and dark cuffed jeans go perfectly with tan boots and a snakeskin bag. Complement with <strong>Lisa Levine</strong>''s silver and gold effortlessly intertwined and twisted <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lisa-levine-vertebrae-necklace.html" target="_blank">Vertebrae Necklace</a></strong>. Top off with a scarlet lip and spend the day in style.\n\n<strong>Shop Lisa Levine Vertebrae Necklace <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lisa-levine-vertebrae-necklace.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6468" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/0724.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nPlay into Sunday''s cool and casual vibe with a silk printed tee and loose drawstring trousers. To take the look up a notch tower high in leopard heels and rock the ultimate in simple statement rings with the silver and gold <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">Striate Grandissimo Ring</a></strong> from <strong>ebbandpflow</strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop ebbandpflow Striate Grandissimo Ring <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and