(6485, 8, '2011-07-28 11:45:57', '2011-07-28 09:45:57', 'With weeks and weeks of blogger styles in the <strong><a href="www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICU</a></strong> vaults it is now time to turn on a critical eye for a friendly battle between our weekly bloggers. <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/04/14/blogger-of-the-week-2/" target="_blank">Adeline Rapon</a> (<a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">adelinerapon.com</a>), <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/04/28/blogger-of-the-week-le-dressing-de-leeloo/" target="_blank">Lee Loo</a> (<a href="http://ledressingdeleeloo.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">ledressingdeleeloo.com</a>) and <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?s=california&amp;submit.x=0&amp;submit.y=0" target="_blank">Seaghna</a> (<a href="http://lightsdrivemysoul.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">lightsdrivemysoul.com</a>): three girls from two countries, all inspring looks with the thin geometric <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Silver Bangles from Noot</a>.\n\nWho''s the winner? That''s for you to decide. But afterall, with fashion like these three bloggers have there most definitely are no losers!\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/adeline-rapon-rocker.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6486" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/adeline-rapon-rocker.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="410" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Noot Silver Bangles: Eclectic Street</strong></p>\nWith a perfect grasp on Parisian street style it''s no wonder Adeline has inspired a mix of silver jewelry full of playful rocker personality: pair a mix of tough and delicate necklaces with silver and grey leather bracelets. Top off the look with a handful of different rings, mixing polished silver with antique finishes and even a touch of lavender.\n\n<strong>Shop the loo