(6521, 8, '2011-08-04 12:00:12', '2011-08-04 10:00:12', 'Feeling in the mood for a little taste of Irish luck, <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a></strong> has found its newest blogger inspiration in <strong><a href="http://www.anouskaproettabrandon.com/" target="_blank">Anouska Proetta Brandon</a></strong>. A model-slash-photographer from Dublin, she embodies cool glam and chic style. See below how <strong>Anouska</strong> has inspired a trio of looks featuring a bevy of <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a>''s</strong> favorite designers.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6522" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/anouska1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="410" /></a></p>\nNothing says cool and casual like black leggings and the perfectly draped white tank. Follow <strong>Anouska</strong>''s style by complementing your tank with a <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/clear-crystal-quartz-necklace.html" target="_blank">crystal quartz necklace</a></strong>, <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">amethyst ring</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">rainbow quartz ring</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nShop the look: <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/clear-crystal-quartz-necklace.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Clear Crystal Quartz Necklace</a></strong>, <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila Light Purple Amethyst Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Rainbow Quartz Ring</a></strong>.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6523" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/anouska2.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\n<strong>ICU</strong> can''t get enough of <strong>Anouska''s</strong> anatomical homage! Pair a tough <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-skull-black-diamond.html" target="_blank">Silver Skull Black Diamond Necklace</a></strong> with an eye catching <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-crystal-ring.html" target="_blank">Rainbow Crystal Rock Ring</a></strong>. If you''re lacking skeleton leggings just top off your look with a wooden etched<strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-skull-brooch.html" target="_blank">Skull Brooch</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nShop the look: <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-skull-black-diamond.html" target="_blank">Tracy Matthews Silver Skull Black Diamond Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-crystal-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Rainbow Crystal Rock Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/bena-skull-brooch.html" target="_blank">Bena Skull Brooch</a></strong>.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6524" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/anouska3.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a></p>\nAnouska is rocking the ultimate chic statement with a large draped scarf and pair of statement rings. Wrap yourself in a <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/military-cashmere-scarf.html" target="_blank"><strong>Screen Printed Cashmere Scarf</strong> </a>and sport two rocky rings: genuine <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/purple-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Purple Quartz</a></strong> and crystal inspired <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Caroline</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nShop the look: <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/military-cashmere-scarf.html" target="_blank">Leigh &amp; Luca Printed Cashmere Scarf</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/purple-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Purple Quartz Ring</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">Visit <a href="http://www.anouskaproettabrandon.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Anouska''s </strong>blog</a> to check out her style and <strong>shop all looks</strong> at<strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a></strong>.</p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Anouska Proetta Brandon', 'Feeling in the mood for a little taste of Irish luck, ICU has found its newest blogger inspiration in Anouska Proetta Brandon.  A model-slash-photographer from Dublin, she embodies cool glam and chic style.  See below how Anouska has inspired a trio of looks featuring a bevy of ICU''s favorite designers.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-anouska-proetta-brandon', '', '', '2011-08-04 12:00:12', '2011-08-04 10:00:12', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6521', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6534, 9, '2011-08-10 15:24:25', '2011-08-10 13:24:25', 'With fall just around the corner <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/#" target="_blank">ICU</a></strong> is in the mood for new textures, cozy layers and an earthy autumnal palette. Keep summer''s glow with you all season long by offsetting your stormy colored looks with gold and silver jewels from <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=charlotte+martyr" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Curiosity &amp; Mirabella</a></strong> collection.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Screen-shot-2011-08-10-at-2.16.24-PM.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-6536 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Screen-shot-2011-08-10-at-2.16.24-PM.png" alt="" width="548" height="448" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Rain Cloud</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">As stormy skies roll in, don a prim look by creating your own mix of greys. Layer a sweet dress with heathered tights and chunky knit socks, accented by Charlotte Martyr''s bold <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Gold Sabrina Bracelet</a></strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Shop Gold Sabrina Bracelet here.</a></strong></p>\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html"><img class="size-full wp-image-6535 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Screen-shot-2011-08-10-at-2.16.09-PM.png" alt="" width="479" height="438" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Autumn Peacock</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Avoid true blacks this fall in favor of a monochrome palette of inky darks. Punctuate deep peacock from head-to-toe with royal cranberry velvet boots and the luxuriously large <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Caroline Ring</a></strong> from Charlotte Martyr.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Shop Silver Caroline Ring here.</a></strong></p>\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html"><img class="size-full wp-image-6545 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Screen-shot-2011-08-10-at-2.46.54-PM.png" alt="" width="596" height="366" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Golden Harvest</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left">Channel winter wheat fields with a relaxed look of ashen neutrals, playing with texture and volume by pairing cropped knits with pleated trousers. Stay warm by layering a golden ochre <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/crochet-summer-scarf-yellow.html" target="_blank"><strong>Hand Crochet Snood</strong> from Ariane Haas </a>and an enchanting <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Vladimir Ring</a></strong> by Charlotte Martyr.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left"><strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/crochet-summer-scarf-yellow.html" target="_blank">Shop Hand Crochet Snood here</a> &amp; <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">shop Silver Vladimir Ring here</a>.</strong></p>\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/index/?limit=all&amp;q=charlotte%20martyr" target="_blank"></a><strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/index/?limit=all&amp;q=charlotte%20martyr" target="_blank">Shop all Charlotte Martyr here!</a></strong></p>', 'Fall into Curiosity with Charlotte Martyr', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fall-into-curiosity-with-charlotte-martyr', '', '', '2011-08-10 15:24:25', '2011-08-10 13:24:25', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6534', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6554, 9, '2011-08-12 12:00:10', '2011-08-12 10:00:10', '<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=snood"><img class="size-full wp-image-6555 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/ARIANE_HAAS_ICUINPARIS_GILT.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="378" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center">Fall into Autumn''s textures with <strong>Hand Crochet Snoods</strong> by <strong>Ariane Haas</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=snood" target="_blank"><strong>Shop all Snoods here.</strong></a></p>', 'Cozy up to Fall with Ariane Haas Hand Crochet Snoods', 'Fall into Autumn''s textures with Hand Crochet Snoods by Ariane Haas.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cozy-up-to-fall-with-ariane-haas-hand-crochet-snoods', '', '', '2011-08-12 12:00:10', '2011-08-12 10:00:10', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6554', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6564, 9, '2011-08-11 12:07:17', '2011-08-11 10:07:17', '<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a></strong> has reached into another pocket of the world and found ourselves a style muse hailing all the way from Auckland, New Zealand. Marcella''s blog <strong><a href="http://www.fashion-distraction.com/" target="_blank">Fashion Distraction</a></strong> truly is just that: a delectable distraction of her effortless sartorial combinations. Check out Marcella''s looks below to swoon over <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU''s</a></strong> restyling.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6565 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/fashion-distraction-1.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="430" /></a></p>\nSometimes all you need to take an outfit from simple to stellar is a handful of your favorite rings and a trusty scarf. Slip into a cool tubular scarf with <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/crochet-summer-scarf-greige.html" target="_blank">Ariane Haas'' Hand Crochet Snood</a></strong>, and pile on a range of rings including <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/jay-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Silver Jay Ring</a></strong>, <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-blue-topaz-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila''s Blue Topaz Ring</a></strong>, the <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">Striate Grandissimo</a></strong> from <strong>ebbandpflow</strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-ring-charlotte.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq''s Charlotte Ring</a></strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/crochet-summer-scarf-greige.html" target="_blank">Ariane Haas Hand Crochet Snoot Olive-Grey</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/jay-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Jay Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-blue-topaz-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila Blue Topaz Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/ebb-and-pflow-striate-grandissimo-ring.html" target="_blank">ebbandpflow Striate Grandissimo Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/unsurcinq-ring-charlotte.html" target="_blank">Unsurcinq Charlotte Ring</a></strong>.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6566 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/fashion-distraction-2.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="492" /></a></p>\nFollow <strong><a href="http://www.fashion-distraction.com/" target="_blank">Marcella''s</a></strong> lead and keep your accessories simple when adorning a printed top with interesting design details. Mix three statement rings by sticking to cool silver tones and one complementary color: <strong>Charlotte Martyr''s <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Caroline Ring</a> </strong>and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Vladimir Ring</a></strong>, and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Blue Quartz Ring</a></strong>. Top off the look with the thin <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gold Eyelash Necklace</a> </strong>from <strong>Noot</strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Vladimir Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Blue Quartz Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Eyelash Necklace</a></strong>.\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6567 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/fashion-distraction-3.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="492" /></a></p>\nWe love <strong><a href="http://www.fashion-distraction.com/" target="_blank">Marcella''s</a> </strong>polished take on a summer boho ensemble! Pair your favorite flowing dress with a trio of silver gems: <strong>Lisa Levine''s </strong>dazzling <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spellbound-necklace.html" target="_blank">Spellbound Necklace</a></strong>, the bold <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle-164.html" target="_blank">Handmade Silver Cuff</a> </strong>from <strong>Anna Beck </strong>and <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Wing Ring</a> </strong>from <strong>Emily Rothschild.</strong>\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/spellbound-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Spellbound Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle-164.html" target="_blank">Anna Beck Handmade Silver Cuff</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silver-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild Silver Wing Ring</a>.</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">Check out all of Marcella''s looks at <strong><a href="http://www.fashion-distraction.com/" target="_blank">Fashion Distraction</a></strong>, and <strong>shop </strong>all jewelry at <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"><strong>www.icuinparis.com</strong>.</a></p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Fashion Distraction', 'ICU has reached into another pocket of the world and found ourselves a style muse hailing all the way from Auckland, New Zealand.  Marcella''s blog Fashion Distraction truly is just that: a delectable distraction of her effortless sartorial combinations.  Check out Marcella''s looks below to swoon over ICU''s restyling.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-fashion-distraction', '', '', '2011-08-11 12:07:17', '2011-08-11 10:07:17', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6564', 0, 'post', '', 0);
