(6575, 4, '2011-08-16 14:16:02', '2011-08-16 12:16:02', '<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/SWEET-SUMMER_2011_BIARRITZ.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6630" title="SWEET-SUMMER_2011_BIARRITZ" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/SWEET-SUMMER_2011_BIARRITZ.jpg" alt="Sweet Summer Biarritz icuinparis.com" width="600" height="886" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>WELCOME TO BIARRITZ</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Welcome to a Sweet Summer sur la plage au soleil. ou.la.la.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Last week a team of ICU fashionistas took a wee trip down to the South of France to visit a brand new idea and one that is taking over the beaches of Biarritz,</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SWEET SUMMER. </strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;">Thanks to the wonderful ladies of <a title="soon famous paris" href="http://www.soon-famous.com/Soon_Famous/Accueil.html" target="_blank">Soon Famous Paris</a> and the <em>must-be-visited</em> <a title="sweet art shop" href="http://www.sweet-art-shop.fr/" target="_blank">Sweet Art Shop of Toulouse</a>,<a title="http://www.icuinparis.com/" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"> ICU - IN PARIS.COM</a> is proud to present a select few of our beloved designers for an exclusive one-month exposition on the beaches of Biarritz. </span></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;">Created from the pure love of independent design, we were more than ecstatic to participate in the gallery and from now u</span></strong><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;">ntil August 25th you can try, fit, feel, touch &amp; shop pieces from <a title="charlotte martyr " href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=charlotte+martyr+" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a>, <a title="noot, bijoux" href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=noot" target="_blank">Noot</a> &amp; Jiastyle (not even live on the site - so even more of a reason to go!). Not to mention the beautiful creations by jewelry designer, Ccile Pic, Oragami Jewelry, unsurcinq </span></strong><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;">and clothing by Emma Tess. Below a small re-count of the gallery, the sun, the beaches, the textures and of course, of course, the JEWELS.</span></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">SWEET SUMMER</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">15 Boulevard du Gnral de Gaulle</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Grande Plage</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you can''t make it to the beach... that''s okay, you can still shop the ICU Boutique <a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">HERE</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_0324.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6600" title="Sweet Summer Biarritz icuinparis.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_0324.jpg" alt="Sweet Summer Biarritz icuinparis.com" width="415" height="622" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_0263.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6597" title="IMG_0263" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_0263.jpg" alt="" width="622" height="415" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/CHARLOTTE-MARTYR_VLADMIR.jpg"></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_0266.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6598" title="Sweet Summer Biarritz icuinparis.com_amethyst ring" src="https://www.ic