(6658, 9, '2011-08-18 14:13:44', '2011-08-18 12:13:44', 'No style is more inspiring than a style that is loved, and <a href="http://ftbh.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Bebe Zeva''s</a> style is just that. Through her blog <a href="http://ftbh.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Fated To Be Hated</a>, Bebe infectiously shares her affection for putting together a look and creating a character. For such a young girl this Sin City native has an experienced sartorial sense, making her the perfect choice for ICU''s Blogger of the Week-- with looks ranging from casual and full of attitude to a playful nod at traditional classics. Some people use words to express who they are. Bebe uses fashion. And <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> uses jewels.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6660 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/bebe-zeva-1.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="410" /></a>\n\nClassic and casual in studded shorts and Doc Martens, Bebe is never short on cool attitude. Support the look with arms of metal, layering gold geometric bangles by <strong>Noot</strong>, an embellished leather cuff by <strong>Fiona Paxton</strong>, a large gold disc bangle by <strong>Anna Beck</strong> and the Two Tone Chain Bracelet from<strong> Coralie De Seynes</strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-bangle-bracelets.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Bangle Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/anna-beck-balinese-gold-bangle.html" target="_blank">Anna Beck Large Handcrafted<strong> Gold</strong> Bangle</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-fifi-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Fifi Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/coralie-de-seynes-two-tone-chain-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Coralie De Seynes Two Tone Chain Bracelet</a>. </strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6667 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/bebe-zeva-21.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nMake a classic black and white polka dot look modern with a plethora of fine and heavy chain necklaces. Create the ultimate combination with the vintage style Speed of Sound Necklace from <strong>Rackkandruin</strong> and three amazing pieces from <strong>Lisa Levine</strong>, including a mixed gold and silver chain, a long and dangling silver spike necklace and the multi-tone Short Gold Saber Necklace. Balance a gold chain cuff from <strong>Fiona Paxton</strong> with a gold crystal bracelet from <strong>Charlotte Martyr</strong>, and top off the look with a black and white printed bowtie from <strong>Laurent Desgrange</strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lisa-levine-vertebrae-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Rainbow Vertebrae Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/double-spike-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Double Spike Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/short-saber-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Short Gold Saber Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rackkandruin-speed-of-sound-necklace.html" target="_blank">Rackkandruin Speed of Sound Necklace</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/laurent-desgrange-heart-bow.html" target="_blank">Laurent Desgrange Heart Bow</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-brass-trixy-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Trixy Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-sabrina-gold-crystal-bangle.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Gold Sabrina Crystal Bracelet</a>.</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com"><img class="size-full wp-image-6662 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/bebe-zeva-3.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a>\n\nWe love Bebe''s casual summer look! Complement the perfect tee, sunnies and hat with the innovative Diamond Script Bracelet, and a touch of bright with <strong>Lamia Benalycherif''s</strong> fringe bracelet. Add two statement crystal rings: <strong>Charlotte Martyr''s</strong> silver statement ring and <strong>Astraleye''s</strong> Rainbow Quartz Ring.\n\n<strong>Shop the look: <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/lamia-benalycherif-pink-fringe-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Lamia Benalycherif Pink Fringe Bracelet</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Rainbow Quartz Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>, <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/diamond-bracelet.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild Diamond Script Bracelet</a>.</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>View <a href="http://ftbh.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Fated To Be Hated here</a> and <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">shop ICU here</a>.</strong></p>', 'Blogger of the Week: Bebe Zeva', 'No style is more inspiring than a style that is loved, and Bebe Zeva''s style is just that.  Through her blog Fated To Be Hated, Bebe infectiously shares her affection for putting together a look and creating a character.  For such a young girl this Sin City native has an experienced sartorial sense, making her the perfect choice for ICU''s Blogger of the Week-- with looks ranging from casual and full of attitude to a playful nod at traditional classics.  Some people use words to express who they are.  Bebe uses fashion.  And ICU uses jewels.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-of-the-week-bebe-zeva', '', '', '2011-08-18 14:13:44', '2011-08-18 12:13:44', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6658', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(6676, 9, '2011-08-19 11:26:47', '2011-08-19 09:26:47', 'With the introduction of new designer <strong>Jiastyle </strong>to the <strong>ICU boutique</strong>, we are eagerly awaiting a weekend full of elegant looks to complement their graceful and organic jewels.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silk-thread-scar-ring.html"><img class="size-full wp-image-6677 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/0820.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nTie one on with<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silk-thread-scar-ring.html" target="_blank"> <strong>Jiastyle''s Silk Threaded Scar Ring</strong>.</a> Innovative in concept and beautifully minimal in design, the perfect outfit to go along is a simple white dress, leather bag and striped heels. With arms covered make sure your legs are bare to soak up the last of the summer sun!\n\n<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/silk-thread-scar-ring.html" target="_blank">Shop Jiastyle Silk Threaded Scar Ring here.</a></strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/black-tassel-and-pearl-earrings.html"><img class="size-full wp-image-6678 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/0821.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nTemps are up so make sure your glam levels match! A comfortable jersey dress is the perfect staple for 33 degree heat. Top it off with metallic shoes and the alluring combo of a bare neck with dangling<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/black-tassel-and-pearl-earrings.html" target="_blank"> <strong>Black Tassel and Pearl Earrings</strong> from <strong>Jiastyle</strong></a>.\n\n<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/black-tassel-and-pearl-earrings.html" target="_blank"><strong>Shop </strong></a><strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/black-tassel-and-pearl-earrings.html" target="_blank">Jiastyle Black Tassel and Pearl Earrings here.</a></strong>\n\n&nbsp;', 'Paris Weekend Forecast', 'With the introduction of new designer Jiastyle to the ICU boutique, we are eagerly awaiting a weekend full of elegant looks to complement their graceful and organic jewels.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paris-weekend-forecast-15', '', '', '2011-08-19 11:26:47', '2011-08-19 09:26:47', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6676', 0, 'post', '', 0),
