(6705, 9, '2011-08-25 11:53:05', '2011-08-25 09:53:05', 'With a fierce showdown between Ireland, New Zealand, France and Hong Kong, consider this <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/07/28/blogger-battle/" target="_blank">Blogger Battle</a></strong> the next great world war. We''ve dipped into the<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">ICU</a> <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?s=blogger+of+the+week&amp;submit.x=0&amp;submit.y=0" target="_blank">Blogger of the Week</a> </strong>vaults once again to stir up a little friendly competition. One item, four girls.\n\nThe item: <strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Caroline Ring by Charlotte Martyr</a></strong>. The girls: Anouska from <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/04/blogger-of-the-week-anouska-proetta-brandon/" target="_blank">Anouska Proetta Brandon</a></strong>,Mercella from <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/11/blogger-of-the-week-fashion-distraction/" target="_blank">Fashion Distraction</a></strong>, Punky B from <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/06/30/blogger-of-the-week-punky-b/" target="_blank">Punky B</a> </strong>and Sam from <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/07/07/blogger-of-the-week-sam-is-home/" target="_blank">Sam Is Home</a></strong>.\n\nIt''s up to you to decide: which look is the best?<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/04/blogger-of-the-week-anouska-proetta-brandon/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6708" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/www.icuinparis-2.jpeg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/04/blogger-of-the-week-anouska-proetta-brandon/" target="_blank">Anouska Proetta Brandon</a></strong></p>\n<strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/04/blogger-of-the-week-anouska-proetta-brandon/" target="_blank"></a></strong>Nothing says cool and casual like black leggings and the perfectly draped white tank. Follow<strong><a href="http://www.anouskaproettabrandon.com/" target="_blank">Anouska</a></strong>''s style by complementing your tank with a<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/clear-crystal-quartz-necklace.html" target="_blank">crystal quartz necklace</a></strong>,<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">amethyst ring</a></strong> and<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">rainbow quartz ring</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Shop the look:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/clear-crystal-quartz-necklace.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Clear Crystal Quartz Necklace</a></strong>,<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/shamila-purple-amethyst-ring.html" target="_blank">Shamila Light Purple Amethyst Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/rainbow-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Rainbow Quartz Ring</a></strong>.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/11/blogger-of-the-week-fashion-distraction/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6707" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/www.icuinparis-1.jpeg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/08/11/blogger-of-the-week-fashion-distraction/" target="_blank">Fashion Distraction</a></strong></p>\nFollow<strong><a href="http://www.fashion-distraction.com/" target="_blank">Marcella''s</a></strong> lead and keep your accessories simple when adorning a printed top with interesting design details. Mix three statement rings by sticking to cool silver tones and one complementary color:<strong>Charlotte Martyr''s<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Silver Caroline Ring</a> </strong>and<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Silver Vladimir Ring</a></strong>, and<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye''s Blue Quartz Ring</a></strong>. Top off the look with the thin<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">Gold Eyelash Necklace</a> </strong>from<strong>Noot</strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/vladmir-ring-silver.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Vladimir Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Blue Quartz Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">Noot Gold Eyelash Necklace</a></strong>.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/06/30/blogger-of-the-week-punky-b/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6710" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/www.icuinparis-4.jpeg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/06/30/blogger-of-the-week-punky-b/" target="_blank">Punky B</a></strong></p>\nA classic beauty in stripes with a splash of color,<a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a> knows just how to accessorize with personality and elegance. Create a simple combination of the two tone<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Ginger Necklace</a></strong> and a pair of rock rings: the crystal inspired silver<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Caroline Ring</a></strong> and the genuine crystal<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Blue Quartz Ring</a></strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:</strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/fiona-paxton-ginger-necklace.html" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Ginger Necklace</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/blue-quartz-ring.html" target="_blank">Astraleye Blue Quartz Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/07/07/blogger-of-the-week-sam-is-home/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6709" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/www.icuinparis-3.jpeg" alt="" width="560" height="468" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/07/07/blogger-of-the-week-sam-is-home/" target="_blank">Same Is Home</a></strong></p>\nFollow<strong><a href="http://www.samishome.com/blog" target="_blank">Sam''s</a></strong> lead to colorblock to perfection! Accessorize a two-tone outfit of brights with two tones of metal.<strong> <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-necklace-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot''s Silver Knot Necklace</a></strong> and<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Silver Caroline Ring</a></strong> mingle with<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=fifi" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton''s Fifi Cuff</a> </strong>and<strong><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-mini-pinky-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Mini Pinky Wing Ring</a></strong>.\n\n<strong>Shop the look:<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/noot-knot-necklace-silver.html" target="_blank">Noot Silver Knot Necklace</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/charlotte-martyr-silver-crsytal-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr Silver Caroline Ring</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=fifi" target="_blank">Fiona Paxton Fifi Cuff</a>,<a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/gold-mini-pinky-wing-ring.html" target="_blank">Emily Rothschild''s Mini Pinky Wing Ring</a>.</strong>\n\n<strong>\n</strong>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://www.anouskaproettabrandon.com/" target="_blank">Anouska Proetta Brandon</a> - <a href="http://www.fashion-distraction.com/" target="_blank">Fashion Distraction</a> -<a href="http://www.punky-b.com/" target="_blank">Punky B</a> - <a href="http://www.samishome.com/blog" target="_blank">Sam Is Home</a></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SHOP ALL JEWELRY AT <a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">www.icuinparis.com</a></strong></p>', 'Blogger Battle', 'With a fierce showdown between Ireland, New Zealand, France and Hong Kong, consider this Blogger Battle the next great world war.  We''ve dipped into the ICU Blogger of the Week vaults once again to stir up a little friendly competition.  One item, four girls.  The item: Silver Caroline Ring by Charlotte Martyr.  The girls: Anouska from Anouska Proetta Brandon, Mercella from Fashion Distraction, Punky B from Punky B and Sam from Sam Is Home.  It''s up to you to decide: which look is the best?', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'blogger-battle-2', '', '', '2011-08-25 11:53:05', '2011-08-25 09:53:05', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=6705', 0, 'post', '', 0),
