(7094, 9, '2011-09-28 13:05:58', '2011-09-28 11:05:58', '<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html"><img class="size-large wp-image-7095 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Noot-ICU-Gold-Eyelash-Necklace_03-716x1024.jpg" alt="Noot ICU Gold Necklace" width="372" height="533" /></a></p>\nFor another <strong>Story Behind The Piece </strong>the ICUINPARIS.COM team sat down with <strong>Tania Petit</strong>, the designer behind the jewelry label <strong>Noot</strong>, to film her in her Paris atelier and find out more about her inspiration behind her <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">handmade 18k gold Eyelash Necklace</a></strong>.\n\nA delicate and whimsical piece with a story to match, find out what sparked such a unique design by watching the video and reading the story below.\n\n<a href="http://www.vimeo.com/29697964"><img class="size-full wp-image-7104 aligncenter" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Screen-shot-2011-09-28-at-12.59.16-PM.png" alt="Tania Petit Noot Video" width="448" height="335" /></a>\n\n<em>"The inspiration comes more so from those little moments in life. For example, the Eyelash Necklace I''m making right now. In fact it''s a piece that I made because I don''t normally use mascara, because every time I use it my eyelashes end up looking like a big ball of dough, never like the advertisements. </em>\n\n<em>So I asked myself </em>Who is this girl who seems to always look fantastic wearing mascara?\n\n<em>Since I never seem to get it right I created my own eyelash element which could be worn as a necklace, short or long... and could be worn many different ways.</em>\n\n<em>So there you go-- it''s those little moments that stop like a photograph, those instances in life are what feed my inspiration."</em>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank"></a><strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/gold-eyelash-necklace.html" target="_blank">SHOP NOOT''S 18k GOLD EYELASH NECKLACE HERE.</a></strong></p>', 'Story Behind the Piece: ICU Sits Down with Noot&#039;s Tania Petit', 'For another Story Behind The Piece the ICUINPARIS.COM team sat down with Tania Petit, the designer behind the jewelry label Noot, to film her in her Paris atelier and find out more about her inspiration behind her handmade 18k gold Eyelash Necklace.\nA delicate and whimsical piece with a story to match, find out what sparked such a unique design by watching the video and reading the story below.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'story-behind-the-piece-icu-sits-down-with-noots-tania-petit', '', '', '2011-09-28 13:05:58', '2011-09-28 11:05:58', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=7094', 0, 'post', '', 0),
