(7520, 9, '2011-11-25 10:15:07', '2011-11-25 09:15:07', 'Whether you''re reeling from a wonderful Thanksgiving full of food and friends or just hiding out from the dropping temperatures, it''s a weekend for relaxed style. Keep things casual with two of ICU''s newest designers: Jee Vice and Onikann.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/sexy-sunglasses.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7521" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/1126.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nKeep a cozy feeling with you all day by layering printed harem pants and a wrapped up sweater. Stay comfortable in flats and stay glamorous with <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/sexy-sunglasses.html" target="_blank">Jee Vice''s Sexy Cat Eye Sunglasses</a></strong>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/sexy-sunglasses.html" target="_blank"><strong>&gt; Shop Jee Vice Sexy Cat Eye Sunglasses</strong></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/delphi-silk-scarf.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7522" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/1127.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="490" /></a>\n\nGive traditional winter sweaters a fashionable update with fine knits and a pleated metallic skirt. Add color with the boldly printed <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/delphi-silk-scarf.html" target="_blank">Delphi Silk Scarf from Onikann </a></strong>and leopard loafers.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories/delphi-silk-scarf.html" target="_blank"><strong>&gt; Shop Onikann Delphi Silk Scarf</strong></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center">Click on the products below to view them in the ICU boutique.</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-desi