(7613, 9, '2011-12-06 12:06:21', '2011-12-06 11:06:21', 'This week ICU checks in with street style photographer Laura Wassermann and fashion illustrator Laura Geddes for another exclusive collaboration. Elegantly captured by Laura Wassermann, the ladylike and classic look of houndstooth and gold chains inspires Laura Geddes'' beautifully rendered drawing of those same timeless elements. Scroll down to see what the artists themselves were thinking when they captured this stunning look.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/lauras_7.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-7620" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/lauras_7-450x1024.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="1024" /></a>\n\n<em>Laura Wassermann''s photo inspiration:</em>\n\n"I was drawn to this look because it was so feminine, it was very Chanel, so chic and immaculate. I loved the blossoming, decorative, metal flowers over the small scale dimensions in the houndstooth - which is actually an emerging fabric trend for the fall,wink wink!"\n\n<em>Laura Geddes'' illustration inspiration:</em>\n\nI love this mix of houndstooth, curls and chunky gold - I drew exactly as I saw the picture as it''s amazing!\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/category/wwwindielovecom/icu-illustrators/" target="_blank">Click <strong>here</strong> to view more collaborations from the Lauras!</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/category/wwwindielovecom/icu-illustrators/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7622" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/thumbnail-tiles.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="267" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>', 'ICU Exclusive: Street Style &amp; Fashion Illustration', 'This week ICU checks in with street style photographer Laura Wassermann and fashion illustrator Laura Geddes for another exclusive collaboration.  Elegantly captured by Laura Wassermann, the ladylike and classic look of houndstooth and gold chains inspires Laura Geddes'' beautifully rendered drawing of those same timeless elements.  Scroll down to see what the artists themselves were thinking when they captured this stunning look.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'icu-exclusive-street-style-fashion-illustration', '', '', '2011-12-06 12:06:21', '2011-12-06 11:06:21', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=7613', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(7624, 9, '2011-12-09 10:00:11', '2011-12-09 09:00:11', 'Everyone knows the only thing to really cure winter blues is some true winter style. Bundle up this weekend, with temps dropping into the single digits, and make sure to keep ICU designers EA Burns and Vaskolg with you to guarantee a standout look.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/large-green-leather-triangle-pendant.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7625" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/1210.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\nUpdate Summer''s colorblock trend by pairing your primaries with stark black and white. A red shoe and yellow nail polish are perfect to offset <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/large-green-leather-triangle-pendant.html" target="_blank">EA Burns'' Large Green Leather Pendant</a>, made completely from recycled materials.\n\n<strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/large-green-leather-triangle-pendant.html" target="_blank">&gt; EA Burns: Large Green Leather Pendant</a></strong>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/large-green-leather-triangle-pendant.html"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/esparta-shell-necklace.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7626" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/1211.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a></a>\n\nCreate the ultimate contrasting look this Sunday featuring a range of neutral tones and black. Balance the geometric cuts and paneling of the clothes with a beautifully organic conversation starting necklace like <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/esparta-shell-necklace.html" target="_blank">Vaskolg''s Esparta Shell Necklace</a>.\n\n<strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/esparta-shell-necklace.html" target="_blank">&gt; Vaskolg: Esparta Shell Necklace</a></strong>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/large-green-leather-triangle-pendant.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7627" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-conte