(7640, 9, '2011-12-15 11:27:05', '2011-12-15 10:27:05', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ERIK_RAYNAL1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-7680" title="ERIK_RAYNAL" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ERIK_RAYNAL1-1024x682.jpg" alt="" width="577" height="383" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href=" https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/20/erik-raynal-bienvenue-a-icu/">VERSION FRANAISE CLIQUEZ ICI</a></strong></p>\n&nbsp;\n\nICU is happy to introduce a new member amongst its ranks. A local Parisian, Erik Raynal is already making his mark on the web through his widely read blog,<strong><a href="http://erikraynal.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">www.erikraynal.blogspot.com</a> </strong>and tumblr, <strong><a href="http://erikraynal.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">www.erikraynal.tumblr.com</a></strong>. We stumbled upon Erik by chance at a fashion event here in Paris and it was love at first site. With an aesthetic that is dark and mysterious, Erik''s style and presence are impossible not to love, and after reading the articles and interviews on his blog we knew he would be the perfect ICU contributor to the insider''s world of Paris'' creative fashion scene.\n\nAlready with numerous creative projects underway, Erik''s ability to connect with the new, the now and the not-to-be-missed is what keeps his readers coming back and wanting more. As of early 2012 his blogs with transition into an online magazine in which he will continue to showcase interviews, events, his photography and of course ICU!\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\nStay tuned for Erik''s first ICU contribution on December 21, as he sits down with <a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Adeline Rapon</a>, stellar blogger, soon to be Boucheron jewelry designer and all around cool Parisian girl.\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_7681" align="alignright" width="437" caption="Adeline Rapon"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rapon.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-7681 " title="Adeline-rapon" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rapon.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="292" /></a>[/caption]\n\n<img class="size-full wp-image-7643 alignleft" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: 0px initial initial;" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ERIK_RAYNAL-2.jpg" alt="" width="432" height="288" />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/01/icu-exclusive-interview-april-hubal-the-triple-threat/" target="_blank">Click <strong>here</strong> to read ICU''s latest creative interview with April Hubal, owner and founder of Maniac Magazine.</a></p>\n&nbsp;', 'Bienvenue, Erik Raynal', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome-erik-raynal', '', '', '2011-12-15 11:27:05', '2011-12-15 10:27:05', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=7640', 0, 'post', '', 0),
