(7671, 9, '2011-12-16 11:00:22', '2011-12-16 10:00:22', 'We''re counting down weekends until a new year begins and this is one of the last. Finish 2011 with style by pulling out bright colors, mixed proportions, and textured knits. And make sure you have ICU''s stand-out accessories.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/silver-royal-scales-ring.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7672" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/1217.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/silver-royal-scales-ring.html"></a>Wrap up with a double layer coat for a night out Saturday, sporting a bright jewel tone blouse. Finish off minimal accessories with <strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/silver-royal-scales-ring.html" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr''s Royal Scales Ring</a></strong> for a touch of refined roughness.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/silver-royal-scales-ring.html" target="_blank"><strong>Click here to shop&gt; Charlotte Martyr Silver Royal Scales Ring.</strong></a>\n\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7673" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/1218.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="549" />\n\nStay cozy Sunday afternoon with an oversized cardigan and long jersey dress. Make sure to keep your clothes quiet so your accessories can really shout. A mustard boot and tangerine nail are the ultimate complement to the ultimate statement necklace: <a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/scheherazade-necklace.html" target="_blank">AEA''s Scheherazade Necklace</a>, made from vintage glass beads from around the world.\n\n<strong><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/scheherazade-necklace.html" target="_blank">Click here to shop&gt; AEA Scheherazade Necklace.</a></strong>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/silver-royal-scales-ring.html"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7675" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/charlotte_martyr