(7699, 10, '2011-12-22 06:51:01', '2011-12-22 05:51:01', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong><em><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/22/a-stellar-blogger-adeline-rapon-english-version/" target="_blank">English version click HERE</a></em></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://ICUINPARIS.COM/">ICUINPARIS.COM</a> (<a title="https://www.icuinparis.com/" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank">https://www.icuinparis.com/</a>) en collaboration avec Erik Raynal, rencontre avec lauthentique Adeline Rapon ; clbre blogueuse parisienne (<a title="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com</a>), tudiante  BJOP une cole de la rue du Louvre et potential futur collaboratrice avec notre coup de coeur, Charlotte Martyr ?</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Regardez le vido et lisez la texte racontait par notre nouveau collaborateur Parisien, <a title="erik raynal" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/20/erik-raynal-bienvenue-a-icu/" target="_blank">Erik Raynal</a>.</p>\n\n<div style="text-align: center;"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/34066031?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0" width="601" height="338" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>\n\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg"></a>&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg">_</a>___________\n\n</div>\n<address style="text-align: justify;"> </address> <address style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Dimanche 11 dcembre 2011,</strong> rencontre avec lauthentique Adeline Rapon; clbre blogueuse parisienne (<a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/">http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com</a>) dans son propre chez soi en banlieue proche de Paris, en compagnie de son amoureux Tony...<span style="font-style: normal;">Etudiante en joaillerie  lcole BJOP de la Rue du Louvre, Adeline fait preuve depuis 2008 dune relle simplicit  travers son blog; en proposant un univers simple; vaste et recherch.</span></address>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cest dans un appartement trs charmant; mlangeant plusieurs univers que lon retrouve la source dmancipation et dinspiration dAdeline et de son copain; collectionneurs ne jetant rien. Parisienne bientt ge de vingt-deux ans; Adeline Rapon connat un succs quasi immdiat  travers son blog; <em>"j''ai commenc par poster mes looks sur lookbook puis j''ai dcid de crer un blog afin de continuer  les partager"</em>.</p>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/MG_9308copie1.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-7758 alignright" title="adeline-rappon-icuinparis.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/MG_9308copie1.jpg" alt="" width="408" height="272" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Tout en restant humble, elle dveloppe une politique diffrente en voulant montrer toutes sortes de tenues vestimentaires:<em> "il n''y a aucun but avec la cration du blog, c''est juste drle et a m''est venu comme a"</em> nous dit-elle. Le blog attire, en effet, de plus en plus de personnes depuis sa cration avec un public plus tranger : <em>"ce qui est marrant, c''est que ce sont plus les amricains; allemands ou anglais qui visitent mon blog"</em>. C''est en s''inspirant de "tout et de rien, en parcourant internet" que la blogueuse, Adeline Rapon, apporte un esprit nouveau et lger aux blogs parisiens.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">La majeure partie de ses tenues proviennent d''enseignes accessibles  tous (<em>h&amp;m</em>, <em>topshop</em>, <em>asos</em>, <em>zara</em>...); les photos sont principalement prises par elle ou par son copain de faon trs simple avec la volont premire d''trehonnteavec les visiteurs du blog : <em>"la plupart des blogs, aujourd''hui, manquentdhonnteet de simplicit"</em> nous dit-elle. C''est  travers, ce rel CV en ligne, qu''Adeline Rapon exprime ses inspirations; nous dvoile une partie de sa vie et inspire la gente fminine  travers ses tenues. Elle a connu <em><strong>ICUINPARIS</strong></em>  travers Charlotte Martyr et en raison de ses tudes en joaillerie.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nous avons t ravis de rencontrer Adeline Rapon, personnalit parisienne phare de ces dernires annes. Dcouvrez galement, son second blog encore plus authentique et attrayant (<a href="http://wolvesandbucks.blogspot.com/">http://wolvesandbucks.blogspot.com/</a>) o elle partage une partie de sa vie en couple.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg">_</a>___________</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7725" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com " src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="520" /></a></p>\n\n<pre style="text-align: center;">photo credit: Adeline Rapon</pre>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ADELINE-rappon-icuinparis.com-interview.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7727" title="ADELINE-rappon-icuinparis.com-interview" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ADELINE-rappon-icuinparis.com-interview.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7728" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 1" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-1.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-31.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7729" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 3" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-31.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-8.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7730" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 8" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-8.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7731" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 11" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-11.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-18.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7732" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 18" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-18.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-20.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7733" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 20" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-20.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n\n<pre style="text-align: center;">photo credit: Christan Summers</pre>\n<pre style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia, times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; white-space: normal;">An<a title="ICUINPARIS.COM" href="http://www.ICUINPARIS.COM/" target="_blank">ICUINPARIS.COM</a></span><span style="font-family: georgia, times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; white-space: normal;"> Production</span></pre>\n<pre style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia, times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; white-space: normal;">En collaboration avec<a title="erik raynal" href="http://erikraynal.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Erik Raynal</a></span></pre>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Lisez notre dernire interview avec le<em>self-made-woman</em>,<a title="april hubal" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/01/icu-exclusive-interview-april-hubal-the-triple-threat/" target="_blank"> April Hubal,</a> fondatrice du publication, Maniac Magazine et photographe connue entre les Hollywood Stars.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>', 'A stellar blogger, Adeline Rapon (Version Franaise)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-stellar-blogger-adeline-rapon-version-francaise', '', '', '2011-12-22 06:51:01', '2011-12-22 05:51:01', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=7699', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(7702, 9, '2011-12-20 14:19:50', '2011-12-20 13:19:50', '<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ERIK_RAYNAL1.jpeg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-7704" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ERIK_RAYNAL1.jpeg" alt="" width="614" height="409" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="ERIK RAYNAL, ICUINPARSIS.COM" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/15/welcome-erik-raynal/">ENGLISH VERSION CLICK HERE</a></p>\n&nbsp;\n\nICU est trs contente de bienvenue Erik Raynal, jeune Franais sur le scne Parisien qui ne manque pas une soire, un vernissage, un vnement important...il est juste<em>the guy to know</em>. Nous laissons donc lui de s''introduise ci-dessus...\n\n&gt;&gt; Je suis tudiant dans le marketing de la mode, je suis trs jeune ( peine 18 ans) et dj plein de projets en cours. J''ai effectu un stage chez balenciaga me permettant de rentrer plusprcismentdans le monde de la mode; j''ai toujours t passionn par la mode mais aussi par le monde du journalisme. Je lance mon projet de magazine en ligne ds le dbut de l''anne 2012.\n\nJe suis ravis d''entrer en collaboration avec I.C.U; j''avais rencontr Christina  une soire au chacha club et elle m''a donn sa carte and then i send her an email. Je fais toujours la fashion week de Paris; je connais beaucoup de personnes  force de sortir par exemple. J''aime aussi prendre des photos en soires, de paysage, d''amis ce qui est considr comme une passion. Je tiens deux blogs (<a href="http://erikraynal.blogspot.com/">http://erikraynal.blogspot.com</a> avec des petits articles et <a href="http://erikraynal.tumblr.com/">http://erikraynal.tumblr.com</a> o je dpose mes photos). Je suis parisien, plus tard je veux travailler absolument dans la mode soit dans la presse, soit dans une grande maison ou bien organiser des vnements comme des dfiles. &lt;&lt;\n\nVoil !Restez branchs pourErikranimationpremire contributionle 21 Dcembre, commeil s''assoitavec <a title="ADELINE_RAPON" href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">AdelineRapon</a>, le blogueurstellaires, qui fait ses tudes  l''cole BJOP de la rue du Louvre... sera bienttcratrice de bijouxextraordinaire : )  etautour juste une fille cool.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class="alignleft" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ERIK_RAYNAL-2.jpg" alt="" width="432" height="288" />\n\n[caption id="attachment_7716" align="aligncenter" width="504" caption="Adeline Rapon"]<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rapon1.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-7716" title="Adeline-rapon" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rapon1.jpg" alt="" width="504" height="336" /></a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<a title="maniac magazine" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/01/icu-exclusive-interview-april-hubal-the-triple-threat/">Lisez notre dernire interview avec le <em>self-made-woman</em>, April Hubal qui est la fondatrice du publication, Maniac Magazine et photographe connue entre les Hollywood Stars... </a>', 'Erik Raynal, Bienvenue  ICU', 'Bienvenue, Erik Raynal, a l''equipe ICU.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'erik-raynal-bienvenue-a-icu', '', '', '2011-12-20 14:19:50', '2011-12-20 13:19:50', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=7702', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(7740, 4, '2011-12-22 08:58:08', '2011-12-22 07:58:08', '<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Version Franaise Clickez <a title="adeline-rappon-icuinparis.com" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/22/a-stellar-blogger-adeline-rapon-version-francaise/" target="_blank">ICI</a></em></p>\n&nbsp;\n\nICUINPARIS.COM in collaboration with Erik Raynal met with Adeline Rapon, sought after Parisian blogger and up and coming jewelry designer to ask about her quick rise to international blogger recognition, design school at the Louvre and possible collaborations with ICU''s own, <a title="charlotte martyr " href="https://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=charlotte+martyr" target="_blank">Charlotte Martyr</a>.\n\nWatch the video and read below the encounter told by ICU''s newest Parisian contributor, <a title="erik raynal" href="http://erikraynal.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Erik Raynal</a>:\n\n<p style="text-align: center;"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/34064998?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0" width="601" height="338" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>\n\n<p style="text-align: justify;">------------------------</p>\n\n<address style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Sunday December the 11th</strong>, we met Adeline Rapon, (<a href="http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com/">http://adelinerapon.blogspot.com</a>) at her apartment just outside Paris with her boyfriend, Tony Stone...</address>It was in her charming flat, a mix of creative atmospheres where we found the origin of emancipation and inspiration of Adeline Rapon and Tony, describing themselves as true collectors. Twenty-two years old, student in jewelry at the Louvres BJOP school of design and fabrication, she didn''t expect the fast and lasting recognition for her blog that was launched in 2008:<em>I started my blog by posting my looks onto the website, <strong>Lookbook</strong> then I decided to create a blog in order to share them again.</em>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/MG_9308copie.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-7753 alignright" title="adeline rappon for icuinparsi.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/MG_9308copie.jpg" alt="" width="408" height="272" /></a></em></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Keeping it simple, she created a different way of showing outfits mixed with inspirations and experiences of her personal life:<em>there was no goal with the creation of this blog, its just fun and a way to express ideas and what inspires me. </em> The blog continues to attract more and more visitors with a growing international readership:<em>what it is funny is that Americans, Germans and English are the first visitors to my blog. </em></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Adeline and her boyfriend, and blogger collaborator (www.wolvesandbucks.blogspot.com), shoot all the photos used for the blog themselves - keeping it simple. The first goal for them is to be honest with the blogs visitors: Adeline says,<em>the majority of blogs today lack honesty and simplicity.</em></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Since 2008, Adeline has expressed a true simplicity through her blog, by making a simple universe; vast and popular - we don''t see this changing anytime soon.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">A fan of<a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">ICUINPARIS</a> thanks to Charlotte Martyr, one of ICU''s best coveted designers... soon to be collaborating with Adeline Rapon...? We''ll have to wait and see.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">-<strong><em> Erik Raynal</em></strong> FOR ICU</p>\n------------------------\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7725" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com " src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/46058_425172445317_235087770317_5433729_1328659_n.jpg" alt="" width="576" height="416" /></a><span style="font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Courier New'', Courier, monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre;">photo credit: Adeline Rapon</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ADELINE-rappon-icuinparis.com-interview.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7727" title="ADELINE-rappon-icuinparis.com-interview" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/ADELINE-rappon-icuinparis.com-interview.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7728" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 1" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-1.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-31.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7729" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 3" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-31.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-8.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7730" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 8" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-8.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7731" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 11" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-11.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-18.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7732" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 18" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-18.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-20.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7733" title="Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com 20" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Adeline-rappon-interview-icuinparis.com-20.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="392" /></a><span style="font-family: Consolas, Monaco, ''Courier New'', Courier, monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: pre;">photo credit: Christan Summers</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">An <a title="ICUINPARIS.COM" href="http://www.ICUINPARIS.COM/" target="_blank">ICUINPARIS.COM</a> Production</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">In collaboration with <a title="erik raynal" href="http://erikraynal.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Erik Raynal </a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Read our last interview with <a title="april hubal" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/2011/12/01/icu-exclusive-interview-april-hubal-the-triple-threat/" target="_blank">April Hubal,</a> Owner and Founder of Maniac Magazine and celebrity photographer.</p>', 'A stellar blogger, Adeline Rapon (English Version)', 'ICUINPARIS.COM in collaboration with Erik Raynal met with Adeline Rapon, sought after Parisian blogger and up and coming jewelry designer to ask about her quick rise to international blogger recognition, design school at the Louvre and possible collaborations with ICU''s own, Charlotte Martyr.\n\nWatch the video and read below the encounter told by ICU''s newest Parisian contributor, Erik Raynal:', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-stellar-blogger-adeline-rapon-english-version', '', '', '2011-12-22 08:58:08', '2011-12-22 07:58:08', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=7740', 0, 'post', '', 1),
