(8088, 4, '2012-02-28 14:25:46', '2012-02-28 13:25:46', '<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/37577038?byline=0&amp;color=ffffff" width="601" height="338" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe><p>ICUINPARIS.COM Designer Profile: EA Burns<br />\n<br />\n\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>ICUINPARIS.COM Designer Profile: EA Burns</strong></h4>\n<p style="text-align: center;">ICU recently sat down with designer, Lizzie Burns to talk a little eco-shop and jewelry design. Working beside the infamous designer, Mrs. Jones, in London''s eccentric fashion scene Lizzie had the opportunity to style renowned names such as the Scissor Sisters, The Killers, Kylie Minogue, Goldfrapp among others... and after some time she was ready to feed the desire of being the designer herself and with enormous support from her peers, she launched EA Burns.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">With the desire to "create ethical, affordable and still exciting pieces" Lizzie began to work with the geometry of shapes, colors, sizes and using only recycled leathers (you would never be able to tell!) she is now on her second collection, sweeping the international fashion scene markets with a stocklist to show for it.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Based in London, Lizzie hand makes all her pieces available now to shop online at <strong><a title="ea-burns-icuinparis.com" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/catalogsearch/result/?q=ea+burns" target="_blank">icuinparis.com</a></strong></p>', 'Designer Profile: EA Burns (Creative Exploration of the Recycled Cool)', 'ICU recently sat down with designer, Lizzie Burns to talk a little eco-shop and jewelry design. Working beside the infamous designer, Mrs. Jones, in London''s eccentric fashion scene Lizzie had the opportunity to style renowned names such as the Scissor Sisters, The Killers, Kylie Minogue, Goldfrapp among others... and after some time she was ready to feed the desire of being the designer herself and with enormous support from her peers, she launched EA Burns.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'designer-profile-ea-burns-creative-exploration-of-the-recycled-cool', '', '', '2012-02-28 14:25:46', '2012-02-28 13:25:46', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8088', 0, 'post', '', 0);
