(8197, 4, '2012-10-03 09:14:41', '2012-10-03 07:14:41', 'Paris Fashion Week 2012 exhibits forte_forte "10" an iconographic research through the first forte_forte decade.\n\nSettled within a stone covered <em>couloir </em> on Rue Charlot was a large wooden structure filled with a decade of forte_forte''s most iconic pieces. Each piece hung from a hanger designed as a women''s profile, an affiliation with an artist friend of the designers''. Small labels were included to describe the piece, the year of fabrication and materials used. Each piece displayed in a precious way, not to be touched, yet no glass to keep you from temptation.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1623.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-8207 aligncenter" title="forte_forte Paris Fashion Week 2012" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1623-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="732" height="732" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1621.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8205" title="forte_forte Paris Fashion Week 2012" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1621-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="732" height="732" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1622.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8206" title="forte_forte Paris Fashion Week 2012" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1622-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="732" height="732" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1620.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8204" title="forte_forte Paris Fashion Week 2012" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/IMG_1620-1024x1024.jpg" alt=