n at icuinparis.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_0952.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640" /></a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_0954.jpg">\n</a>', 'Onikann Scarves on Sale at Printemps', 'Onikann Scarves are on sale at Printemps! Every year the infamous Parisian multi-brand store organizes a portion of the shop for Christmas spending called, Boutique Noir and Onikann was one of the brands chosen this year to participate.\n\nRadiant, 100% silk scarves made in France scarves designed the wonderful Anne Boivin... if you are in Paris go have a look and if you are not, well you can always browse in our e-shop. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'onikann-scarves-on-sale-at-printemps', '', '', '2012-10-27 18:19:11', '2012-10-27 16:19:11', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8288', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(8296, 4, '2012-11-06 08:55:01', '2012-11-06 07:55:01', '<p style="text-align: left;">Yesterday I met designer, Mathilde Baissas De Chastenet of <a title="Mathilde 2C" href="http://www.mathilde2c.com/" target="_blank">Mathilde 2C</a> for a little stroll through the infamous Paris boutique, <a title="Merci Boutique Paris" href="http://www.merci-merci.com/" target="_blank">Merci</a>. We began our admiration with Florentini + Baker''s new collection, moved slowly over to Isabel Marant''s fantastically over-sized print sweaters and stopped for a good while on <em>the</em> couch. Oh, the infamous sinking couch. I think Mathilde nearly fell asleep for a split second.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you have never been to Merci, it is something you should put on your list of visits to make. The concept store has accomplished an impressive curation of goods - from kitchenware, fashion, accessories, lifestyle and dcor. Inspiring to say the least.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Below, a few pictures of our short visit, with a quick re-visit to the 50''s and a light of an idea.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1856.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8297" title="merci boutique, paris + Mathilde 2C" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1856-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="659" height="659" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1858.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8298" title="Merci  Paris boutique" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1858-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="641" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1859.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8299" title="Merci  Paris boutique" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1859-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="480" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1860.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8300" title="Merci  Paris boutique" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1860-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="641" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1861.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8301" title="Merci  Paris boutique" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1861-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="641" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1862.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8302" title="Merci  Paris boutique" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1862-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="641" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1863.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8303" title="Merci  Paris boutique" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_1863-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="641" /></a></p>', 'Return of the 50&#039;s &amp; The Sinkable Couch at Merci with Designer, Mathilde 2C ', 'Yesterday I met designer, Mathilde Baissas De Chastenet of Mathilde 2C for a little stroll through the infamous Paris boutique, Merci. We began our admiration with Florentini + Baker''s new collection, moved slowly over to Isabel Marant''s fantastically over-sized print sweaters and stopped for a good while on the couch. Oh, the infamous sinking couch. I think Mathilde nearly fell asleep for a split second. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'return-of-the-50s-the-sinkable-couch-at-merci-with-designer-mathilde-2c', '', '', '2012-11-06 08:55:01', '2012-11-06 07:55:01', '', 0, 'https://www.