(8355, 4, '2009-08-08 13:06:53', '2009-08-08 11:06:53', '<p style="text-align: left;"><em>8.18.09</em></p>\nVogue photo shoot.\n\nCameras are rarely allowed to prowl around Georgia O''Keeffe''s Ghost Ranch in the desert of New Mexico, but<em>Vogue</em> spent three days shooting September cover girl Charlize Theron in the breathtaking (and historic) location.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><object id="flashObj" classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="404" height="436" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="bgcolor" value="#FFFFFF" /><param name="flashVars" value="videoId=33573440001&amp;linkBaseURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.style.com%2Fvideo%2Fvogue%2Fivoguei%2F1896809786%2Fvogue-diaries-charlize-theron%2F33573440001&amp;playerID=8558003001&amp;domain=embed&amp;" /><param name="base" value="http://admin.brightcove.com" /><param name="seamlesstabbing" value="false" /><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="swLiveConnect" value="true" /><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://c.brightcove.com/services/viewer/federated_f9/8558003001?isVid=1&amp;publisherID=1568114478" /><param name="name" value="flashObj" /><param name="flashvars" value="videoId=33573440001&amp;linkBaseURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.style.com%2Fvideo%2Fvogue%2Fivoguei%2F1896809786%2Fvogue-diaries-charlize-theron%2F33573440001&amp;playerID=8558003001&amp;domain=embed&amp;" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed id="flashObj" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="404" height="436" src="http://c.brightcove.com/services/viewer/federated_f9/8558003001?isVid=1&amp;publisherID=1568114478" name="flashObj" allowscriptaccess="always" swliveconnect="true" allowfullscreen="true" seamlesstabbing="false" base="http://admin.brightcove.com" flashvars="videoId=33573440001&amp;linkBaseURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.style.com%2Fvideo%2Fvogue%2Fivoguei%2F1896809786%2Fvogue-diaries-charlize-theron%2F33573440001&amp;playerID=8558003001&amp;domain=embed&amp;" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"></embed></object>\n\n<p style="text-align: center;">--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\nA play on photo shoots and Paris.\n\nModel: Micheala Bruno\n\nPhotographers:<a href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a> &amp; Christan Summers\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-613" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/daily-fashion-insight/_buildings-boys-and-ladies/"><img class="   aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="ebb.and.pflow designer bangle, brass, 18k gold and silver bangle" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/buildings-boys-and-ladies.jpg" alt="Buildings. boys. &amp; ladies. " /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">8.06.09</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Arm Play.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Model: Micheala Bruno</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Photographer: Dewald Brand</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Graphic Design: Christan Summers</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-614" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/daily-fashion-insight/top-micheala-arm-and-blonde-legs/"><img class="         aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="The mode. Brass Bangle. Blonde Model. Contemporary Fashion." src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/top-micheala-arm-and-blonde-legs.jpg" alt="top blon. bottom gold" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<strong>Espressos, deer pillows &amp; one beautiful model</strong>\n\nOur firstphoto shoot. We are not going to pretend like we were not giddy like little kids in a candy shop, because we were.\n\nThe shoot was located in the 16th Arrondissement, gorgeous, high ceiling, classic and modern-designed apartment.\n\nBeautiful model, espressos until the end of time and one very cool photographer.\n\nA couple samples below, more on the website and more to come.\n\n<em>Photographer: </em><em><a href="http://www.dewaldbrand.com" target="_blank">Dewald Brand</a></em>\n\n<em>Model: Michela Bruno</em>\n\n<em>Make up: Antinea Mazurier\n</em>\n\n<em>Designer Jewelry: </em><em><a href="http://www.cinsummer.com" target="_blank">CinSummer.com</a></em>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class=" aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Philip Crangi Earrings" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/michalea-18.jpg" alt="Philip CRangi Academie 18k gold vermeil Earrings, $225" /></a></p>\n<em>Above</em>: <a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/PC003" target="_blank">Philip Crangi Academie</a> 18k gold Earrings\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="  aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Lisa Levine necklace, Zhen U.N., Anna Beck bracelet" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/michaela-6.jpg" alt="Anna Beck Bangle, Lisa Levine Twisted Chain Necklace, Zhen U.N. 18k Pendant &amp; Pin Necklace" /></a></p>\n<em> Above: </em><a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/anna-beck-14k-gold-plated-and-solid-silver-bang14.html" target="_blank">Anna Beck Bangle</a>, <a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/lisa-levine-twotoned-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Necklace</a>, Zhen U.N. Necklace and pin combo. All designs in silver and gold.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class=" aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Lisa Levine Rose Gold Necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/michala-8.jpg" alt="Lisa Levine Rose Gold Necklace, $275" /></a></p>\n<em>Above: </em><a href="http://www.cinsummer.org/lisa-levine-rose-gold-rope-necklace.html" target="_blank">Lisa Levine Necklace.</a> Rose Gold with an urban chic style.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class=" aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="ebbandpflow Etheral Earrings, Lisa Levine Necklace" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/michala-10.jpg" alt="ebbandpflow Etheral Earrings, Lisa Levine Necklace" /></a></p>\n<em>Above: </em><a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/LLE001" target="_blank">Lisa Levine</a> design necklace, <a href="http://www.ebbandpflow.com/" target="_blank">ebb.and.pflow</a> handmade earrings.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank"><img class="  aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Lisa Levine Necklace, Model: Michaela Bruno, CinSummer.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/micheala-couch-1.jpg" alt="Michaela Bruno" /></a></p>\n<em>Above: </em><a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/LLE006" target="_blank">Lisa Levine</a> Rainfall necklace and<a href="http://www.ebbandpflowlookbook.tumblr.com/page/10" target="_blank">ebbandpflow</a> linea plata earrings.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-525" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/daily-fashion-insight/michaela-philip-crangi-rio/"><img class=" aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Philip Crangi Designs, ebb.and.pflow brass bangle, Model: Micheala Bruno, CinSummer.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/Michaela-philip-crangi-rio.jpg" alt="Philip Crangi earrings, $225 &amp; ebbandpflow Rio bangle, $225" /></a></p>\n<em>Above: </em><a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/PC003" target="_blank">Philip Crangi Academie</a> 18k gold Earrings &amp;<a href="http://www.ebbandpflowlookbook.tumblr.com/page/3" target="_blank">ebbandpflow</a> 18k gold, brass and silver Rio bangle.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"><img class="  aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Lisa Levine designs, ebbandpflow Stackable Rings, CinSummer.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/micheala-2.jpg" alt="ebbandpflow Stackable Rings $35" /></a></p>\n<em>Above: </em><a href="http://www.ebbandpflowlookbook.tumblr.com/page/4" target="_blank">ebbandpflow</a> silver and gold stackable rings. Two toned and a great price for designer jewelry.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.icuinparis.com/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Lisa Levine Earrings, CinSummer.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/michaela-121.jpg" alt="Lisa Levine Feather Earrings, $89" width="604" height="403" /></a></p>\n<em>Above: </em><a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/LLE008" target="_blank">Lisa Levine</a> purple calico feather &amp; chain earrings\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-529" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/daily-fashion-insight/michaela-17/" target="_blank"><img class="  aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Lisa Levine &amp; ebbandplfow Designs, CinSummer.com" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/michaela-17.jpg" alt="Lisa Levine Necklace, $205 &amp; ebbandpflow Ring, $65" /></a></p>\nAbove:<a href="https://www.cinsummer.com/index.php#/shop/product/LLE001" target="_blank">Lisa Levine</a> triple tone gradient chain necklace &amp;<a href="http://www.ebbandpflow.com" target="_blank">ebbandpflow</a> silver and 18k gold<a href="http://www.ebbandpflowlookbook.tumblr.com/page/4" target="_blank">Inversion Ring </a>&amp;<a href="http://www.ebbandpflowlookbook.tumblr.com/page/7" target="_blank">Ethereal Limon Earrings.</a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<em>8.04.09</em>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Tiger. Eye.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Model: Micheala Bruno</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Photographer: Dewald Brand</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Graphic Design: Christan Summers</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-615" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/daily-fashion-insight/michela-and-philip-crangi/" target="_blank"><img class="    aligncenter" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;" title="Philip Crangi Earrings, independent designer jewelry" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/michela-and-philip-crangi.jpg" alt="Tiger. Eye." /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>', 'AUGUST UPDATES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'august-updates', '', '', '2009-08-08 13:06:53', '2009-08-08 11:06:53', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8355', 0, 'post', '', 0);
