(8660, 4, '2012-12-23 00:54:43', '2012-12-22 23:54:43', '<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">I would guess that not many people even know the <a title="Norman Rockwell" href="http://www.nrm.org/" target="_blank">Norman Rockwell Museum</a> exists. I didn''t and was delighted to discover it while recently in Massachusetts in the Berkshires. Norman Rockwell is one of the most influential artists of the American publication history.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Known for his incredible ability to communicate a story and message through his work, documenting America''s history for over 40 years. His commissions included covers for The <em>Post</em>, <em>Look</em>,<em>Life</em>,<em>Literary Digest</em>, <em>Saturday Evening Post</em> and<em>Country Gentleman</em>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">We don''t see this kind of work anymore - interesting thought.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2351.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8650" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2351-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="483" height="644" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2352.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8651" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2352-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="483" height="644" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2353.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8652" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2353-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="483" height="644" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2354.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8653" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2354-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="476" height="356" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2355.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8654" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2355-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="367" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2356.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8655" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2356-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="453" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2357.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8656" title="Simon Rockwell" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2357-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="453" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>', 'Norman Rockwell: A Stroll Through American History', 'I would guess that not many people even know the Norman Rockwell Museum exists. I didn''t and was delighted to discover it while recently in Massachusetts in the Berkshires. Norman Rockwell is one of the most influential artists of the American publication history.\n', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'norman-rockwell-a-stroll-through-american-history', '', '', '2012-12-23 00:54:43', '2012-12-22 23:54:43', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8660', 0, 'post', '', 0),
