2/IMG_2381-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="604" /></a></p>', 'I Like What Your Wearing Pop-Up Shop Opening at Dagny + Barstow', 'Last week the e-commerce site, I Like What You''re Wearing (ILWYW) celebrated the opening of their pop-up shop at DAGNY + BARSTOW on Bowery between Houston & Prince. Fantastic selection - they will be in the shop until the 31st of December.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'i-like-what-your-wearing-pop-up-shop-opening-at-dagny-barstow', '', '', '2012-12-23 01:13:55', '2012-12-23 00:13:55', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8664', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(8681, 4, '2012-12-23 17:41:38', '2012-12-23 16:41:38', '<p style="text-align: left;">Buying beautiful jewels for a cause, is always a great idea. <a title="aea jewelry" href="http://www.aeajewelry.com/" target="_blank">AEA Jewelry</a>,<a title="Thomas IV bags" href="http://thomasthefourth.com/" target="_blank">Thomas IV</a> and <a title="opus" href="http://www.amagnumopus.com/" target="_blank">Opus</a> organized a fantastic event the 19th of December at <a title="lost weekend nyc" href="http://www.lostweekendnyc.com/" target="_blank">Lost Weekend NYC</a> to raise funds for Sandy and support Keepin'' it Local (all designers design and create in NYC).</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">I was accompanied by my dear friend and PR jaguar lady, Jessica De Guardiola, we had the pleasure of also meeting Illustrator/designer <a title="emily bartley" href="http://www.emilybartley.com/" target="_blank">Emily Bartley</a>- I would love one of her prints.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2395.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8684" title="AEA @ LOST WEEKEND NYC" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2395-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="604" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2389.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8682" title="AEA @ LOST WEEKEND NYC" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2389-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="453" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2390.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8683" title="AEA @ LOST WEEKEND NYC" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2390-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="453" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/20