(8709, 4, '2012-12-31 03:34:51', '2012-12-31 02:34:51', 'Today was a museum day to the<a title="MFA Boston" href="http://www.mfa.org/" target="_blank"> Museum of Fine Arts</a> in Boston. I was graced with the presence of Jamall Ouokun of <a title="papercut magazine" href="http://www.papercutmag.com/" target="_blank">PaperCut Magazine</a> to peruse through the many lenses of <strong>Mario Testino</strong>. A grand exhibit, divided into two parts; one dedicated to the Royal Family, the other to his work in fashion editorial and fashion''s most beloved super models. Go figure the division.\n\nOn our way to the exhibit we stopped to feast our eyes on the <a title="MFA Boston jewels, gems &amp; treasures " href="http://www.mfa.org/exhibitions/jewels-gems-and-treasures" target="_blank">Jewels, Gems and Treasures</a> exhibit; showcasing a rare selection of fine jewelry dating all the way back to the 24th Century BC. Extraordinary pieces.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2575.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-8721" title="Mario Testino, MFA Exhibit Boston" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2575-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="453" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2576.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-8722  aligncenter" title="Mario Testino, MFA Exhibit Boston" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2576-1024x768.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="453" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Untitled, Los Angeles, V Man, 2008</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2578.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-8723  aligncenter" title="Mario Testino, MFA Exhibit Boston" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/IMG_2578-768x1024.jpg" alt="" width="604" height="805" /></a