(8788, 4, '2013-01-24 17:23:16', '2013-01-24 16:23:16', '<strong>BACK IN NYC WITH BELLS ON -</strong>\n\n- <strong>Tuesday, January 29th</strong> we will host our American dbut for <a title="Showroom ICU" href="http://www.showroomicu.com/" target="_blank">Showroom ICU</a>, the sister division to <a title="icuinparis.com" href="http://www.icuinparis.com" target="_blank">icuinparis.com</a>, presenting designers to the international retail market on a B2B level.\n\nAlthough the day is dedicated to press, we will open the event for a fabulous <strong>shopping soire from</strong> <strong>6:30pm - 8:30pm</strong>.\n\nYou will gain an exclusive peak &amp; option to pre-order the <strong>FW/13 collections</strong> from French designers; <a title="Charlotte Martyr x Solweig Lizlow" href="http://charlottemartyr.com/" target="_blank">Solweig Lizlow x Charlotte Martyr</a>, <a title="noot - icuinparis.com" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?designer=44" target="_blank">Noot</a> and NYC based designer, <a title="AEA icuinparis.com" href="https://www.icuinparis.com/shop-independent-designer-accessories.html?designer=44" target="_blank">AEA</a>. Current SS/13 collections will be on immediate sale.\n\nThe invite is attached below, the event will be hosted by <a title="25 PARK" href="http://www.25park.com/" target="_blank">25 PARK</a> at their new Madison Ave. location: <a title="25 PARK" href="http://maps.google.com/maps?client=safari&amp;rls=en&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;q=998+MADISON+AVE+NY+NY+10075&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=0x89c258944ebc5717:0xac8b512673496f74,998+Madison+Ave,+New+York,+NY+10075&amp;gl=us&amp;sa=X&amp;ei=l1ABUd62JYTH0QHGn4GABA&amp;ved=0CDAQ8gEwAA" target="_blank">998 Madison Ave. between 77th &amp; 78th St</a>.\n\nFeel free to <a href="christan@icuinparis.com" target="_blank">contact me</a> directly to me with any questions and I hope to see you there!\n\n Christan\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-conten