/a>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/pHeavenTanudiredjaSS13Campaign159351873728.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8882" title="Heaven-Tanudiredja" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/pHeavenTanudiredjaSS13Campaign159351873728.jpg" alt="Heaven-Tanudiredja" width="620" height="465" /></a>', 'Found Heaven in Tanudiredja', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2013-04-20 00:53:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8881', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(8893, 4, '2013-04-24 21:42:53', '2013-04-24 19:42:53', '<p style="text-align: left;">Yesterday, we sat in on <a title="Luxury Daily" href="http://www.luxurydaily.com/" target="_blank">Luxury Daily</a>s most recent webinar, Tapping Social Media Without Diluting the Luxury Brands Mystique, where panelists fromMcCann Worldgroups MRM, Style Coalition, Pandemic Labs and B Culture Media discussed what works and what doesnt when using social media for luxury brands. We found Dior''s IconicColors campaign the best all-around example of a well-thought and authentic campaign. Below, we''ve shared some of the knowledge gained:</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Beautiful Imagery is Key - Dior''s #IconicColors Campaign</strong></p>\nNeedless to say, in the world of luxury digital marketing, imagery and presentation is crucial in attracting and engaging our consumer. Who wants to share a pixelated or blurry image? If I am to share/like an image, and in other words, be a brand''s promoter <em>for free</em>, I want to support content that is beautiful, unique, innovative - presentable. In the end, as a consumer and marketer, I am building my reputation through the concept of sharing andexpressing support for this brand.\n\nA true test to a brand''s marketing ability is how well they are able to create a story the consumer identifies with or aspires to. A great example of this would be Dior''s recent #IconicColors campaign which marketed this season''s exclusive lip color palette. they posted every 30 minutes for one day on their Twitter feed. Every 30 minutes, for one day only (March 27th), "Dior posted one exclusive brand color accompanied by an image of a makeup look or an apparel or accessory item. The brand described each color in a few words and provided its name and number," reports <em>Tricia Carr, editorial assistant on Luxury Daily</em>.\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/6013.jpg"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-8910" title="6013" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/6013.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="430" /></a><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Dior-tweets.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-8909 alignright" title="Dior-tweets" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Dior-tweets.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="385" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe strategy of inspiring consumers via color palettes not only makes this campaign internationally unified (color communicates across all languages), but it also circles back to the roots of Dior as a brand. Using the term, <em>iconic</em>is bold and reiterates the brand''s enduring position in the luxury and retail markets. Beautiful imagery is therefore provided by matching the iconic color to a striking image, making this campaign not only shareable, but remarkable, literally.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/BGW9EEQCAAA6I8M.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-8914 aligncenter" title="BGW9EEQCAAA6I8M" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/BGW9EEQCAAA6I8M.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="716" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/tumblr_mkdk3jp9AD1rpywblo1_500.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-8912 aligncenter" title="tumblr_mkdk3jp9AD1rpywblo1_500" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/tumblr_mkdk3jp9AD1rpywblo1_500.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="597" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p.txt1.jpeg"><img class="size-full wp-image-8913 aligncenter" title="p.txt" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/p.txt1.jpeg" alt="" width="497" height="372" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>\n</strong>', 'Tapping Social Media Without Diluting the Luxury Brands Mystique - Dior&#039;s #IconicColors', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tapping-social-media-without-diluting-the-luxury-brands-mystique-diors-iconiccolors', '', '', '2013-04-24 21:42:53', '2013-04-24 19:42:53', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8893', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(8921, 12, '2013-04-25 22:26:55', '2013-04-25 20:26:55', '&nbsp;\n\nYesterday evening, I attended an event at the <a title="Wix Lounge" href="http://www.wixlounge.com/? utm_source=ixda&amp;utm_medium=ixda&amp;utm_campaign=lounge&amp;experiment_id=[ixda ]" target="_blank">Wix Lounge</a>, a free co-working space near Union Square, that is also host to events from business marketing to fashion shows. In addition, the space acts as a gallery, with shows rotating every few months. The current show, <a title="Catwalk Sidewalk" href="http://www.catwalk-sidewalk.com/" target="_blank">Catwalk-Sidewalk</a>, caught my attention as it juxtaposes the work of two photographers to explore the relationship between runway and street fashion.\n\n<a title="Liam Alexander" href="http://www.liamalexanderphoto.com" target="_blank">Liam Alexander</a> and <a title="Galo Delgado" href="http://www.galodelgado.com" target="_blank">Galo Delgado</a>, have been friends and collaborators for over 10 years. Liam walked me through the gallery, while explaining his and Galo''s complimentary experience in their work; Liam''s in runway and Galo''s in NYC street style.  The two felt that their respective styles of photography paint a complete picture of fashion as it moves from catwalk to street and vice-versa.\n\nWhat made the exhibit special was the curation of the photographs. The photos were displayed in pairs, in a way that blurs the line between runway and street style, intersecting trends between worlds. As I walked with Liam around the gallery, I couldn''t always decipher which runway photo was his.\n\nBelow are a selection of photos from the show at Wix, all taken by Liam Alexander and Galo Delgado.\n\n<strong>Wix Lounge10 W18th St. 2nd Fl.NY NY 10011</strong>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_ragandbone.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8928" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_ragandbone.jpg" alt="Alone Amongst Many photo of model on runway" width="555" height="832" /></a>\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_redglove.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8924" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_redglove.jpg" alt="The Red Glove" width="556" height="833" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_karenwalker.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8927" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_karenwalker.jpg" alt="Photo looking up onto balcony at fashion show Stella and her Sisters" width="747" height="496" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_coldair.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8929" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_coldair.jpg" alt="The Cold Air Brings A Moment of Clairty" width="747" height="498" /></a><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"></span>\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_annyee.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8925" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_annyee.jpg" alt="Photo of woman on balcony at Ann Yee Fashion Show" width="747" height="498" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_carrotbay.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8923" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_carrotbay.jpg" alt="Photo by Galo Delgado of woman against graffitied wall" width="746" height="497" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_breakattiff.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8922" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/galo_delgado_breakattiff.jpg" alt="Breakfast at Tiffany''s But Better" width="747" height="498" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_eccodomani.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-8926" src="https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/liam_alexander_eccodomani.jpg" alt="Snakeskin Wallet photo of model walking down runway" width="556" height="833" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAll of the photos were taken by Liam Alexander and Galo Delgado, and are from the show<em>Catwalk-Sidewalk</em>currently hosted at the <a title="wix lounge" href="http://www.wixlounge.com/? utm_source=ixda&amp;utm_medium=ixda&amp;utm_campaign=lounge&amp;experiment_id=[ixda ]" target="_blank">Wix Lounge</a>.', 'Catwalk-Sidewalk Exhibit at Wix Lounge', 'Liam Alexander and Galo Delgado, have been friends and collaborators for over 10 years.  Liam walked me through the gallery, while explaining his and Galo''s complimentary experience in their work; Liam''s in runway and Galo''s in NYC street style.   The two felt that their respective styles of photography paint a complete picture of fashion as it moves from catwalk to street and vice-versa.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'catwalk-sidewalk-exhibit-at-wix-lounge', '', '', '2013-04-25 22:26:55', '2013-04-25 20:26:55', '', 0, 'https://www.icuinparis.com/blog/?p=8921', 0, 'post', '', 0),
